\mt1 Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\is1 Akar Faragha Zuim 
\ip Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim…®n, e Iesus…®n garima, a Israelbar gumazamiziba ua me inigha, egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba, uaghan me ini. Ez…® Iesus uan ingangarim damuasa, kamagh…®n gumazamizibav m…®g…®a ghaze, God akar aghuim gumazir onganaraziba mik…®nasa na ginaba. Ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Ekiam…®n Duam nan iti. (Luk 4:18…®n gan.) Ez…® bar guizbang…®ra, ak…®nafarir kam…®n Luk Iesus geghara ghaze, a gumazamizir os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateribar apangkuvigha derav…®ra me gami. 
\ip Bizir Iesus amiba, da an adarazir gamima, me bar a gakonge. Dughiar Maria a batezim…®n, gumazamiziba bar akonge (Luk 1:42-48, 2:10), egha ghua ak…®nafarim g…®vaz…® nagh…®n tuz…®, Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanaboz…®ma, me bar akuega mamagh…®ra iti. (Luk 24:52…®n gan). 
\ip Iesus…®n ik…®m…®rim…®n bizir av…®riba Luk uab…®ra dagh eghari. Bizir kaba, da ak…®nafarir igharazitam…®n itir puvat…®. Luk uab…®ra, Iesus nguazim…®n izezir bizir av…®rir otivizibagh eghari. Luk uab…®ra, a Iesus…®n akar is…®n zuir kam geghari, a kamak…®n: Gumazir mam os…®mt…®zim tuavim…®n a bato, ez…® Samarian gumazim an akura. Ez…® akar is…®n zuir igharazim, Luk a geghari, otarim afeziam ategha ghua tintinibar aruigha g…®n uamategha ize. Egha Luk Iesus…®n akar is…®n zuir mabanang uaghan dagh eghari. Egha Luk uab…®ra, bizir Sakius batozim geghari, kar gumazir dag…®aba isim. 
\ip Bizir maba Luk akar av…®riba dar iti, dar kara: God ko m…®k…®m…®v…®ra ikiamin arazim, ko God…®n Duam…®n ingangarim, ko God gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir arazim. Egha Luk uaghan amiziba ingarizir bizibar akar av…®riba da iti. 
\ip Luk…®n akaba, da ak…®nafarir kamra itir puvat…®. Luk uaghan ak…®nafarir igharazim osiri, e a d…®bora ghaze, Aposelbar Ingangaribar Ak…®nafarim. E fo, Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabogha g…®vaz…®ma, Aposelba bizir av…®ribagh ami. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven, Luk aposelba amizir bizibar eghaghanim osiri. 
\c 1  
\s1 Luk osirizir akar faragha zuim 
\p  
\v 1-4 Gumazir aruam, Tiofilus, n…® fo, gumazir av…®riba God en tong…®n amizir bizibar ganigha, dar gun osirasava ami. E gumazir uari uan damaziba ganizibar akam baraki. Egha me faragha God…®n akam…®n ingangarir gumazibar otivigha, egha an akam akuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uaghan akar kam osirigh n…® bagh anemangasa. Egha k…® deraghav…®ra dar m…®ngaribagh foghasa ingara ghua dagh foghava, n…® bagha bar derav…®rama da osiri. N…® dar gan fogh suam, bizir n…® oraghizir kaba da guiz…®n biziba. 
\ms1 Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n amebam a batezir dughiam, ko Maria Iesus batezir dughiam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am 
\mr (Sapta 1:5-2:52) 
\s1 Ensel Sekaraian m…®g…®a ghaze, Jon otogham 
\p  
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n Herot Judian atrivim…®n itima, God…®n ofa gamir gumazir mam…®n ziam Sekaraia, an Abiyan adarazir gumazir mam. Ez…®ma an amuim Elisabet, an Aron…®n ovavim.  
\v 6 Aning bar deraghav…®ra God…®n araziba koma an akam baragha dar g…®n zui. Ez…®ma God aning…®n garima, aning an damazim…®n bar dera.  
\v 7 Elisabet furabagh ati, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma aning boriba puvat…®ghava, dughiar ruarim pura ikia ghua bar ghuri. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ingarima, Sekaraia uaghan ofa gamir gumazim…®n m…®n God…®n damazim…®n ingari.  
\v 9 Ez…® me God…®n D…®penim…®n ofa gamir gumazibar arazibar g…®nt…®gha, gumazim am…®s…®vasa me dag…®abagh da kuri. Ez…® God anem…®sefe. Eght…® Sekaraia God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…® m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim dapongam.\f + \ft (1:9) Kar men arazim, God gumazim uan ingangarim bagha anem…®s…®vasa, me ikararer kam gami. Ikararer kam a satun ikararer biziba iniasa ikararem…®n amir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 10 Ez…®ma m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim dapongamin dughiam otoz…®ma, gumazamizir God…®n ziam feba, God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n uari akuvagha God ko m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…®ma Ekiam…®n Ensel a batogha, m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim…®n ofan danganim…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan tughav iti.  
\v 12 Ez…® Sekaraia an apigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha bar atiatingi.  
\v 13 Ez…®ma ensel kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSekaraia, n…® atiatingan mark…®, n…® God ko m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®am, God a baraki. Ez…®ma n…®n amuim Elisabet n…® bagh otarim bategham. Eght…® n…® ziar kam, Jon a dat…®gh.  
\v 14-15 Egh n…® bar akuegh navir am…®r…®zim…®n ik…®. Eght…® a God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iniam, kamagh…®n gumazamizir av…®riba an otoghamin dughiam…®n bar akuegham. Eght…® a wain ko d…®par onganibar aman kogham. Egh a uan amebam…®n navir averiam…®n aven ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, God…®n Duam bar a giz…®vagham.  
\v 16 Egh a uam Israel…®n gumazamizir av…®riba inigh men Ekiam God bagh mangam.  
\v 17 Egh Elaijan itir God…®n Duam ko gavgavir kamra Jon Ekiam…®n faragh mang…®va, afeziabar amut…®ma me uan boriba ua dagh fuegh…®va, ak…®riba ragha God gasaraziba ua me damut…®ma me ua n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar gumazibar amuva, egh gumazibav k…®mt…®ma me uari ak…®r…®ghas…® Ekiam m…®zuam ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Sekaraia ensel…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® ghuriz…®, nan amuim uaghan ghurigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® manmagh…®n bizir kam guizbang…®ra a g…®fogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® ensel an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® Gebriel. K…® God…®n damazim…®n tughav iti. God uab…® na amadaz…®ma, k…® akar aghuir kam…®n n…® m…®k…®masa ize.  
\v 20 N…® nan akaba baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar itir puvat…®. Ez…® bizir kam bagh n…® m…®k…®man kogh n…®m…®ra ikiam, mamagh…®ra ik…®t…®ma bizir kaba otivamin dughiam otogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ensel Sekaraia m…®geima, gumaziba ko amiziba azenan ikia Sekaraia m…®zua ghuav am…®ragha pura n…®ghn…®si, manmagh…®n amizim a dughiar ruarim…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti?  
\v 22 Ez…® an azenan otoghava, me m…®k…®man asaghasaki. Ez…® me fo, a ti God…®n D…®penim…®n aven irebam…®n m…®n bizitam…®n gani. Egha an akam…®n me m…®geir puvat…®gha dafaribara me m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 23 Eghava an ingangarir dughiam g…®vaz…®ma, a uan nguibam…®n ghu.  
\v 24 Ez…®ma dughiar maba ghua g…®vaz…®ma an amuim Elisabet navim ada 5 plan iakinibar uab…® modo.  
\v 25 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam na bagha bizir kam gami. A nan apangkuvigha nan aghums…®zim gumazamizibar damazim…®n anedangi.‚Äù 
\s1 Ensel Maria bagha akam inigha zui 
\p  
\v 26 Egha Elisabet…®n navir adasem 6 plan iakinim…®n otoz…®ma, God ensel Gebriel Nasaret…®n anemada, Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam.  
\v 27 Ez…® ensel ghua, guivir igiar gumazitam koma akuizir puvat…®zim, an ziam Maria, me gumazim Josep…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Josep, an Atrivim Devit…®n ovavimra.  
\v 28 Ensel a bagha ghuava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar aghuarim Maria. Ekiam n…® gifongegha derav…®ra n…® gamua egha n…® ko iti.‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® Maria an akam baregha d…®gavir kuram gamigha pura n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúKar akar manmagh…®n amizim?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMaria, n…® atiatingan mark…®, God bar n…® gifuegha n…® ko iti.  
\v 31 N…® oragh, n…® navim asegh otarim bategh…®va, ziar kam Iesus, a dat…®gh.  
\v 32 A ziar ekiam ik…®t…®, me suam, kar God…®n bar p…®n itim…®n otarim. Eght…® God a damight…®, a uan ovavim, Atrivim Devit…®n m…®n ikiam.  
\v 33 Eght…® a Jekop…®n adarazir atrivim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Eght…® a bizibagh ativamin dughiar kam g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 34 Ez…®ma Maria kamagh…®n ensel…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® guivir igiar patam…®n itir puvat…®zim. Ez…®ma bizir kam manmagh…®n na batogham?‚Äù  
\v 35 Ez…® ensel an akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n Duam n…® bagh izeght…® bar p…®n itir God…®n gavgavim n…® avaragham. Eght…® borim God…®n damazim…®n zueght…® me God…®n Otarim a dar…®gham.  
\v 36-37 Bizitam God…®n aven kozir puvat…®. N…®n anabam Elisabet, a ghurigha, egha uaghan navim adai. Me ghaze, an navim asangan kogham, ez…® an navir adasem dat…®r…®gh…®n iakinir 6 plan tu.‚Äù  
\v 38 Ez…® Maria kamagh…®n ensel ikara, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n ingangarir amizim. N…® m…®kemezir mogh…®ra God bizibar na damu.‚Äù Ez…® ensel anetegha ghu. 
\s1 Maria Elisabet…®n ganasa zui 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Maria uan biziba ak…®righava zuam…®ra nguibar ekiar Judian Distrigh…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n itim…®n ghu.  
\v 40 Egha a Sekaraian d…®penim…®n aven ghugha dughiam Elisabet gan…®ngi.  
\v 41 Ez…® Elisabet Marian tiarim barazima, an borim an navim…®n aven aguaghfa, ez…®ma Elisabet God…®n Duam a giz…®fa.  
\v 42 Eghava a pamtem…®n tiarim akarigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® amizibagh afiraz…® God bar bizir aghuim n…® gami. Egh a uaghan bizir aghuim borir n…® oteghamim gami.  
\v 43 Ez…® God tizim bagha derav…®ra na gami, ez…®ma nan Ekiam…®n amebam na bagh izi?  
\v 44 Ez…® k…® n…® barazi, n…® dughiam na gan…®ngiz…®ma borir na navir averiam…®n itim bar akuegha aguaghfa.  
\v 45 N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti, ez…® Ekiam n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar n…® gami. Kamagh…®n n…® bar akongegh.‚Äù 
\s1 Marian ighiam 
\p  
\v 46-49 Ez…® Maria kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® pura Ekiam…®n ingangarir amizim, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a na gin…®r…®. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n nan navim Ekiam…®n ziam fe. 
\q2 Ez…® nan duam God bagha bar akonge, 
\q3 a nan akurvazim. 
\q1 God a bar gavgavigha bizir bar ekiabar na gami. 
\q2 Ez…® an ziam bar zuegha dera. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n tugh mang…® 
\q3 gumazamiziba na m…®k…®m suam, 
\q3 God derav…®ra n…® gami. 
\q1  
\v 50 Ez…®ma a gumazamizir an atiatiava an apengan itibar apangkufi. 
\q2 A kamagh…®ra dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizibar amu 
\q3 g…®n izamin gumaziba ko amizibar amu mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 51 A uan dafarim…®n bizir bar gavgavibagh ami. 
\q2 Gumazir uarira uan ziaba feba, a men ag…®raz…®ma me are. 
\q1  
\v 52 God atrivibar gavgavim d…®kab…®ragha 
\q2 gumazir k…®niba fe. 
\q1  
\v 53 A bizir aghuiba isava m…®tiriaba azibagh aniga, 
\q2 biziba bar iz…®vaziba amangiz…®ma me pura ghue. 
\q1  
\v 54-55 A uan ingangarir gumazim Israel…®n akura. 
\q2 Egha en ovavibagh amizir akar gavgavim g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. 
\q2 Egha Abraham…®n apangkuvigha, 
\q3 egh g…®n otivamin gumazibar apangkuvigh mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 56 Ez…® Maria iakinir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n Elisabet ko ikegha g…®n uamategh uan nguibam…®n ghu. 
\s1 Elisabet Jon batezir dughiam 
\p  
\v 57 Ez…®ma Elisabet otamin dughiam otoz…®ma, an otarim bate.  
\v 58 An borogh…®ra itir darasi koma an anababa kamagh…®n oraki, Ekiam an apangkuvigha bizir aghuim a gamiz…®ma, me a ko bar akonge.  
\v 59 Ez…® an 7 plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, me borim…®n m…®karzir mogomem aghorasa izi. Egha me an afeziam…®n ziam Sekaraia a dar…®ghasa.  
\v 60 Ez…®ma an amebam kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®! E Jon a dar…®gham.‚Äù  
\v 61 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n anabatam ziar katam itir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 62 Egha me dafarimra an afeziam…®n azangs…®si, a ziar manatam uan otarim dar…®gham.  
\v 63 Egha Sekaraia an ziam osirasa biziba bagha dafaribara men azangs…®si. Egha kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄúAn ziam Jon.‚Äù Ez…®ma me kamagh…®n ganigha bar aguaghfa.  
\v 64 Ez…®ma an akam zuam…®ra kuiaghr…®z…®ma an m…®zem f…®riaghr…®z…®ma, a magh…®ra m…®g…®ava God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 65 Ez…®ma an borogh…®n itir darazi kamagh…®n ganigha, bar atiatingi. Ez…®ma Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibar m…®ghs…®abar itibar gumaziba bizir otivizir kaba baregha dar gun uariv gei.  
\v 66 Ez…® Ekiam…®n gavgavim borir kam ko iti. Ez…®ma me bar mogh…®ra bizir kam baregha, a g…®n…®ghn…®gha a bagha azangs…®si, ‚ÄúBorir kam bar manmagh…®ram otogham?‚Äù 
\s1 Sekaraian ighiam 
\p  
\v 67 Ez…®ma an afeziam Sekaraia God…®n Duam a giz…®vaz…®ma, a God…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n gun m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 68 ‚ÄúEkiam iza uan gumaziba ko amiziba ua me ini, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, e an ziam fe, a Israelbar God. 
\q1  
\v 69 God en akurvaghasa uan ingangarir gumazim Devit…®n adarazir aven gumazir bar gavgavim am…®sefe. 
\q1  
\v 70 God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba bizir kam…®n gun fom…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®keme. 
\q1  
\v 71 An en apaniba koma en atara pazav e gamibar dam e iniasa ize. 
\q1  
\v 72 Egh apangkuvim en ovavibar akakagh…®va, 
\q1 uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim n…®r…®gham, 
\q2  
\v 73 akar gavgavir en ovavim Abraham gan…®ngizim. 
\q1  
\v 74 Egh en apaniba dam e iniva, 
\q2 en amamangat…®ght…®ma e an ingars…®va atiatingan kogh…®va, 
\q2  
\v 75 egh…®va e an damazim…®n arazir aghuir a ifongezibar g…®n mangam, 
\q3 eght…® a ifongezir arazir aghuir kaba en ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 76 Ez…® n…® nan borim, n…® faragh mang…® Ekiam bagh tuavim ak…®r. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amizim, me God…®n bar p…®n itim…®n akam inigha izir gumazim n…® dar…®gham. 
\q1  
\v 77-78 God…®n apangkuvim e ko itima, a uan gumazamiziba ua me iniamin fofozim me gan…®ga, 
\q2 men arazir kuraba g…®n amadi. 
\q3 Ez…®ma aruem…®n angazangarim God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegh e bagh izighram. 
\q1  
\v 79 Egh angazangarim m…®tarmem…®n ikiava aremeghasava amibagh fegh…®va, 
\q2 egh navir am…®r…®zim…®n tuavim en suebar akagham.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 80 Ez…®ma Jon g…®n aghuiga g…®vaz…®ma an duam uaghan aghua gavgafi. Egha a Judian nguazir gumaziba puvat…®zim…®n iti. Egha ghua an azenim gir…®gha Israel…®n gumazibar damazim…®n oto. 
\c 2  
\s1 Maria Iesus bate 
\r (Matyu 1:18-25) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar kam Sisar Ogastus akar gavgavim amadagha ghaze, ‚ÄúRom garir nguibabar gumazamiziba bar mang…® uan ziaba osir.‚Äù  
\v 2 Dughiar kam Kwirinius, a Sirian gumazir dapanim…®n itima, ziaba osirir dughiar faragha zuir kam oto.\f + \ft (2:2) Dughiar kam, Rom…®n gavman Israelbar nguibaba bar dagh ativagha dar gari. Israel…®n nguibar ekiam, a Provins Sirian aven iti. Rom…®n gavman…®n gumaziba, me men garir atriviba d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúSisar.‚Äù\f* 
\v 3 Ez…® gumazamiziba uan ziaba osirasa uan nguibabara zui.  
\v 4 Ez…® Josep uaghan Devit…®n anabar mam. Kamagh…®n a Galilin Distrigh…®n itir nguibam Nasaret ategha, Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibam Betlehem…®n zui, kar Devit…®n nguibam.  
\v 5 A mang…®va uan amuir inabazim Maria ko aning uan ziamning osirasa. Dughiar kam Maria borim…®n navim adai.  
\v 6 Egha aning ghuava Betlehem…®n itima, Maria borim batamin dughiam oto.  
\v 7 Ez…® a uan otarir ivariam bate. Egha borim inir av…®zibar a nomke. Dughiar kam d…®penir akuim iz…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning borim isava bulmakauba apir danganim…®n anet…®. 
\s1 Enselba akam inigha sipsipbar garir gumaziba bagha zui 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® sipsipbar garir gumazir maba nguibam…®n azenan ikiava, d…®magaribar uan sipsipbar gara me geghufi.  
\v 9 Ez…® Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam pura me batoz…®, Ekiam…®n angazangarim me gisira. Ez…® me bar atiatingi.  
\v 10 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa atiatingan mark…®. Ia oragh! K…® akar aghuim inigha ia bagha izi. Akar aghuir gumazamiziba bar me damight…®, me bar akongegham.  
\v 11 Dat…®r…®gh…®n Devit…®n nguibam…®n akurvazir gumazim ia bagha oto. A God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, a en Ekiam.  
\v 12 Ia mang…® kamagh…®n ganigh fogh, ia gant…®ma me borim inir av…®zibar a nomkegh…®va bulmakauba apir danganim dat…®ght…®ma a ir…®gh…®v ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® magh…®ra, God…®n nguibam…®n ensel…®n av…®rir bar dafam otogha ensel…®n kam ko me God…®n ziam fa kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 ‚ÄúIa bizibar p…®n itir God…®n ziam f…®. 
\q2 Eght…® nguazim…®n itir gumaziba ko amizir God ifongeziba, 
\q3 me navir am…®r…®zim…®n ik…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Sipsipbar garir gumaziba Iesus…®n ganasa zui 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® enselba sipsipbar garir gumaziba ategha God…®n nguibam…®n ghuez…®ma, ez…® sipsipbar garir gumaziba uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúAria, e Betlehem…®n mang…®va Ekiam e m…®kemezir bizir otozim…®n ganika.‚Äù  
\v 16 Egha me zuam…®ra ghuava Josep ko Marian api, egha borim…®n garima a bulmakauba apir danganim gir…®ghav iti.  
\v 17 Egha sipsipbar garir gumaziba borim…®n ganigha, egha ensel borim…®n gun me m…®kemezir akabar gun gumazir igharazibav gei.  
\v 18 Ez…® gumazamiziba sipsipbar garir gumazibar eghaghanim baregha d…®gavir kuram gami.  
\v 19 Ez…® Maria bizir kaba uan navir averiam gat…®gha, egha dagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti.  
\v 20 Ez…® sipsipbar garir gumaziba uamatenge. Ensel me m…®kemez…® me oraghiz…® mogh…®n bizibar gari, da otifi. Kamagh…®n me bar akuegha God…®n ziam fa zui. 
\s1 God…®n ensel me m…®kemez…® mokon, me ziam Iesus a gat…® 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® 7 plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma an m…®karzir mogomem aghoramin dughiam otoz…® me ziam Iesus a gat…®. Maria t…®ghar navim asangam, ensel faragha a gat…®zir ziam. 
\s1 Simeon ko Ana God…®n D…®penim…®n Iesus…®n gari 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Moses Osirizir Arazibar m…®n amebam God…®n damazim…®n zueghamin dughiam otoz…®ma, Maria ko Josep borim inigha Ekiam dan…®ngasa Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 23 Ekiam Moses gan…®ngizir arazibar osizirim iti, borir otarir ivariaba me da is…® ua Ekiam dan…®ngam.  
\v 24 Ez…® aning Ekiam…®n arazir osiriziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, aning ofa damuasa, kuarazir bunbar pumuning, o bunbam…®n m…®n gari kuarazir igiar pumuning inigha izi. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n aven gumazir mam, an ziam Simeon, a God…®n damazim…®n deragha God baghav…®ra iti. A Israel…®n gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba a g…®vamin dughiam bagha m…®zuai iti.  
\v 26 God…®n Duam bizir kam azenarama an akagha g…®fa, a faragh Ekiam…®n Krais (Gumazir God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezim), an an ganigh…®va, g…®n aremegham.\f + \ft (2:26) Krais…®n m…®ngarimra kara, God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.\f* 
\v 27 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma God…®n Duam n…®ghn…®zim a gan…®ngiz…®ma a God…®n D…®penir av…®zim…®n zui. Ez…® Josep ko Maria Iesus inighava aven iza Ekiam…®n arazir osirizim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a damuasa.  
\v 28 Ez…® Simeon Iesus inighava uan dafarimning…®n a ifiraghava God…®n ziam fa kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 29-32 ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim. 
\q1 Eght…® n…®n akurvazim…®n angazangarim n…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba me dan…®ngam. 
\q2 Egh ziar ekiam Israelbar an…®ngam; me n…®n gumazamiziba. 
\q1 Ez…® n…® gumazamizibar damazibar me bagha akurvazir bizir kam gami. 
\q2 Ez…® n…® en akuragh ua e iniamin bizir kam, k…® uan damazim…®n an ganigha g…®fa. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® fom…®ra m…®kemez…® mogh…®n n…® na ateght…® k…® mang…®, 
\q2 navir am…®r…®zim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® borim…®n amebam ko afeziam Simeon an gun m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha aning n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 34 Ez…® Simeon ghaze, God bizir aghuiba ia bagh a dar amu, egha Simeon an amebam Maria kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBorir kam God a ginaba, eght…® Israel…®n av…®riba God bagh tugh gavgavigham. Eght…® av…®riba iregham. Eght…® gumazamiziba bizir an amibar gan…®va akar kurabar dav k…®mam.  
\v 35 Kamagh…®n gumazir av…®ribar n…®ghn…®zir navim…®n aven itiba azenan otivam. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir ekiar mam uaghan n…®n m…®karzim…®n otivam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir amizir mam iti, an ziam Ana, a Panuel…®n guivim, Aser…®n anabam. A faragha pam…®n itima aning…®n 7 plan azeniba, ez…® an pam aremez…®ma, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n a bar ghuri.  
\v 37 Egha 84 plan azeniba, a odiarim…®n iti. A God…®n D…®penim ataghrazir pu, egha d…®magariba ko arueba God…®n ziam fa, egha dagheba ataghragha God ko m…®gei.  
\v 38 Egha dughiar kamra a uaghan iza men m…®riam…®n tu. A biziba bagha God m…®nabi. Egha borir kam…®n gun gumazamizir av…®ribav gei, me God ua Jerusalem…®n itir gumaziba ko amiziba iniamin dughiam m…®zuai. 
\s1 Josep uamategha Nasaret…®n zui 
\p  
\v 39 Egha Josep ko Maria biziba bar Ekiam…®n arazir osirizim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n dagh amigha g…®vagha, egha uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Nasaret…®n zui.  
\v 40 Ez…® borim aghuiga m…®karzim…®n gavgafi. Ez…® fofozir aghuim bar a giz…®fa. Ez…® bizir aghuiba God a bagha dagh ami. 
\s1 Iesus otarir igiamra ikiava, God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 41 Azeniba zurara Iesus…®n amebam ko afeziam, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n Isam bagha Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 42 Ez…® an azenir 12 plan otogha, arazim m…®rara me isam bagha zui.  
\v 43 Isam g…®vaz…®ma, an g…®n, an amebam ko afeziam uamategha nguibam…®n zuima, aning…®n otarim Iesus, a Jerusalemra itima aning a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 44 Aning ghaze, a ti uan namakaba ko izi. Egha aruer kam…®n ghuav…®ra iti. Egha aning magh…®ra uan namakaba koma anababar torim…®n a bagha rui.  
\v 45 Egha aning an apizir puvat…®, egha aning a bagh ruiasa uamategha Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 46 Dughiar m…®kezim…®n g…®n aning God…®n D…®penim…®n av…®zim…®n an api. A tisabar torim…®n aperaghav iti, egha me baragha azangs…®zibar me gami.  
\v 47 Gumazir kaba bar an fofozim ko akar ikarvazir kaba baragha egha d…®gavir kuram gami.  
\v 48 Ez…® an amebam ko afeziam an apigha, egha d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha an amebam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan otarim, n…® tizim bagha arazir kurar kam…®n ga gami? Ga n…® bagha bar osemegha n…® buri.‚Äù  
\v 49 Ez…® a kamagh…®n aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizim bagha na buri? Gua ti fozir puvat…®, k…® uan Afeziam…®n D…®penim…®n aven ikiam?‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® an aning…®n m…®geir bizim…®n m…®ngarim aning a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 51 Egha a aning…®n akam baregha aning ko Nasaret…®n uaghiri. Ez…® an amebam bizir kaba baregha dagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti.  
\v 52 Ez…® Iesus fofozim ko m…®karzim sarama aghui. Ez…® an araziba God koma gumazibagh amima, me a gifonge. 
\c 3  
\ms1 Jon Iesus bagha tuavim ak…®ri 
\mr (Sapta 3:1-4:13) 
\s1 Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, faragha izava Iesus…®n akam akuri 
\r (Matyu 3:1-12 ko Mak 1:2-8 ko Jon 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam Taiberius Sisar…®n 15 plan azenim…®n Rom…®n atrivim…®n itim oto. Ez…® Pontius Pailat Judian Distrigh…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n iti, Herot Galilin Distrigh…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® an aveghbuam Filip Iturian Distrigh ko Trakonitis…®n Distrigh…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n ti, ez…® Lisanias Abilenen Distrigh…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n iti.  
\v 2 Ez…®ma Anas ko Kaiafas God…®n ofa gamir gumazir dapanimning…®n iti. Dughiar kam Jon, Sekaraian otarim, gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n itima, God uan m…®g…®r…®g…®am a gan…®ngi.  
\v 3 Ez…® Jon Jordan…®n d…®par m…®riam…®n aruava akam kura kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uan navibagh iragh…®va rueght…®, God ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù  
\v 4 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaian ak…®nafarim…®n osirizir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®rara ghu, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGumazir tiarir mam gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n dia ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh…®va tuaviba azen…®va, dar k…®r. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kukuniba apem…®va, m…®ghs…®aba ko ak…®ribar amut…® da mag…®r…®. 
\q2 Tuavir ighuagha aruiba dar amut…® da vorogh…®ra ik…®. 
\q3 Egh tuavir kurabar amut…® da deragh. 
\q1  
\v 6 Eght…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar 
\q2 God…®n akurvazim…®n ganam.‚Äô‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Jon gumazamizir b…®zir ruasa a bagha izibav gei, ‚ÄúIa kuruzir divir anababa! Tina ia m…®kemez…® ia God…®n adarim…®n ar…® mangasa?  
\v 8 Ia navim girazir arazibara amu. Egh ia pura Abraham…®n ovavibar uari ar…®gh m…®k…®man mark…®. K…® ia m…®gei, God dag…®ar kabara amight…® da Abraham…®n ovavibar m…®n otivighamin gavgavim iti.  
\v 9 Sobiam dat…®r…®gh…®n temer povibar iti, eght…® temer dagher ov…®zir aghuiba itir puvat…®ziba, God bar da okegh…®va da is…®va avim m…®k…®nam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® gumazamiziba Jon…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® e manmagh…®ra damuam?‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® Jon me ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir korotiar aven azuir pumuning itim, tam is…® gumazir puvat…®zim dan…®ngigh. Ez…® dagheba itiba uaghan kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® gavman…®n dag…®aba isir gumaziba uaghan ruasa ize. Egha me azangs…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúTisa, e manmagh…®ra damuam?‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazibar dag…®abagh is…®n ua dag…®ataba inian mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir maba Jon…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® eia, e manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù Ez…® a me ikara, ‚ÄúGumazamizibar dag…®aba ok…®ms…®va akar ifavaribar me gasan mark…®. Ia uan ingangarim…®n ivezimra init…® deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Gumazamiziba bizir kabar garima men navir averiaba me ginivima me pura n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Jon ti God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim?  
\v 16 Ez…® Jon bar men n…®ghn…®ziba ikara, ‚ÄúK…® d…®pam…®n ia rue. Ez…® gumazir mam g…®n izam, an gavgavim bar nan gavgavim gafira. An dagarir asuabar beniba k…® da firan gavgaviba puvat…®. A God…®n Duam ko avim…®n ia ruam.  
\v 17 A witba m…®sevir savol an agharim…®n iti, eght…® a uan witba m…®s…®va dar daghebar ar…®gh…®va, witba m…®sevir d…®penim…®n wit…®n m…®seviba aviva, egh dar m…®seviba avir munger puvat…®zim…®n da akunt…®ma, da isiam.‚Äù  
\v 18 Egha Jon m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®rir maba sara me m…®g…®a men navibagh inifi. Egha kamagh…®n akar aghuim me m…®k…®ri. 
\s1 Herot Jon kalabus gat…® 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® dughiar kam Herot gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n ti. A uan aveghbuam Filip…®n amuim Herodias koma akui, egha arazir kurar maba sarama ami. Ez…® kamagh…®n Jon Herodias bagha Herot…®n guam gat…®gha a m…®keme.  
\v 20 Herot uan arazir kurar maba ko kam sara is…®n at…®ghava, Jon kalabus gat…®ghava an tiam asara. 
\s1 Jon Iesus rue 
\r (Matyu 3:13-17 ko Mak 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 21 Jon gumazamiziba ruer dughiam, Iesus uaghan, Jon a rue. Ez…® Iesus uan afeziam God ko m…®geima, overiam kuiaghr…®z…®,  
\v 22 God…®n Duam bunbam…®n nivaf…®zim gavagha a bagha izaghiri. Ez…® tiarir mam overiam…®n otogha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim, Otarir k…® ifongezim. K…® n…® bagha bar akonge.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovaviba 
\r (Matyu 1:1-17) 
\p  
\v 23 Dughiar kam Iesus uab…® 30 plan azeniba. Ez…® a uan ingangarim magh…®ram a gami. Gumaziba ko amiziba ghaze, Iesus Josep…®n otarimra. Ez…® Josep Helin otarim.  
\v 24 Ez…® Heli Matat…®n otarim. Ez…® Matat Livain otarim. Ez…® Livai Melkin otarim. Ez…® Melki Janain otarim. Ez…® Janai Josep…®n otarim.  
\v 25 Ez…® Josep Matatias…®n otarim. Ez…® Matatias Amos…®n otarim. Ez…® Amos Nahum…®n otarim. Ez…® Nahum Eslin otarim. Ez…® Esli Nagain otarim.  
\v 26 Ez…® Nagai Mat…®n otarim. Ez…® Mat Matatias…®n otarim. Ez…® Matatias Semin…®n otarim. Ez…® Semin Josek…®n otarim. Ez…® Josek Jodan otarim.  
\v 27 Ez…® Joda Joanan…®n otarim. Ez…® Joanan Resean otarim. Ez…® Resea Serubabel…®n otarim. Ez…® Serubabel Sealtiel…®n otarim. Ez…® Sealtiel Nerin otarim.  
\v 28 Ez…® Neri Melkin otarim. Ez…® Melki Adin otarim. Ez…® Adi Kosam…®n otarim. Ez…® Kosam Elmadam…®n otarim. Ez…® Elmadam Er…®n otarim.  
\v 29 Ez…® Er Josuan otarim. Ez…® Josua Elieser…®n otarim. Ez…® Elieser Jorim…®n otarim. Ez…® Jorim Matat…®n otarim. Ez…® Matat Livain otarim.  
\v 30 Ez…® Livai Simeon…®n otarim. Ez…® Simeon Judan otarim. Ez…® Juda Josep…®n otarim. Ez…® Josep Jonam…®n otarim. Ez…® Jonam Eliakim…®n otarim.  
\v 31 Ez…® Eliakim Melean otarim. Ez…® Melea Menan otarim. Ez…® Mena Matatan otarim. Ez…® Matata Natan…®n otarim. Ez…® Natan Devit…®n otarim.  
\v 32 Ez…® Devit Jesin otarim. Ez…® Jesi Obet…®n otarim. Ez…® Obet Boas…®n otarim. Ez…® Boas Salmon…®n otarim. Ez…® Salmon Nason…®n otarim.  
\v 33 Ez…® Nason Aminadap…®n otarim. Ez…® Aminadap Atmin…®n otarim. Ez…® Atmin Arnin otarim. Ez…® Arni Hesron…®n otarim. Ez…® Hesron Peres…®n otarim. Ez…® Peres Judan otarim.  
\v 34 Ez…® Juda Jekop…®n otarim. Ez…® Jekop Aisak…®n otarim. Ez…® Aisak Abraham…®n otarim. Ez…® Abraham Teran otarim. Ez…® Tera Nahor…®n otarim.  
\v 35 Ez…® Nahor Seruk…®n otarim. Ez…® Seruk Reun otarim. Ez…® Reu Pelek…®n otarim. Ez…® Pelek Eber…®n otarim. Ez…® Eber Selan otarim.  
\v 36 Ez…® Sela Kainan…®n otarim. Ez…® Kainan Arpaksat…®n otarim. Ez…® Arpaksat Siem…®n otarim. Ez…® Siem Noan otarim. Ez…® Noa Lamek…®n otarim.  
\v 37 Ez…® Lamek Metuselan otarim. Ez…® Metusela Enok…®n otarim. Ez…® Enok Jaret…®n otarim. Ez…® Jaret Mahalalel…®n otarim. Ez…® Mahalalel Kenan…®n otarim.  
\v 38 Ez…® Kenan Enos…®n otarim. Ez…® Enos Set…®n otarim. Ez…® Set Adam…®n otarim. Ez…® Adam God…®n otarim. 
\c 4  
\s1 Satan Iesus gifarasa a gakaghori 
\r (Matyu 4:1-11 ko Mak 1:12-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus, God…®n Duam bar a giz…®vaz…®ma a Jordan…®n d…®pam ategha uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n zui. Ez…®ma God…®n Duam a inigha gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n zui.  
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam…®n 40 pla arueba ko d…®magaribar itima, Satan bizibar a gifari. Iesus dughiar kabar daghetam amezir puvat…®. Ez…®ma dughiar kaba g…®vaz…®ma m…®tiriam an azi. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…®ma Satan kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim, n…® dag…®ar kam m…®kemeght…®ma a bret…®n m…®n otogh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus Satan ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazamiziba daghebara dam…®va dar gavgavim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Satan Iesus inigha danganir bar p…®n itim…®n ghuavanaboghava, egha zuam…®ra nguazir kam…®n nguibaba bar an aka.  
\v 6 Egha Satan kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir kaba nan agharim…®n iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® tina dan…®ngs…® fuegh…®va, a dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n k…® nguibar kabar ganamin gavgavim ko, dar bizir aghuiba n…® dan…®ngam.  
\v 7 Eght…® n…® tevimning ap…®righ nan ziam f…®t…®, bizir kaba bar n…®na.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan Ekiam God, n…® an apengara ik…® an ziamra fam.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…®ma Satan Iesus inighava Jerusalem…®n ghughava a isava God…®n D…®penim p…®n mar anefa.  
\v 10-11 Egha a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòA n…® bagh uan enselbar m…®kemeght…®ma me deraghv…®ra n…®n ganam, egh me uan dafaribar n…® feght…®ma n…® dag…®atam uan dagarim aseghan kogham!‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma n…® guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim, n…® kagh ik…® uab…® ekunigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan Ekiam God a gifar, a gakaghont…®, a n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mangan mark…®.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Satan ifavarir kaba bar Iesus gamigha g…®vagha anetaki. A Iesus ategha ghua dughiar igharazim bagha m…®zuai. 
\ms1 Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n ghua ingangarim gami 
\mr (Sapta 4:14-9:50) 
\s1 Iesus Galilin ghughava magh…®ra uan ingangarim gami 
\r (Matyu 4:12-17 ko Mak 1:14-15) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…®ma Iesus God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n a uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu. Ez…®ma an akam bar mogh…®ra nguibabar ghu.  
\v 15 Egha a God ko m…®geir d…®penibar men sure gamima, me bar an ziam fe. 
\s1 Nasaret…®n itir gumaziba Iesus…®n aghua 
\r (Matyu 13:53-58 ko Mak 6:1-6) 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus Nasaret…®n ghu, a ikiava aghungiz…® nagh…®n. Egha Sabat…®n dughiam…®n a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghu, an arazir a zuraram amim. Egha tugha God…®n Ak…®nafarim d…®ponasava ami.  
\v 17 Ez…® me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaian ak…®nafarir r…®ghizim a gan…®ngi. Ez…®ma Iesus ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir kam onegha, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n api. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18-19 ‚ÄúGod akar aghuim gumazir onganarazibav k…®nasa na ginaba, 
\q2 ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Ekiam…®n Duam nan iti. 
\q1 Egha uaghan akar kam kunasa na amada; 
\q2 akar kalabus…®n itiba ataghraghamim ko gumazir damazir kuraba ua ganamim. 
\q1 Egh os…®mt…®zibar apengan itiba k…® ua me f…®r…®va egh suam, 
\q2 Ekiam gumazamizibagh ifongezir dughiam otogha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 20 Ez…®ma Iesus ak…®nafarim uam a righava, egha a isava ingangarir gumazim ganigha, egha apera. Ez…®ma me bar mogh…®ra God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven pamtem an gari.  
\v 21 Ez…®ma a magh…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ia oraghizim a guizbangram oto!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® me an akabagh ifongeghava n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar akar aghuir a m…®kemezibagh ami, egha me kamagh…®n azara, ‚ÄúKar pura Josep…®n otarimra, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ti akar is…®n zuir kam na m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòDokta n…® uab…® uan m…®karzim ak…®righ!‚Äô Egh e oraghizir bizir n…® Kaperneam…®n amiziba n…® kagh uaghan uan nguibam…®n dar amu.‚Äù\f + \ft (4:23) Dokta uab…® uan m…®karzim ak…®ramin akar m…®ngarim, a kamagh…®n ghu. Gumazim ingangaritam damus…®, a derav…®ra gumazamizibar damazim…®n a damight…®, eght…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an akam…®n ikiam. Luk 4:18-19…®n aven, Iesus God a gan…®ngizir ingangarir ekiabav gei. Kamagh…®n, Iesus ghaze, gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, me an gant…® a faragh mirakelbar amight…®, me an akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam.\f* 
\p  
\v 24 Egha a m…®g…®a ghuav…®ra ikiava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, men adarazi me baraghan aghua.  
\v 25 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Elaijan dughiam…®n, amuir odiarir bar av…®rim Israel…®n iti. Ez…® amozim izir puvat…®gha ghua azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim ko azenir akuam…®n oto. Ez…® dagheba bar puvat…®zir dughiam bar nguibabar oto.  
\v 26 Ez…® God Israel…®n amizitam bagha Elaija amadazir puvat…®. A Sidon…®n danganir aven itir nguibar mam, Sarefet…®n itir amuir odiarim baghav…®ra anemada.  
\v 27 Ez…®ma God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisan dughiam…®n, lepan av…®rim Israel…®n ti. Ez…® God men tav gamiz…®ma a zuegha derazir puvat…®. Ez…® Namanra, God a gamiz…®ma a zuegha dera, a Sirian gumazir mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® gumazir God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven itiba bar bizir kam bareghava men naviba Iesus bagha men isi.  
\v 29 Egha me d…®kavigha, Iesus batoghez…®ma a nguibam ategha azenan ghuz…®ma, me a inigha nguibam itir m…®ghs…®ar avarir konim anekunasa zui.  
\v 30 Ez…® a men tong…®n ghua munagh otogha ghu. 
\s1 Iesus duar kuram gumazir mam dam a batoke 
\r (Mak 1:21-28) 
\p  
\v 31 Egha Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam, Kaperneam…®n ghuaghiri. Egha Sabat…®n dughiam…®n, a gumaziba ko amizibar sure gami.  
\v 32 Egha an akaba gavgavim dar ti. Egha bizir kam bagha me an suren m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraghava d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…®ma gumazir duar kurar itir mam, a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven iti. Egha a pamtem dia kamagh…®n m…®gei,  
\v 34 ‚ÄúIesus, Nasaret…®n gumazim, n…® manmagh…®ra e damuasa ize? N…® e gas…®ghas…®ghasa izi? K…® n…® g…®fo, n…® God amadazimra, n…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir gumazim!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…®ma Iesus an atarava a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® n…®m…®ra ik…®! Egh…®va gumazim ategh…®va azenan iz…®!‚Äù Ez…®ma duar kuram men damazibar gumazim akunigha azenim…®n izava duatam gumazim gat…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® me bar aguaghfagha egha uarira uariv gei. ‚ÄúEei, kar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manam? A m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batoghez…®ma da azenan izi.‚Äù  
\v 37 Ez…®ma an amir bizir kaba, dar m…®g…®r…®g…®am bar nguibabar ghu. 
\s1 Iesus Pitan asamim ak…®riz…®ma a ghuamaghe 
\r (Matyu 8:14-15 ko Mak 1:29-31) 
\p  
\v 38 Egha Iesus God ko m…®geir d…®penim ategha Saimon…®n d…®penim…®n ghu. Ez…® Saimon…®n asamim ariava m…®karzim puv…®ra feima, me an akuravaghasa Iesus…®n azai.  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus amizim…®n m…®n tugha aviraghava akar gavgavim…®n an ar…®mariam batoghez…®ma ar…®mariam ghu. Ez…® amizim zuam…®ra d…®kavighava me bagha daghebagh amuava me gan…®di. 
\s1 Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribagh amiz…®, me ua dera 
\r (Matyu 8:16-17 ko Mak 1:32-34) 
\p  
\v 40 Ez…® aruem ghuaghirima, gumazamiziba me gumazir ar…®mariar anabar av…®riba itiba Iesus bagha me inigha ize. Ez…® a vaghvagha uan dafariba me gis…®n ar…®zima me ghuamazi.  
\v 41 Ez…® uaghan a duar kurabagh ami da gumaziba ataghragha azenan iza kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n Otarim!‚Äù Duar kuraba fo, kar God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Iesus m…®k…®man dar anogoroke. 
\s1 Iesus nguibar igharazibagh arui 
\r (Mak 1:35-39) 
\p  
\v 42 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma Iesus danganir gumaziba puvat…®zim…®n ghu. Ez…®ma gumazamiziba a buria ghuava a batogha, egha a me ategh mangan me an anogorosi.  
\v 43 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod akar aghuim kunasa na amada. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® nguibar igharazibar uaghan dar mang…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar aghuim akunam.‚Äù  
\v 44 Egha Judian Distrigh…®n a God ko m…®geir d…®penibar akam akura ghuav…®ra iti. 
\c 5  
\s1 Iesus faragha diazir suren gumaziba 
\r (Matyu 4:18-22 ko Mak 1:16-20) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam…®n Iesus Genesaret…®n d…®par akarer m…®riam…®n tughav itima, gumaziba anekuvagha God…®n akam barasi.\f + \ft (5:1) Ziam ‚ÄúGenesaret,‚Äù a Galilin d…®par akarem…®n ziar mam.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…®ma a d…®par m…®riam…®n garima osiriba isir gumazibar bot…®n pumuning pura iti. Aning…®n ghuaviba uan iver ekiaba rue.  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus bot…®n mam…®n ghuavanabo, Saimon…®n bot. Egha an azaragha ghaze, n…® tong a g…®s…®vaght…®ma a d…®par m…®riam atakigh. Ez…® a bot gaperaghav ikia gumaziba ko amizibar sure gami. 
\p  
\v 4 Egha Iesus m…®kemegha g…®vagha Saimon…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBot g…®s…®vagh d…®par konim…®n mang…®va iver ekiaba osiriba bagh da akunigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Saimon an akam ikara, ‚ÄúEkiam, e d…®magarir kam…®n ingara ghua bar osiritam inizir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® m…®geima kamagh…®n k…® iver ekiaba akunam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® me Iesus m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amigha, egha me osirir bar av…®riba iniz…®ma men iver ekiaba magh…®ra akarasava ami.  
\v 7 Ez…® me uan namakar bot…®n igharazim…®n itiba me gikariz…®ma me iza men akura, egha me iza bot…®n pumuning uaghara aning gaghuiz…®ma aning bar iz…®vagha osemegha magh…®ra d…®pam…®n ghuaghiri. 
\p  
\v 8-10 Ez…®ma Saimon Pita, ko a ko itir darasi, me osirir me inizir kabar ganigha kamagh…®n d…®gavir kuram gami. Saimon…®n roroamning Jems ko Jon, Sebedin otarimning. Aning Saimon ko ingarir gumazimning, aning uaghan d…®gavir kuram gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Saimon kamagh…®n ganigha, tevimning ap…®righa Iesus…®n suemning…®n borogh…®n ir…®. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amim! Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma n…® na ategh mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n Saimon…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n tugh mang…®, n…® gumaziba iniam.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® me uan botba m…®k…®rvegha, d…®par dadarim…®n ghuavanega, egha biziba bar da ategha Iesus…®n g…®n zui. 
\s1 Gumazir lepa itim 
\r (Matyu 8:1-4 ko Mak 1:40-45) 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…®ma Iesus nguibar ekiar mam…®n itima, gumazir mam lepa bar aneg…®riz…®ma, a izava oto. Egha a Iesus…®n apighava ira uan guam nguazim m…®tuaghava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® fuegh…®va n…® na damut…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ua deragham.‚Äù \f + \ft (5:12) N…® akar Matyu 8:2…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus uan agharim isa gumazir kam gat…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ifonge. N…®n m…®karzim zuegh, egh ua deragh.‚Äù Ez…®ma lepa zuam…®ra anetaki. 
\p  
\v 14 Egha Iesus akar gavgavim a gan…®ngi, ‚ÄúTav…®n m…®k…®man mark…®. Egh mang…®, uab…® God…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh, egh Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® uab…® zueghs…® ofa damu. Eght…® gumazamiziba fogh suam, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…®ma Iesus amizir bizir kabar eghaghanim bar mar ghu. Kamagh…®n gumaziba ko amizir av…®rim a baragh…®va men ar…®mariaba ua deraghasa izi.  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus zurara me ataghragha ghua, gumazamiziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia God ko m…®gei. 
\s1 Iesus gumazir soroghafariba am…®razim gamiz…®ma a dera 
\r (Matyu 9:1-8 ko Mak 2:1-12) 
\p  
\v 17 Dughiar mam…®n Iesus gumaziba ko amizibar sure gami. Ez…® Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me Galilin Distrigh ko Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibaba bar, ko Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ikegha izava apiaghav iti. Ez…® Ekiam…®n gavgavim uaghan iti, kamagh…®n Iesus men ar…®mariabar amut…®ma da deragham.  
\v 18 Ez…® gumazir maba gumazir soroghafariba aremezim inighava akuriam gat…®ghava a inigha d…®penim…®n aven mang…® Iesus…®n guam…®n aner…®ghasa.  
\v 19 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar av…®raseme. Ez…®ma me aven mangan iburaghava d…®penir siriam…®n ghuavanabogha d…®penir siriam…®n torim gamigha benibar an akuriam dafagha, n…®m…®ra anetaghrazima a ghuaghira gumazamizir okuruam…®n tong…®n Iesus…®n guam…®n anet…®. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…®ma Iesus men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar ganigha, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNamakam, n…®n arazir kuraba k…® da g…®n amada.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…®ma Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba magh…®ra uan navir averiabar aven n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúKar gumazir manam God…®n danganim iniasa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami? Gumazir k…®nitam arazir kuraba g…®n amangam, o puvat…®? God uab…®ra.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha, egha a men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha bizir kabar uan navir averiabar dagh n…®ghn…®si?  
\v 23 K…® akar manam m…®k…®mam? Pura gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada. Egh uaghan gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham suam, n…® d…®kavigh mang…®, egh ua deragh.  
\v 24 K…® arazir kam damight…®ma, ia ganigh fogham, Gumazibar Otarim a nguazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù Egha kamagh…®n gumazir soroghafariba am…®razim m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…®ma a zuam…®ra men damazibar d…®kavigha, ir…®ghav ikezir akuriam inigha uan nguibam…®n ghuava God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 26 Ez…® me bar d…®gavir kuram gamigha God…®n ziam fe. Egha agorogem me giz…®vaz…® me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir bar igharagha garibar gari.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus uab…®n g…®n mangasa Livain dei 
\r (Matyu 9:9-13 ko Mak 2:13-17) 
\p  
\v 27 Bizir kabar g…®n Iesus ghua garima gavman…®n dag…®aba isir gumazir mam, an ziam Livai, a uan dag…®aba isir d…®penim gaperaghav iti. Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù\f + \ft (5:27) Ziar kam Livai, ti Matyun ziar igharazir mam. N…® Matyu 9:9…®n gan.\f* 
\v 28 Ez…® Livai d…®kavighava, biziba bar da ateghava an g…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 29 Egha Livai isar ekiam Iesus bagha uan d…®penim…®n aneru. Ez…®ma dag…®aba isir gumazir av…®rim ko gumazir maba sara izava me koma api.  
\v 30 Ez…®ma Farisiba koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumazibar adarasi, me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mabar Iesus…®n suren gumazibagh ami, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba koma api?‚Äù\f + \ft (5:30) N…® Matyu 9:11…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúAr…®mariaba puvat…®zir gumaziba, dokta bagha zuir puvat…®. Gumazir ar…®mariaba itibara, me dokta bagha zui.  
\v 32 K…® God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumaziba bagha izezir puvat…®. K…®, gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar d…®m…®va men navibagh iraghasa, k…® ize.‚Äù 
\s1 Dagheba ataghrazir arazim…®n azangs…®zim 
\r (Matyu 9:14-17 ko Mak 2:18-22) 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon…®n suren gumaziba, me zurara God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrasi. Ez…® Farisin suren gumaziba uakan. Ez…® n…®nanaba apa mamagh…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir amuim…®n ikiamim, a ia ko ik…®t…®, ia a bagha izezir gumazibav k…®mt…® me dagheba ategham, o puvat…®gham?  
\v 35 Egh dughiam iz…®t…®ma gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim me me dama a inigh mang…®t…®ma, eght…® dughiar kabar me dagheba ategham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Egha Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam…®n me geghari, ‚ÄúGumazitam…®n korotiar ghurim torim an ik…®t…®ma, a korotiar igiatam abigh, egh inir av…®zir kam is…®, korotiar ghurim a dukuagh a isaman mark…®. A kamagh…®n damuva, korotiar igiar kam ar…®zigham. Egh uaghan inir av…®zir igiar korotiar ghurim dukuagha isamizim, korotiar ghurim…®n m…®n ganan kogham.  
\v 37 Ez…® gumazitam wain…®n igiam isava wain…®n m…®sevir ghuribagh ingezir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n damight…®ma, wain…®n igiam wain…®n m…®sevir ghuriba a bight…®ma wain ir…®t…®ma wain…®n m…®seviba ikuvigham.  
\v 38 A kamagh…®n damuan kogham. Wain…®n igiam, wain…®n m…®sevir igiam gingam.\f + \ft (5:38) N…® Matyu 9:17…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\v 39 Ez…®ma gumazim wain…®n ghurim amegha, egha igiam gifongezir pu. Egh…®va a kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGhurim a dera.‚Äô‚Äù 
\c 6  
\s1 Iesus uab…® Sabat…®n Ekiam 
\r (Matyu 12:1-8 ko Mak 2:23-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Sabat…®n mam, Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko raiz…®n m…®n garir dagher mam wit, an kuriabagh aruava, egha an suren gumaziba wit…®n asiziba ghuaza da kuava, dar tuziba api.  
\v 2 Ez…® Farisin maba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim sua arazir Sabat…®n amir puvat…®zim gami.‚Äù \f + \ft (6:2) N…® Matyu 12:2…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus me ikara, ‚ÄúIa ti Devit fom…®ra amizir arazim…®n eghaghanim…®n ganizir puvat…®? Devit dughiar kam…®n uan adarazi ko m…®tiriam men azi,  
\v 4 ez…®ma Devit God…®n Averpenim…®n aven ghua me ofa damuasa at…®zir bret inigha uan adarazi ko me aneme. Egha e fo, me bret…®n kam raman kogham.‚Äù  
\v 5 Egha Iesus me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEz…® Gumazibar Otarim a Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Ekiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Sabat…®n dughiam…®n dafarir ekonezir gumazim gamiz…® a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 12:9-14 ko Mak 3:1-6) 
\p  
\v 6 Sabat…®n dughiar igharazim Iesus God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghugha men sure gami, ez…® gumazir mam men tong…®n iti. An dafarir guvim ekonegha an areme.  
\v 7 Farisin maba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba an arazitam…®n apigh akam agasasa, me bar derav…®ra an gari. Me kamagh sua, a Sabat…®n ar…®mariaba batogham, o?  
\v 8 Kamagh…®n Iesus men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha egha gumazir dafarir ekonezim m…®gei, ‚ÄúD…®kavigh men damazibar tught…®ma me bar n…®n ganika.‚Äù Ez…® a d…®kavigha tughav iti.  
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ian azai, arazir manam Sabat…®n dera? E arazir aghuim damuam, o arazir kuram damuam, o gumazim…®n akuragham, o a gas…®ghas…®gham?‚Äù  
\v 10 Egha a bar men ganigha egha gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim onegh.‚Äù Ez…® a uan dafarim onez…®ma an dafarim bar mogh…®ra ua dera.  
\v 11 Ez…®ma me atara egha uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, e arazir tizitam…®n Iesus damuam. 
\s1 Iesus 12 pla aposelba m…®sefe 
\r (Matyu 10:1-4 ko Mak 3:13-19) 
\p  
\v 12 Dughiar kabar dughiar mam Iesus God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®am…®n m…®n ghuavanabogha, egha God ko m…®geima am…®nim a bang…®n tira.  
\v 13 Am…®nim tiraz…®ma, a uab…®n g…®n aruir gumazibar diaz…® me a da ghuez…®ma ez…® a 12 pla me am…®sefe. Egha magh…®ra ziam aposelba me gat…®:  
\v 14 Saimon (Iesus Pita a gat…®), ko an dozim Andru, Jems, Jon, Filip, Bartolomyu,  
\v 15 Matyu, Tomas, Jems Alfius…®n otarim, Saimon, a Selotiabar gumazir mam,  
\v 16 Judas Jems…®n otarim, ko Judas Iskariot, gumazir g…®n Iesus isava apanibagh an…®ngizim. 
\s1 Iesus ar…®mariaba batosi 
\r (Matyu 4:24-25 ko Mak 3:7-12) 
\p  
\v 17-18 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko ghuaghirava danganir zarim…®n tu. An g…®n aruir gumazamizir av…®rim iti. Ez…® maburan av…®rir Jerusalem ko Tair koma Saidon…®n Ongarir dadarim, ko Judian aven itiba, bar Iesus baragh…®va men ar…®mariaba ghuamaghasa me ize. Ez…® gumazamizir duar kuraba as…®ghas…®ghiziba, da me ataki.  
\v 19 Ez…® gavgavim Iesus ategha azenan ghua gumaziba ko amiziba bar me gami me ghuamazi, ez…® kamagh sua me bar mogh…®ra Iesus…®n m…®karzim…®n suighasa. 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, onganarazibagh amiba me bar akongegh. 
\r (Matyu 5:1-12) 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Iesus uan g…®n aruir gumazibar garava kamagh m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa biziba puvat…®ziba, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven iti, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh. 
\q1  
\v 21 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®tiriam aziba, ia g…®n iz…®vagham, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh. 
\q1 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n azi darasi, ia g…®n akam, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh. 
\q1  
\v 22 Me ian gant…® ia Gumazibar Otarim…®n g…®n mang…®t…®ma, 
\q2 men naviba ia bagh bar kuvigham. 
\q2 Egh me ia batogh…®va paz ia damuva ian ziabagh as…®ghas…®gham. 
\q3 Bizir kaba ia bativt…® ian naviba deragh. 
\q2  
\v 23 Men afeziaba fom…®ra kamagh…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibagh amiz…® mogh…®n me ia gami. 
\q2 Ia uaghan ivezir ekiam God…®n nguibam…®n a iniam. 
\q3 Kamagh…®n dughiar kam otoght…®, ia bar akongegh…®va agoroguem sara p…®n uari akun. 
\q1  
\v 24 Ia bizir av…®riba itiba, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia navir aghuim inigha g…®fa, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ia ikuvigham. 
\q1  
\v 25 Ia dagher av…®riba itiba, ia g…®n m…®tiriam ian agham, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ia ikuvigham. 
\q1 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ati darasi, ia g…®n arang…®va temeribagh ruam, 
\q2 kamagh…®n ia ikuvigham. 
\q1  
\v 26 Gumaziba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibar ia damut…®, 
\q2 eght…® ia bar kuvigham. 
\q3 Fom…®ra men inaziba akam inigha izir gumazir ifariba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuiba me gami. 
\q2 Kamagh…®ra gumaziba me bar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuiba ia damut…®, 
\q3 kamagh…®n ia bar ikuvigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Arazir apanibagh ifongeziba 
\r (Matyu 5:38-48) 
\p  
\v 27 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEz…® ian na barazir darasi, k…® ia m…®gei, ia uan apanibagh ifongegh, arazir aghuiba ia gifongezir puvat…®ziba me damu,  
\v 28 m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuiba ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kuraba ia gamibar amu, paza ia gamiba ia me bagh afeziam ko m…®k…®m.  
\v 29 Eght…® tav ian koviatam apezeght…®, ia koviar vuem sara a dan…®ngi. Eght…® tav ian korotiar azenan itim inight…®ma, uaghan aven itir korotiam sara an taki.  
\v 30 Egh te biziba bagha ian azangs…®si, ia da me dan…®ng. Egh te ian biziba ini, ua da bagh m…®k…®m…®va me dam ada inian mark…®.  
\v 31 Ia arazir aghuir me ia damuamin ia ifongeziba, ia arazir kabara me damu. 
\p  
\v 32 ‚ÄúEgh ia, ia gifongezibara fuegh…®va, egh manmagh…®n arazir aghuitam damigham? Arazir kurabagh amiba uaghan kamagh…®ram ami. Me me gifongez…® daraziragh ifonge.  
\v 33 Egh ia deraghv…®ra deragha ia gamir darazigh amua, egha kamagh…®n arazir aghuir manam ia gami? Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba uaghan kamagh…®ram ami.  
\v 34 Egh ia pura uan biziba me dan…®ng, egh n…®ghn…®gh suam, me ti da ikarvagham, egh manmagh…®n arazir aghuitam damigham? Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba me uaghan ghaze, k…® gumazir kurar igharazim uan biziba a dan…®ngt…®, eght…® a g…®n ua da ikarvagham.  
\v 35 Ia uan apanibagh ifuegh…®va, derav…®ra me damuva, egh…®va biziba pura me dan…®ng…®va, uamategh da ikarvaziba in…®s…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ez…® God arazir aghuiba gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba koma gumazir a m…®nabir puvat…®zibagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, g…®n ian ivezim bar ekeveght…®ma, ia God…®n bar p…®n itim…®n boribar m…®n ikiam.  
\v 36 Afeziam…®n apangkuvim…®n m…®rara, ia apangkuvim ik…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Igharaz darazir araziba tuis…®ghan mark…® 
\r (Matyu 7:1-5) 
\p  
\v 37 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod ia tuis…®gh ian kuraghan koghs…®, kamagh…®n ia munen araziba tuis…®ghan mark…® suam, men araziba ikufi. Ivezir kuram an…®ngan mark…®, eght…® God ivezir kuram ia danigan kogham. Ia men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaght…®, God ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.  
\v 38 Ia dan…®ng, eght…® God ia dan…®ngam. M…®nem bar derav…®ra iz…®vaght…®ma, a is…® m…®kebabar amang…®va agasavkon, eght…® a ir…® mag…®r…® ian apozibar inibagh iram. God bizir iz…®v…®r…®ziba, ia gan…®di mogh…®n ia igharaz darazir an…®ng.‚Äù  
\v 39 Iesus uaghan akar is…®n zuir mam sara me m…®keme; ‚ÄúGumazir damazir kuram damazir kurar igharazitam…®n suiragh mangam, o? Aning v…®rara mozim…®n mag…®r…®gham.  
\v 40 Suren gumazim, uan tisa gafirazir puvat…®. Ez…® suren gumazir bar derav…®ra uan sure a g…®vazim, a uan tisan m…®rara ghu.  
\v 41 Tizim bagha, m…®nezir bar muziarim n…®n aveghbuam…®n damazim…®n itima, n…® ti an gara egha temer ararir ekiar n…®n damazim…®n itim…®n garir puvat…®?  
\v 42 Ter ararir ekiam n…®n damazim…®n ik…®t…®, n…® manmagh uan aveghbuam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòAveghbuam, k…® n…®n damazim…®n itir m…®nezim asigham?‚Äô N…® bar ifari! N…® faraghv…®ra ter ararir n…®n damazim…®n itim asigh, egh deragh gan…®va m…®nezir n…®n aveghbuam…®n damazim…®n itim asigh.‚Äù 
\s1 Temem ko an ov…®zim 
\r (Matyu 7:16-20 ko 12:33-35) 
\p  
\v 43 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTemer aghuitam ov…®zir kuram batezir puvat…®, kamagh…®ra temer kuratam ov…®zir aghuim batezir puvat…®.  
\v 44 Gumaziba temer ov…®zibar gara fogha ghaze, temer aghuim o temer kuram. Me figh…®n ov…®ziba temer ataghatarim…®n da kuari pu. Egha me wain…®n ov…®ziba temer ataghatarir muziarir kuram…®n da isir puvat…®.  
\v 45 Gumazim…®n navir averiam…®n ikezir biziba, an akatorim, dav gei. Kamagh…®n gumazir aghuim bizir aghuiba an navir averiam…®n ikegha otivaghiri. Ez…® gumazir kuram bizir kuraba an navir averiam…®n ikegha otivaghiri.‚Äù 
\s1 D…®penim…®n ingarir gumazir d…®k…®riam ko onganim 
\r (Matyu 7:24-27) 
\p  
\v 46 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha ‚ÄòEkiam‚Äô na gar…®si, egh a k…® m…®geir biziba dagh amir puvat…®?  
\v 47 Tina iza nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragha dagh ami, k…® an araziba ian akagham.  
\v 48 A mati gumazim d…®penim…®n ingara, an okora bar v…®n ghuaghira dag…®am gis…®n ter ak…®niba kuni. D…®penir kam me bar derav…®ram an ingari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma aperiam…®n dughiam d…®pam d…®penir kam…®n aven ghuz…®ma a nuighnuizir puvat…®.  
\v 49 Ez…® gumazir nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragha dar g…®n zui puvat…®zim, mati gumazim uan d…®penim nguazir k…®nim ko bizitam gis…®n an ingarizir puvat…®. Eght…® dughiar d…®pam izamim a d…®penir kam b…®raght…®ma, a ir…®gh bar kuvigham.‚Äù 
\c 7  
\s1 M…®dorozir gumazir dapanim…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim 
\r (Matyu 8:5-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus bizir kabar gumaziba ko amizibav kemegha g…®vagha, Kaperneam…®n aven zui.  
\v 2 Ez…® 100 plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanir ekiam iti. An ingangarir gumazir a bar ifongezim, ariava aremeghasava ami.  
\v 3 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir dapanir kam Iesus amizir biziba baregha Judan gumazir aruar dapanir maba a baghava da amangi.  
\v 4-5 Ez…® me Iesus bagha izeghava pamtem kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam en gumazamiziba bar me gifonge. Egha e bagha God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n ingari. Kamagh…®n gumazir kam an akurvazim baghava ami, n…® an akuragh.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus tagha me ko zui. A ghua d…®penim…®n borogh…®n otoz…®, ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir dapanir ekiam uan namakaba amangiz…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® gumazir aghuir manam, n…® nan d…®penim…®n aven izam? Ez…® n…® iz…® nan d…®penim…®n averiam…®n izan mark…®. N…® paz uab…® damuan mark…®.  
\v 7-8 Kamagh…®n k…® uab…® n…® bagh m…®g…®r…®g…®am inigh izan kogham. K…® uab…® m…®dorozir gumazir mabar apengan iti, egha uab…® mabar garima, da nan apengan iti. Ez…® k…® me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa mang…®,‚Äô eght…® me mangam. O, k…® me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa iz…®.‚Äô Eght…® me izam. Egh k…® uan ingangarir gumazir mam m…®k…®m suam, n…® ingangarir kam damu, eght…® an a damuam. Egha k…® fo, n…® m…®k…®mt…®, nan ingangarir gumazim ua deragham.‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n oregha, d…®gavir kuram gamigha, egha raghr…®gha gumazamizir a g…®n zuibav gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, k…® Israel…®n aven kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazitam…®n ganizir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…®ma gumazir amadaziba uamategha d…®penim…®n ghuava ingangarir gumazim…®n garima a dera. 
\s1 Amuir odiarim…®n otarim ua d…®kafi 
\p  
\v 11 Egha g…®n Iesus nguibar ziam Nain…®n zui. Ez…® an suren gumaziba ko gumazir av…®rim an g…®n zui.  
\v 12 Egha a nguibar kam…®n tiar akar ekiar kam…®n borogh…®n ghua garima, gumazir maba gumazir kuam gisaghpugha nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha azenan izi. Gumazir aremezir kamnagh, an amizir pam aremezim…®n otarir vam…®ra. Ez…® nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir gumazir av…®rim amuir odiarir kam ko iti.  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus an gara egha bar an apangkuvigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® arangan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus rogh…®ra ghua gumaziba isaghpughav itir kez…®n suira. Ez…® a gisaghpughav itir gumaziba vorogh…®ra m…®tivighav iti. Ez…® a kamagh…®n gumazir igiam a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir igiam, k…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kafigh.‚Äù  
\v 15 Ez…®ma gumazir aremezim d…®kavigha magh…®ra m…®geima, ez…® Iesus uam a isava an amebam gan…®ngi.  
\v 16 Ez…®ma me kamagh…®n ganigha bar d…®gavir kuram gamigha, God…®n ziam fa, egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazir ekiar mam en tong…®n oto.‚Äù Egha me ghaze, ‚ÄúGod uan gumaziba ko amizibar akurvaghasa ize.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…®ma Iesus amizir bizir kam…®n eghaghanim bar Judian Distrigh ko an borogh…®n itir nguibaba sara ghu. 
\s1 Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, Jon, a Iesus bagha azangs…®si 
\r (Matyu 11:2-19) 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, an suren gumaziba bizir kabar gun bar a m…®keme. Ez…® a uan suren gumazir pumuning…®n diaghava,  
\v 19 egha Ekiam Iesus…®n azangs…®ghasava aning amada, ‚ÄúTi n…®rara, gumazir God faragha amangasa m…®kemezim? O, e ti ua gumazir igharazitam m…®zuamam?‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazimning Iesus bagha izegha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim n…®n azangs…®ghasa ga amada, ‚ÄòTi n…®rara, gumazir God faragha amangasa m…®kemezim? O, e ti ua gumazir igharazitam m…®zuamam?‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kamnaghra Iesus gumazamizir ar…®mariaba itiba gamuav…®ra itima, me ua dera. Ez…® a duar kuraba batosi, egha gumazir damazir kurar av…®rim, a me gamima, me ua gari.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Iesus Jon…®n abuir gumazimning…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúGua uamategh mang…® bizir gua ganigha oraghizibar gun Jon…®n m…®kemegh! ‚ÄòGumazir damazir okav…®r…®ziba ua gari, ez…® gumazir suer am…®r…®ziba uam arui. Ez…® gumazir lepa itiba ua zuegha dera, ez…® gumazir kuarir orazir puvat…®ziba uam orasi. Ez…® ovengezir gumaziba ua d…®kavima, ez…® gumazir onganarazibagh amiba akar aghuim barasi.‚Äô\f + \ft (7:22) N…® Matyu 11:5…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\v 23 Gumazir nan ganigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®v…®ra ik…®, eght…® an navir averiam deraght…® a bar akuegham!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Jon…®n abuir gumazimning uamategha ghuz…®ma, ez…® Iesus magh…®ra Jon…®n gun gumaziba ko amizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tizim…®n ganasa gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghue? Ia am…®nim vair ghurunim…®n ganasa ghuez ti?  
\v 25 Ti puvat…®, ez…® ia tizim…®n ganasa ghue? Gumazir kurukazir aghuibagh amizim? Ti puvat…®, gumazir korotiar ivezir ekiaba itiba aghua egha bizir aghuiba men m…®karzibar itima, me atrivibar d…®penibar iti.  
\v 26 Ez…® ia tizim…®n ganasa ghue? Ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n ganasa? Are. K…® ia m…®gei, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam Jon, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharaziba bar dagh afira.  
\v 27 Gumazir kam baghav…®ra God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa oragh. K…® uan abuir gumazim amadaght…®ma, a faragh mang…®va n…® bagh tuavim ak…®ram.‚Äô  
\v 28 K…® ia m…®gei, Jon nguazim…®n itir gumaziba bar me gafira, ez…® tina borim…®n m…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven iti, a bar Jon gafira.‚Äù  
\v 29 (Jon gumazamizir av…®riba ruava egha magh…®ra dag…®aba isir gumaziba sara rue. Kamagh…®n me Iesus…®n akam baregha, egha fo God…®n arazim, a bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 30 Ez…® Farisiba koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me Jon…®n rurim inizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n me ak…®rim ragha God men akazir tuavir aghuim gasara.) 
\p  
\v 31 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEgh k…® gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®n itibar arazibav k…®ms…®va, egha akar is…®n zuir manam m…®k…®mam? Me manmagh…®ra gari?  
\v 32 Me boribar m…®n gara biziba amadir danganibar apiav ikia uarir dei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòE ia bagha marvibagh ivima, ia ighian aghua. 
\q2 Ez…® e ongerakar am…®r…®zibagh amima, ia azir puvat…®.‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 33 Egha Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim iza dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba apir puvat…®z…®, ez…® ia ghaze, ‚ÄòDuar kuraba a gapasa.‚Äô  
\v 34 Ez…® Gumazibar Otarim izava dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba api. Ez…® ia ghaze, ‚ÄòIa gan, a gumazir puv daghem ko wain…®n d…®pam apim. Egha a dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, a men roroabagh amua me ko iti.‚Äô  
\v 35 Ez…® gumazamizir God…®n fofozim iniziba, me gara fo, God…®n fofozim a guizbang…®ra bizim.‚Äù 
\s1 Amizir arazir kurabagh amir mam Iesus…®n dagarimning rue 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Farisin gumazir mam uab…® ko damasava Iesus bagha m…®keme. Ez…® kamagh…®n an a ko daperagh damasa an d…®penim…®n ghu.  
\v 37 Ez…® amizir arazir kurabagh amua nguibar kam…®n itim orazi, Iesus Farisin d…®penim…®n ikiava api. Ez…® amizir kam borer mughuriar aghuim zuim itir alabastan ingarizir m…®sevim inigha izi.  
\v 38 Egha a Iesus…®n dagarimning g…®n tughav ikia azima, ez…® an teriba Iesus…®n dagarimning giri. Ez…® a uan dapanir ar…®zim…®n an dagarimning adizava an dagarimning…®n torava egha borem an dagarimning ginge.  
\v 39 Ez…® Farisin an diazim bizir kam…®n ganigha uab…®ra uab…® m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam a God…®n akam inigha izir guizbang…®ra gumazim a fogh suam, kar amizir manam an suisi, kar amizir arazir kurabagh amim.‚Äù  
\v 40 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúSaimon k…® n…® m…®k…®mamin bizir mam iti.‚Äù Ez…® Saimon ghaze, ‚ÄúTisa, na m…®kemegh.‚Äù  
\v 41 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir pumuning gumazir mam da dag…®aba pura ada ini egh aning g…®n a da ikarvagham. Ez…® mav a da 500…®n dag…®aba ini, ez…® mav a da 50 plan dag…®aba ini.  
\v 42 Ez…® aning uaghara an dag…®aba ikarvaghan ibura. Ez…® a aning ikarvaghamin dag…®ar kaba g…®n amada. Ez…® n…® n…®ghn…®gh, aning…®n tina gumazir kam bar a gifuegham?‚Äù  
\v 43 Ez…® Saimon an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir dag…®ar av…®riba inigha ua da ikarvaghan iburazim.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® deragha m…®gei.‚Äù  
\v 44 Egha a ragha amizim…®n garava kamagh…®n Saimon…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® amizir kam…®n gari? K…® n…®n d…®penim…®n izez…®ma, n…® nan dagarimning bagha d…®patam na gan…®ngizir puvat…®. Ez…® amizim uan temeribar nan dagarimining ruegha, egha uan dapanir ar…®zim…®n aned…®si.  
\v 45 Ez…® n…® nan torezir puvat…®. Ez…® amizir kam dughiar k…® aven izezim…®n a nan dagarimning…®n tora mamagh…®ra ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n.  
\v 46 Ez…® n…® borem nan dapanim gingezir puvat…®. Ez…® amizir kam a borer mughuriar aghuim inigha nan dagarimning ginge.  
\v 47 A bar na gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, God an arazir kurar av…®riba bar da g…®n amada. K…® ia m…®gei, tina God an arazir kurar muziarim g…®n amadaght…®, a kamagh…®n na gifongezir arazir muziarim ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 48 Ez…®ma Iesus amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n arazir kuraba, k…® da g…®n amada.‚Äù  
\v 49 Ez…® gumazir a ko ikiava apiba kamagh…®n oregha, magh…®ra uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúKar gumazir manam uaghan arazir kuraba g…®n amadi?‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n akura. Eght…® n…® navir am…®r…®zim…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\c 8  
\s1 Amizir maba Iesus…®n g…®n arui 
\p  
\v 1 Egha bizir kabar g…®n, Iesus, nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar dozibagh arui, egha God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam kuri. Ez…®ma an gumazir 12 pla uaghan an g…®n arui.  
\v 2 Ez…® amizir maba uaghan, me fom…®ra Iesus men ar…®mariaba ko duar kuraba batoke: Maria, me Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim a gar…®si, Iesus fom…®ra a gamiz…®ma, 7 plan duar kuraba aneteghava azenim…®n ize,  
\v 3 Joana ko Susana koma amizir av…®rir igharaziba uaghan a ko arui. (Joana, a Kusan amuim, a Herot…®n d…®penir averiam…®n garir gumazir dapanim.) Amizir kaba uan bizibar Iesus ko an suren gumazibar akurvasi. 
\s1 Iesus akar is…®n zuir gumazir wit…®n ov…®ziba akurir akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 13:1-9 ko Mak 4:1-9) 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim uan nguibaba ategha Iesus bagha izava uari akuvaz…®ma, an akar is…®n zuir kam m…®gei:  
\v 5 ‚ÄúAzenir gumazir mam ghuava raiz…®n m…®n garir daghem, wit, an ov…®ziba inigha uan azenim…®n da akuri. Egha a da akura zuima, maba tuavim gira ghuz…®ma gumaziba da d…®ke. Ez…® kuarazir p…®n itiba izaghira bar da ame.  
\v 6 Ez…®ma maba dag…®aba itir danganibagh iregha afuangi. Ez…® d…®paba nguazim…®n puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…® wit…®n kaba ua m…®s…®ngigha ariagh…®re.  
\v 7 Ez…®ma wit…®n ov…®zir mabanang benir ataghataribar torim gire, egha benir ataghatariba sara aghuima da da ikiaghar…®ki.  
\v 8 Ez…®ma mabanang nguazir aghuim giregha, aghua dagher bar av…®riba iti, kamagh…®n da vaghvagha 100pla bar m…®sevegha iti.‚Äù An akar is…®n zuir kam me m…®kemegha, a pamtem kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus manmagh sua akar is…®n zuibagh ami 
\r (Matyu 13:10-17 ko Mak 4:10-12) 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim baghava an azara.  
\v 10 Ez…®ma a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGod fofozim ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar mogomeba dagh fo. Ez…® igharaz darazi k…® akar is…®n zuibara me m…®gei, eght…®ma gariba me gan fofoghan kogham, ez…® uaghan oraziba me akar m…®ngaribagh foghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Wit…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim 
\r (Matyu 13:18-23 ko Mak 4:13-20) 
\p  
\v 11 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim. Wit…®n ov…®zim a God…®n akam.  
\v 12 Ez…® wit…®n ov…®zir tuavim gireziba mati gumazamizir God…®n akam baraghiziba, me a baraghiz…® ez…® Satan iza men navir averiabar God…®n akam batoke, eght…®ma me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God damuan koght…® God ua me inian kogham.  
\v 13 Ez…®ma dag…®aba itir danganibagh irezir wit…®n ov…®ziba mati gumazamizir akam baregha bar akongeziba, egha me biba itir puvat…®. Me dughiar otevim…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti, ez…®ma os…®mt…®zibar dughiam me God ataki.  
\v 14 Ez…®ma wit…®n ov…®zir benir ataghataribar tong…®n ireziba mati gumazamizir akam baraghizibar m…®n ti. Egh me deragha tuavim…®n zuima nivaf…®zibar agoroger os…®mt…®ziba, ko dag…®ar n…®ghn…®zir os…®mt…®ziba, koma nguazir kam…®n bizir ganganir agorogeba, me isima me dar aven ikia egha m…®sevir puvat…®.  
\v 15 Ez…®ma wit…®n ov…®zir nguazir aghuim gireziba mati, gumazamizir akar aghuim baraghiziba, me a inigha uan navir averiabagh at…®gha adar suira egha gavgavigha ikia, men dagher aghuiba otifi.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazitam avir angazangarim m…®nem…®n aven anet…®zir puvat…® 
\r (Mak 4:21-25) 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam lam gaborogha m…®nem…®n aven a modogha egha a isa dakozim…®n apengan anefazir puvat…®. Egh an a is…®va dakozim gis…®rarama anefagham, eght…®ma tina aven iz…®va angazangarim…®n ganam.  
\v 17 Kamagh…®ra mogomer biziba da g…®n azenan otivigham. Eght…® bizir amigha aveziba da uaghan g…®n azenan otivigham.  
\v 18 Ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia deraghv…®ra akar kam baragh. Gumazitam God…®n akabagh foght…®, God uan akabar fofozir igharaziba a dan…®ngam, eght…® a God…®n akar av…®ribagh fogham. Eght…® God…®n akabagh foghan aghuazir gumazim, an fofozir muziarim God a dama inigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Tinara a Iesus…®n amebam koma doziba? 
\r (Matyu 12:46-50 ko Mak 3:31-35) 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus…®n amebam ko doziba an ganasa izi. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar anekufa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an borogh…®ra mangan ibura.  
\v 20 Ez…® mav Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®n amebam ko doziba muna azenan tuivighav ikia, egha n…®n ganasa.‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…®ma an an akam ikara, ‚ÄúTina God…®n akam baragha an g…®n zui, me nan amebam ko doziba.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus m…®geima am…®nir ekiam areme 
\r (Matyu 8:23-27 ko Mak 4:35-41) 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® dughiar mam Iesus uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAria e d…®pam…®n vong…®n mangam.‚Äù Eghava me bot…®n ghuavanega egha vong…®n zui.  
\v 23 Egha me ghuava, Iesus pariam an azima an akui. Ez…®ma am…®nir ekiam amozim sara d…®pam…®n oto, ez…® d…®pam men bot bar a giz…®fa. Kamagh…®n me os…®mt…®zir ekiam…®n aven iti.  
\v 24 Egha suren gumaziba ghuava a gaghuragha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, n…® d…®kafigh! E ovengam!‚Äù Ez…® a d…®kavighava am…®nim ko d…®par puv…®ra ingarim akar gavgavim…®n aning m…®gei. Ez…®ma am…®nim ko d…®pam aremegha am…®raghav…®ra iti.  
\v 25 Ez…®ma a uan suren gumaziba kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim managh iti?‚Äù Ez…® me atiatia, n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amuava, uarira uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, a tina? A m…®geima am…®nim ko d…®pam, an akam barasi.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus gumazir mam…®n duar kuraba batoke 
\r (Matyu 8:28-34 ko Mak 5:1-20) 
\p  
\v 26 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko bot…®n ghuava Gerasan Distrigh…®n otifi, Galilin d…®pam…®n vong…®n.  
\v 27 Egha Iesus bot ategha azenan izima, nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir gumazir duar kuraba apazazim a bato. A fom…®ra iniba itir puvat…®ghava d…®penibar aven itir puvat…®, a gumazir ovengezibar dag…®ar mozir toribar aven iti.  
\v 28-29 Egha duar kurar kam dughiar av…®ribar an suigha anekurima a daghiri. Egha uaghan an dafariba ko sueba me senbar da ike, egha an garir gumaziba an borogh…®ra ikiava an gari, ez…® duar kurar kam a gamima a uan senba aghorava ara ghua gumaziba itir puvat…®z…® nagh…®n iti. Ez…® Iesus duar kuram batogha ghaze, n…® gumazim ategh azenan iz…®. Ez…® a Iesus…®n apigha, arava Iesus…®n dagaribar apengan ir…®gha pamtem d…®a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim na damuasa, Iesus, God…®n bar p…®n itim…®n otarim? Ez…® k…® n…®n azangs…®si n…® arazir kuratam na damuam mark…®!‚Äù  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus an azara, ‚ÄúN…®n ziam tina?‚Äù Duar kurar av…®riba an aven ghuz. Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAv…®riba.‚Äù  
\v 31 Ez…®ma duar kuraba Iesus kamagh…®n a gaghorav…®ra iti, ‚ÄúN…® e batoegh e amadaght…®ma e torir m…®ngariba puvat…®zir kam…®n mangan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 32 Dughiar kam dar b…®zir ekiar maba m…®ghs…®ar m…®riam…®n rogh…®ra ikiava api. Ez…®ma duar kuraba Iesus gakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® en amamangat…®ght…®ma e mang…® dar munabar aven mangeka.‚Äù Ez…®ma a me ataghiz…®ma me zui.  
\v 33 Ez…® duar kuraba gumazim ateghava azenan izeghava dabar aven ghue. Ez…®ma dar b…®zir kam ara ghua davarir kuram giraghuegha d…®pam amegha ariagh…®re.  
\v 34 Ez…®ma dabar garir gumaziba garima bizir kaba otiviz…®ma, me ara ghuava nguibar ekiam…®n bizir kabar gun m…®geima nguibar azenan rogh…®ra itiba sarama orasi.  
\v 35 Ez…®ma gumazamiziba ganasa izi, bizir tizimrama oto? Egha me Iesus bagha iza, egha garima, gumazir duar kuraba ategha azenan izezim, a Iesus…®n dagarim…®n m…®n aperaghav iti. A korotiaba aghuiz…®ma an n…®ghn…®zimra uam an izes. Kamagh…®n me atiatingi.  
\v 36 Ez…® ikia bizir kam…®n ganizir darasi gumaziba ko amizibagh eghari, me eghara ghaze, Iesus duar kuraba apazazir gumazim gamiz…® a ua dera.  
\v 37 Ez…® gumazamizir Gerasan Distrigh…®n itiba puv…®ra atiatiava, egha Iesus…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄúN…® e ategh danganir igharazim…®n mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® a bot…®n ghuavanabogha uamategha zui. 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…®ma duar kuraba ataghizir gumazir kam Iesus…®n azangs…®gha uaghan an g…®n mangasa, ez…® Iesus anemadagha, a m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 39 ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®, egh God n…® gamizir biziba bar me m…®k…®m.‚Äù Ez…® gumazim uamategha ghua egha nguibam garuava Iesus a gamizir biziba bar dar gun m…®gei. 
\s1 Iesus aremezir guivir mam gamiz…®ma a ua d…®kafi Egha amizir an korotiam…®n suirazim gamiz…®ma a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 9:18-26 ko Mak 5:21-43) 
\p  
\v 40 Egha Iesus uamategha Galilin d…®pam…®n vong…®n izez…®ma gumazamiziba a iz…® me bativasa me a bagha oragha a m…®zua iti.  
\v 41-42 Ez…®ma gumazir mam, an ziam Jairus, a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n gumazir dapanim. An guivir vam…®ra an azenir 12 plan borogh…®ra ghugha, aremeghasava ami. Kamagh…®n a iza Iesus…®n dagaribar apengan ir…®. Egha uan d…®penim…®n mangasa Iesus gakaghori. Ez…® Iesus ghuav…®ra itima maburan av…®rim bar anekuvagha anedughadusi.\f + \ft (8:42) An guivir vam…®ra, a 12 plan azenibar borogh…®ra ghu, kamagh…®n amiz…® e ghaze, an azenir 12 plan borogh…®ra ghu.\f* 
\v 43 Ez…®ma amizir 12 plan azenim…®n ghuzim batir ar…®mariam itir mam, gumazitam a damight…®ma a deraghan kogham. Ez…® a men tong…®n zui.  
\v 44 Egha a Iesus…®n g…®n izava an korotiar av…®zim…®n suira, egha zuam…®ra an ghuzir ar…®mariam dutugha ghu.  
\v 45 Ez…® Iesus azara, ‚ÄúTina nan suira?‚Äù Ez…® me bar uarir tiragha Pita ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, gumazamiziba bar n…® akuvagha n…® adughadusi.‚Äù  
\v 46 Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n fo, gumazim nan suiraz…®ma gavgavim na ategha azenan ghu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 47 Ez…®ma amizim uab…®ra uab…®n gara fo, a modoghan kogham. Eghava atiatim sara iza Iesus…®n dagaribar apengan ir…®. Egha a gumaziba ko amizibar damazibar m…®g…®a ghaze, nan ar…®mariam g…®vaghasa, k…® Iesus…®n korotiam…®n suira, ez…® nan ar…®mariam zuam…®ra g…®fa.  
\v 48 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…® gamiz…®ma n…® dera. Navir am…®r…®zim…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 49 Egha Iesus m…®g…®av…®ra itima, gumazir mam God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n garir gumazir dapanim, Jairus…®n d…®penim…®n ikegha, Jairus bagha izi. Egha a Jairus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n guivim areme. Eght…® n…® tisa ua ingangarim a dan…®ngan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n oregha, Jairus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®. Pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® eght…®ma n…®n guivim ua deragham.‚Äù  
\v 51 Eghava a Jairus…®n d…®penim…®n otogha, egha a ua tav…®n amamangat…®ght…®ma an an g…®n aven mangan an aghua, kerara a ko aven mangam, Pita, Jon, ko Jems koma guivim…®n amebam koma afeziam.  
\v 52 Dughiar kam gumazamiziba bar uan evaribav m…®sogha azia iti. Ez…® Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAzir akam atakigh. Guivim aremez…® puvat…®. An akui.‚Äù  
\v 53 Me fo, guivim aremez…®, kamagh…®n me an ingaravati.  
\v 54 Ez…® Iesus guivim…®n dafarim…®n suiragha egha m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan borim, n…® d…®kafigh!‚Äù  
\v 55 Ez…®ma an duam uamategha izez…®ma a zuam…®ra d…®kavigha tu. Ez…®ma Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa daghetam a dan…®ngigh.‚Äù  
\v 56 Ez…® an amebam koma afeziam bar aguaghfa. Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a aning ab…®ra, bizir otozir kam gua gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…®. 
\c 9  
\s1 Iesus 12 pla gumaziba amangi 
\r (Matyu 10:5-15 ko Mak 6:7-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus 12 plan suren gumazibar diaghava me akuvaghava, egha gavgavim koma gavgavir duar kuraba batogham koma ar…®mariaba ag…®vamim sara me gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 Egha me amadagha ghaze, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam kunigh, egh gumazibar ar…®mariabar ak…®rt…®ma me ua deragham.  
\v 3 Egha a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®s…®va bizitam inian mark…®, m…®tariba, dagheba, dag…®aba, koma siot…®n ia g…®n daghuamin tam inian mark…®.  
\v 4 Eght…® d…®penir ia aven zuir manam, anar…®ra ik…®, mang…®va nguibar kam ategh mang…®.  
\v 5 Eght…®ma gumaziba ia g…®fueghan koght…®ma, dughiar ia men nguibam ataghraghamim, ia uan dagaribar m…®neziba ap…®sigh, eght…®ma me fogh suam, arazir me amizir kam, a derazir pu.‚Äù\f + \ft (9:5) Judabar arazim kara, n…® me baraghan koght…®ma, me n…®n sagh, uan dagarir asuaba m…®neziba ap…®zigh…®va n…® ategh igharagh mangam. Ez…® en arazim kamak…®n, k…® n…® m…®k…®mt…® n…® na baraghan koght…®, k…® apem ap…®righ uan tuavim gighuvagh, egh suam, k…® n…®n sagham.\f* 
\v 6 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba nguibabar ghuava, akar aghuim akurava egha ar…®mariar gumazibar k…®rima me ghuamazi. 
\s1 Herot foghasa, Iesus a tinara 
\r (Matyu 14:1-2 ko Mak 6:14-16) 
\p  
\v 7-8 Ez…® Herot, gavman…®n dapanim, a bizir Iesus amiba baraghiz…®ma da ghuav…®ra iti. A fo, marazi ghaze, Jon aremegha ua d…®kafi, ez…® marazi ghaze, Elaija oto, maba ghaze, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam fom…®ra ikegha aremegha ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Herot bar n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 9 Egha Herot kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Jon…®n f…®rim atu. Tina, bizir kabagh amima me dar gun m…®gei?‚Äù Egha a Iesus…®n ganasa. 
\s1 Iesus dagheba 5,000…®n gumazibagh an…®di 
\r (Matyu 14:13-21 ko Mak 6:30-44 ko Jon 6:1-13) 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n aposelba uamategha izeghava, bizir me amizibar gun a m…®gei. Ez…®ma a me inigha me uarira nguibar mam an ziam Betsaidan ghue.  
\v 11 Ez…® gumazir b…®zir av…®rim a g…®foghava egha an g…®n zui. Ez…® Iesus me g…®fueghava me isava, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n gun me m…®g…®ava, eghava gumaziba ko amizibar ar…®mariabar ak…®ri.  
\v 12 Bar guarat…®zim…®n Iesus…®n 12 plan aposelba a bagha izeghava a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti. Egh, n…® gumazamiziba me amadaght…® me mang…® danganir kam…®n itir nguibaba ko nguibar rogh…®ra itibar mang…®va, egh dagheba koma dakuamin danganiba buri.‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa uari daghetaba me dan…®ngigh.‚Äù Ez…®ma me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar bret…®n rubuzir 5 pla koma osirir pumuningra iti. Egh e ua mang…® gumazir av…®rir kam bagh dagher tabagh ivezeghan koght…®, dagheba bar otevegham.‚Äù  
\v 14 (Dughiar kam gumazibar d…®bobonim, 5,000 borogh…®n ghu.) Ez…®ma Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa me m…®k…®mt…®ma me 5 pla ten, 5 pla ten…®n, okuruabar dapigh…®r…®.‚Äù  
\v 15 Suren gumaziba kamagh…®ram amiz…®ma, gumazamiziba bar apia.  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus bret…®n rubuzir 5 pla koma osirir pumuning inigha kogha overiam…®n garava Afeziar Ekiam m…®nabagha, egha bretba ko osirimning ap…®righava gumaziba ko amizibar an…®ngasa uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngiz…® me me gan…®di.  
\v 17 Ez…®ma gumazamizir kaba bar amegha, naviba bar iz…®fa. Ez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba, dagher nar me ataghiziba, me da inigha 12 plan ak…®rabagh aghuiz…®ma da bar izefe. 
\s1 Pita Iesus…®n gun m…®g…®a ghaze, a tina 
\r (Matyu 16:13-19 ko Mak 8:27-29) 
\p  
\v 18 Dughiar mam…®n Iesus uab…®ra Afeziam ko m…®geima, an suren gumaziba a ko itima, ez…®ma a men azara, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba tina na gar…®si?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…®ma me an akam ikara, ‚ÄúMarazi ghaze, n…® Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, ez…® marazi ghaze, n…® Elaija, ez…®ma marazi ghaze, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir fom…®ra itir mam aremegha ua d…®kafi.‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…®ma Iesus azara, ‚ÄúEz…® ia? Ia uari ghaze k…® tina?‚Äù Ez…® Pita an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, an aremegh ua d…®kavigham 
\r (Matyu 16:20-28 ko Mak 8:30-9:1) 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim suren gumaziba gan…®ga ghaze, ia nan gun tav m…®k…®man mark…®.  
\v 22 Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazibar Otarim bar m…®zazir ekiaba koma os…®mt…®ziba iniam. Eght…®ma gumazir aruaba, koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me an aghuagh…®va a m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham. Egh dughiar m…®kezim…®n a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Egha a bar mogh…®ra me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam nan g…®n iz…®s…®, a ifongezir biziba g…®n amadagh uan temer ighuvim zurara a gisaghpugh nan g…®n iz…®.  
\v 24 Gumazir manam uan ik…®r…®m…®rim suiraghs…® n…®ghn…®ght…®, an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®vagham. Eght…® gumazir manam na bagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ategh…®va, uan ik…®r…®m…®rim iniam.  
\v 25 Gumazitam nguazim…®n itir biziba bar da iniva, egh a g…®n oveght…®, bizir kaba manmagh…®n an akuragham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 26 Tina nan ziam ko nan akar aghuim…®n gun m…®k…®man aghums…®ght…® g…®n Gumazibar Otarim uan afeziam…®n borogh…®n ikegh…®va an God…®n damazim…®n zuezir enselba koma God…®n angazangarim sara izighir…®va, uaghan men aghums…®gham.  
\v 27 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia kagh tuivighav itir darasi, ian tarazi oveghan kogham. Ia ik…®v…®ra ik…® gant…®ma, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam otogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n m…®karzim igharagha gari 
\r (Matyu 17:1-13 ko Mak 9:2-13) 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus bizir kabav kemez…®, 8 plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, a g…®n Pita, Jon, koma Jems inigha me a ko ghua, God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n p…®n ghu.  
\v 29 Ez…®ma a God ko m…®geima, an guam…®n ganganim ragha igharagha gari. Ez…®ma an korotiaba bar ghurghurighava egha on…®marim…®n m…®n taghtasi.  
\v 30 Gumazir pumuning, Moses koma Elaija,  
\v 31 aning Afeziar Ekiam…®n angazangarim…®n aven ikiava, egha Iesus ko uariv gei. Me Iesus nguazir kam ataghragham koma bizir a Jerusalem…®n damuamin bizibav gei.  
\v 32 Pita uan namakamning ko dakuasava ami, egha me oseghava, egha Iesus…®n angazangarir gavgavim…®n ganigha egha uaghan gumazir pumuning…®n gari, aning a ko tughav iti.\f + \ft (9:32) Bizir otozir kam ti d…®magarim…®n oto.\f* 
\v 33 Ez…®ma gumazimning ane ataghrazima Pita kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, bar deragha e kagh iti! E averpenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ingaram. N…® bagh tam, Moses bagh tam, egh Elaija bagh tam.‚Äù (Pita akar kam m…®g…®ava a uab…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar a m…®kemezir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.) 
\p  
\v 34 A m…®g…®av…®ra itima, ghuariar mam otogha me avara, ez…®ma me ghuariam…®n aven ghuava bar atiatingi.  
\v 35 Ez…® tiarir mam ghuariam…®m tong…®n otogha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar nan Otarim, k…® a ginaba. Ia anar…®ram oragh!‚Äù  
\v 36 Ez…®ma tiarir kam m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma me Iesus…®n garima a uab…®ra iti. Ez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bizir me ganizim me an gun gumazitam m…®kemezir puvat…®. 
\s1 Otarir mam, duar kuram a gapazaz…®ma Iesus a batoke 
\r (Matyu 17:14-23 ko Mak 9:14-32) 
\p  
\v 37 Egha me am…®m…®zaragh…®n m…®ghs…®am ategha izaghirima gumazamizir av…®rim a bato.  
\v 38 Ez…® gumazir mam men torim…®n ikia dei, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® n…® gakaghori, nan otarir bar vam…®ra iti, kamagh…®n n…® an ganigh.  
\v 39 Duar kuram an aven ikiava a gamima a zuam…®ra ara dei. Egha anekurima a nguazim gira puv n…®si. Ez…®ma pupuviba an akam…®n otifi. Duar kurar kam dughiar mabar an ikiava bar pazava a gamuava, egha anetaghrazir puvat…®.  
\v 40 K…® a batoghasa n…®n suren gumazibagh akaghori. Ez…® me a damuan ibura.‚Äù  
\v 41 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n ikara, ‚ÄúOio, k…® bar am…®ra, ia dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba, ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba puvat…®, ian araziba koma n…®ghn…®ziba bar derazir puvat…®. K…® dughiabar manmagh…®n ia ko ikiava egha ian os…®mt…®ziba ateri? N…® uan otarim inigh kagh iz…®.‚Äù  
\v 42 Ez…®ma otarim izav…®ra itima, duar kuram an ekuniz…®ma a nguazim gir…®ghava uam aguava egha puv n…®si. Ez…®ma Iesus duar kuram a batoghez…®ma a borim ataghiz…®ma a dera. Ez…® Iesus a isava uam an afeziam gan…®ngi.  
\v 43 Ez…®ma gumazamiziba bar God…®n gavgavim…®n ganigha egha d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\p Me bar puv Iesus amizir bizibagh n…®ghn…®zima, a uan suren gumazibav gei,  
\v 44 ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra na baraght…®ma, k…® bizitam ia m…®k…®masa. Me Gumazibar Otarim is…®va gumazir kurabar dafarim dar…®gham.‚Äù  
\v 45 Ez…®ma me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®. A men modo, ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me a g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha an azangs…®ghan atiatingi. 
\s1 Tina ziar ekiam iniam 
\r (Matyu 18:1-5 ko Mak 9:33-37) 
\p  
\v 46 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba uarira uari adoghadogha egha ghaze, tina men dapanim…®n ikiam.  
\v 47 Me m…®geima, Iesus men n…®ghn…®zibagh fo, egha a borim iniz…®ma an an m…®n tughav iti.  
\v 48 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam na g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh borir dozir kamagh garitam inigh an akuragham, kamagh…®n a na inigha nan akurvasi. Egha tina nan akurvasi, a nan Afeziar na amadazim…®n akurvasi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, tina ian tong…®n ziam puvat…®, a ziar ekiam iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Tina ian apanim gamir pu, a iananav 
\r (Mak 9:38-40) 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…® Jon Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e garima gumazir mam duar kurabar n…®n ziam…®n da batosi. E fo, a en mav puvat…®, ez…®ma e an anogorosi.‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina ian apanim gamir puvat…®, a iananav. Eght…®, ia an anogoroghan mark…®.‚Äù 
\ms1 Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Jerusalem…®n zui 
\mr (Sapta 9:51-19:28) 
\s1 Samarian gumaziba Iesus nguibam…®n izan me an aghua 
\p  
\v 51 Ez…®ma God Iesus inigh uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanangamin dughiam rogh…®ra izez…®ma, Iesus Jerusalem…®n mangasa n…®ghn…®zim gamigha iti.  
\v 52 Egha uan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gumazir maba amangiz…®ma me akam inigha faragha ghue. Me Samarian nguibar mam…®n a bagha bizibar ak…®rasa ghue.  
\v 53 Ez…®ma gumazamizir nguibar kam…®n itiba fo, Iesus Jerusalem…®n zui, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me Iesus inian aghua.\f + \ft (9:53) Samarian gumazamiziba, me Gerasen M…®ghs…®am…®n uari akuva God bagha ofa gamua God…®n ziam fe. Ez…® Judaba Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ghuava ofa gamua God…®n ziam fe. N…® Jon 4:20…®n gan. Samarian gumazamiziba ghaze, Judaba derav…®ra Ekiam…®n ziam fer arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, me dughiar kam Iesus…®n akurvaghan aghua.\f* 
\v 54 Ez…®ma suren gumazimning, Jems koma Jon bizir kabar ganigha, egha an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® ifueght…®ma e God…®n Nguibam…®n itir avim bagh diaght…®ma a izighr…®va gumazibar isigham.‚Äù  
\v 55 Ez…®ma Iesus raghava aning…®n atari.  
\v 56 Egha me nguibar igharazim…®n ghue. 
\s1 Iesus…®n g…®n mangamin ivezim 
\r (Matyu 8:19-22) 
\p  
\v 57 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko tuavim…®n zuima, gumazir mam Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguibar manam n…® an zui, k…® n…®n g…®n mangam.‚Äù  
\v 58 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAfiar atiaba nguazir toribar itima, kuaraziba m…®konibar iti, ez…® Gumazibar Otarim danganir dakuamiba puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 59 Egha Iesus gumazir igharazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…®ma gumazim an akam ikara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® faragh na amamangat…®ght…®ma, k…® mang…® uan afeziam mozim dafaka.‚Äù  
\v 60 Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMark…®. Gumazir ovengeziba uari uan gumazir kuabar af…®. Egh n…® mang…®va God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam akunam.‚Äù  
\v 61 Ez…®ma ua gumazir mam Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® n…®n g…®n mangam. Egh n…® faragh nan amamangat…®ght…®ma k…® mang…®va uan adarazir ganika.‚Äù  
\v 62 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúTav itazim kuazagh egh a g…®n ganan kogh…®va, a God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ingaran kogham.‚Äù 
\c 10  
\s1 Iesus 72 plan gumaziba amangiz…® me ghua an ingangarim gami 
\p  
\v 1 Egha bizir kabar g…®n Ekiam 72 plan gumazir igharaziba m…®sevegha egha pumuning pumuning faragh nguibar ekiaba koma danganir a mangasa n…®ghn…®zibar me amadi.\f + \ft (10:1) Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir Iesus amadazibar d…®bobonim, a 72 puvat…®. Me ghaze, men d…®bobonim 70ra. Eght…® namba 70, a Luk 10:1…®n ik…®t…®, eght…® Luk 10:17 uaghan, namba 70 an ik…®.\f* 
\v 2 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDagher bar av…®rim anigha g…®vagha azenim…®n iti. Ez…® ingangarir gumazir da iniamin av…®riba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, ia azenir kam…®n ghuavim…®n azangs…®ght…®, a ingangarir gumaziba amangt…®ma, me an azenim…®n mang…®, dagheba iniam.  
\v 3 Ia mang…®! K…® sipsip…®n nguziba afiar atiabar torim…®n iti mogh…®n ia amadaz…® ia zui.  
\v 4 Egh…®va dag…®aba azuir m…®tarim ko beghiam ko dagarir asuaba inian mark…®. Eght…® gumazitam tuavim…®n ia batogh…®va dughiam ia dan…®ngt…®, ia ikaraghan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúEgh…®va ia d…®penitam…®n aven mang…® egh faragh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, navir am…®r…®zim ia ko iti.  
\v 6 Eght…® gumazir navir am…®r…®zim kagh ik…®t…®, ia navir am…®r…®zim an ik…®. puvat…®ght…®ma ian navir am…®r…®zim ua ia bagh izegham.  
\v 7 E fo, ingangarir gumazim uan ivezim isi, kamagh…®n ia d…®penir kam…®n aven ik…®, dagheba ko d…®par tizir me ia gan…®diba, ia dar am…®. Egh…®va d…®penir mam…®n ikegh mam…®n mangan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh…®va ia nguibar ekiam…®n aven mang…®ght…®ma me ia inigh, egh me tizim ia gan…®ngi, ia puram anem…®.  
\v 9 Egh ia ar…®mariar itibar amight…®ma da deraght…®ma, kamagh…®n me m…®kemegh, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize.  
\v 10-11 Egh ia nguibar ekiatam…®n aven mang…®t…®ma, me ia inighan koght…®ma, tuavir dozibar aven mang…® egh m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIan nguibar ekiam…®n nguaziba en dagaribar poghez…®, e a da d…®si, eght…® ia kamagh…®n ganigh fogh suam, ia amizir arazir kam, a derazir puvat…®.‚Äô  
\v 12 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir nguibar kam iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Sodom…®n nguibam iniamim gafiragham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazamizir navim girazir puvat…®ziba bar kuvigham 
\r (Matyu 11:20-24) 
\p  
\v 13 Egha Iesus ghua m…®g…®a uan 72 plan gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Korasin…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba, iavzika! Ia kuram iniam. Ia Betsaidan nguibam…®n itir adarazi, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Gumazitam Tair…®n nguibam ko Saidon…®n nguibam…®n ghua, mirakel…®n k…® amiziba men tong…®n dagh amighai, Tair ko Saidon…®n itir darazi ti fom…®ra navibagh iragha, egha azir adiariba aghuigha, averenim gapiava agura, egha uan arazir kam…®n uari akakagha ghaze, me uan arazir kuraba ataki.  
\v 14 God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir ia iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Tair ko Saidon iniamim gafiragham.  
\v 15 Ez…® ia Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n itir darazi, ia ghaze, ia uari fegh God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam, a? Bar puvat…®, God ia akunight…® ia Hel…®n avim…®n mag…®ram. 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúTina ia barasi uaghan na barasi, tina ia barazir puvat…® a uaghan na barazir puvat…®. Egha tina na barazir puvat…®, a nan Afeziar na amadazim uaghan a barazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\s1 72 plan gumaziba uamatenge 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…®ma 72 plan gumaziba ua iza bar akuegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, e n…®n ziam d…®borima duar kuraba en akabar m…®rara zui.‚Äù  
\v 18 Ez…® a me ikara, ‚ÄúK…® Satan…®n garima a ira on…®marim…®n m…®n God…®n nguibam…®n tagha g…®fa.  
\v 19 Ez…®ma k…® gavgavim ia ganigha g…®fa eght…® ia kuruziba ko tuighiakaba gis…®n daruva da d…®k…®va, egh uan apanibar gavgavim a g…®vagham. Eght…® me bizir kuratam ia damuan iburagham.  
\v 20 Eght…® duar kuraba ian akam m…®rara ghuzir bizim gakongan mark…®. Ian ziaba God…®n Nguibam…®n aven osirizir bizim bagh…®va akong.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus bar akuegha uan Afeziam m…®nabi 
\r (Matyu 11:25-27 ko 13:16-17) 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kamra, God…®n Duam Iesus gamima a bar akongeghava m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, n…® nguazim ko overiam gativazir Ekiam! N…® fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir gumaziba bizir kaba men modo, egha boribar m…®n itir gumazibar aka. Kamagh…®n k…® n…® m…®naba. Guizbang…®ra Afeziam, n…® uan ifongiam…®n kamagh…®n ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Egha Iesus ua kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan Afeziam biziba bar da isa nan dafarim gat…®. Ez…® gumazitam Otarim g…®fozir puvat…®. Afeziam uab…®ra a g…®fo. Egha tav Afeziam g…®fozir puvat…®. Otarim uab…®ra, koma gumazir Otarim ifuegha Afeziam isava men akaziba, merara Afeziam g…®fo.‚Äù  
\v 23-24 Egha a ragha uan suren gumazibar gara kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir av…®riba ko gumazir aghuir av…®riba, me ia dat…®r…®gh…®n garir bizibar ganamin ifongiar bar ekiam ikia, me dar ganizir puvat…®. Egha ia dat…®r…®gh…®n orazir akar kaba, me da baraghan ifongiar bar ekiam ikia, me tam baraghizir puvat…®. Ez…® ia, ian damaziba dar gari, kamagh…®n ia bar akongegh!‚Äù 
\s1 Samarian gumazim Judan mav…®n akurazir eghaghanim, Iesus a gami 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® dughiar mam Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir mam d…®kavighava Iesus gifarasa purama an azara, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® manmagh…®n damigh…®va zurazurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam?‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúAkar manam Moses Osirizir Arazim…®n akam…®n aven iti? N…® manmagh…®n an gari?‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® an a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uan God, n…®n Ekiam, bar a gifongegh, egh n…® uan navir averiam ko uan duam ko uaghan bar uan gavgavim ko uaghan bar uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n, uan God gifongegh. Egh uaghan, n…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongegh.‚Äù  
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® bar deragha m…®gei. N…® mamagh…®ra damigh, zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® a gumazibar damazim…®n deraghasa, kamagh…®n a Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® tina nan namakaba?‚Äù  
\v 30 Ez…®ma Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazim Jerusalem ateghava Jerikon uaghira, egha gumazir kuraba batoz…®ma, me an korotiaba sueghava, puv…®ram a m…®sueghava are, egha anetaghiz…®ma a m…®k…®r…®gha ir…®ghav iti.  
\v 31 Ez…®ma ofa gamir gumazim tuavir kamra uaghira egha an gara a gitagha zui.  
\v 32 Kamagh…®ra Livain gumazim uaghan iza danganir kamnaghra an gara a gitagha zui.  
\v 33 Ez…®ma Samarian gumazir mam, iza danganir gumazir kam itimra izava, an apighava bar an apangkufi.  
\v 34 Egha an a bagha ghua wain ko borem an duaba ruegha egha da nomke. Egha a gumazim isa uan donki gis…®n anefagha, egha a inigha ghua daguir d…®penir mam…®n aven ghugha egha derav…®ram a gami.  
\v 35 Egha am…®m…®zaraghan a dag…®ar pumuning d…®penir ghuavim ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄòDeragh an gan eght…® dughiar k…® uamategham, k…® iz…® bizir tizir n…® uam a gamiziba k…® da ikaragham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 36 ‚ÄúEz…® n…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezir kabar manam gumazir kuraba m…®soghezir gumazim…®n namakam?‚Äù  
\v 37 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazim a ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir an apangkuvizim.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®va kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Maria ko Martan d…®penim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 38 Eghava Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko tuavim…®n izav…®ra ikiava egha nguibam…®n oto. Ez…® amizir mam, an ziam Marta an diaz…®ma an an d…®penim…®n ghu.  
\v 39 Ez…® an afumim…®n ziam Maria. A Iesus…®n dagarim…®n borogh…®ra aperaghav ikiava a barazima a m…®gei.  
\v 40 Ez…® Marta ingangarir av…®rim an n…®ghn…®zim…®n izi, ez…® an os…®mt…®zim sara dagher me damamibagh ami. Egha a Iesus bagha iza egha an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, nan afumim na ataghiz…®ma k…® uab…®ra ingangaribagh ami, ez…® n…® na g…®n…®ghn…®si, o? A m…®kemeght…®ma a nan akuragh!‚Äù  
\v 41 Ez…® Ekiam a ikara, ‚ÄúMarta, Marta, n…® bizir av…®ribagh n…®ghn…®gha egha da bagha muriam n…® d…®ghori.  
\v 42 N…® bizir vam…®ra bagh n…®ghn…®gh. Maria a bizir aghuimra m…®sefe. Ez…® bizir kam gumazitam a dama a inigham kogham.‚Äù 
\c 11  
\s1 Iesus God ko m…®geir arazibar men sure gami 
\r (Matyu 6:9-15 ko 7:7-11) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam Iesus danganir mam…®n ikia God ko m…®gei. Egha a g…®vaz…®ma, an suren gumazir mam a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® God ko m…®geir arazibar en sure damu, mati Jon uan suren gumazibar sure gamiz…® mogh…®n.‚Äù  
\v 2 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® God ko m…®k…®m…®va, kamagh…®n m…®k…®m: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòEn Afeziam, n…®n ziam bar zue, ez…® arazir kuraba an saghon iti. 
\q2 Eght…® Dughiar N…® Bizibagh Ativamim, a iz…®. 
\q1  
\v 3 N…® dughiaba meng en dagheba vaghvagh e dan…®ng, 
\q2 dughiar zurara apir dagheba e dan…®ngigh. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ez…® tina arazir kurabar e gami, e men arazir kuraba g…®n amadi. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh. 
\q1 Egh e ateght…®, e os…®mt…®zibar aven ik…®t…® bizitam en navim b…®raght…®ma, 
\q2 e arazir kuratam damighan kogham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 5-6 Ez…®ma Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIan tong…®n gumazitam namakatam ik…®va, egha d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n a bagh mang…®va, egh kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòNamakam, n…® daghetaba nan akuragh. Nan akar gumazim tuavim…®n iza na batoz…®, k…® a dan…®ngamin dagheba puvat…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúEght…®, gumazir d…®penim…®n aven itim kamagh…®n an akam ikaragham, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarim na dan…®ngan mark…®. K…® tiar akam asaragha g…®fa, egha uan boriba koma akui. Kamagh…®n k…® d…®kavigh…®va bizitam n…® dan…®ngan kogham.‚Äô  
\v 8 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, d…®penir ghuavim d…®kavigh…®va uan namakam puvat…®zir biziba bar a dan…®ngam. A bizir kaba uan namakam dan…®ngan ifongezir pu, egha an a gan…®ngi. An namakam a d…®mv…®ra ikian, an aghuagha egha d…®kavigha iza bizir a bar ifongeziba a gan…®ngi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God ko m…®k…®m, egh biziba bagh an azang, eght…® a da is…® ia dan…®ngam. Egh ia biziba bagh ruiva, ia da bativam. Egh ia tiam gafughafught…®, God ia bagh tiam kuigham.  
\v 10 Gumazir God…®n azaiba, me biziba isi. Ez…® gumazir biziba bagha ruim, da batifi. Eght…® gumazir itiam gafughagham, God a bagh akuigham. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúEgh ian boritam uan afeziam osiriba bagha an azangs…®ght…®ma, eght…® a kuruzitam a danigam, o?  
\v 12 Egh borim tuarir aroriam bagh uan afeziam…®n azangs…®ght…®ma, a tuighakam a danigam, o?  
\v 13 Ia afeziar arazir kurabagh amiba, ia zurara bizir bar aghuiba uan boribagh an…®di. Egha ia kamagh deraghv…®ra fogh, guizbang…®ra ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim bar akueghv…®ra uan Duam is…® gumazir a ko m…®geibar an…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Me ghaze, Iesus duar kuram ko ingari 
\r (Matyu 12:22-30 ko Mak 3:20-27) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus duar kurar gumazim gamima a m…®geir puvat…®zim a batoke. Ez…® duar kuram anetaghiz…®, gumazir m…®geir puvat…®zim dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®gei. Ez…®ma gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gami.  
\v 15 Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúA Belsebul…®n gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batosi, a duar kurabar gumazir dapanim.‚Äù\f + \ft (11:15) Satan…®n ziar mamra kara, Belsebul.\f* 
\v 16 Ez…® marazi Iesus basamasa egha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n gavgavim…®n mirakel…®n arazitam damight…®, an overiam…®n ikegh izighr…®t…®, e an ganigh fogham.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha, egha me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKantrin tam…®n gumaziba uari tuiragh uari uariv sogh…®va egh men dabirabim ikuvigham. Eght…® d…®penir vam…®ran itir darazi uariv sogh, egh uari abigh egh men dabirabim ikuvigham.  
\v 18 Ia ghaze, k…® ti Satan…®n gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batosi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ian azaragha ghaze, Satan uan adarazi ko uari abigh uariv sogh, egh me manmagh…®n tugh gavgavigh bizibar ganamin gavgavim ikiam?  
\v 19 Ia ghaze, k…® Belsebul da gavgavim isa duar kuraba batosi. Ez…® kamagh…®n, tina ian adarazir akurvazima, me duar kuraba batosi? Ian adarazi amir araziba, darara ian akagha ghaze, ia paza na m…®gei.  
\v 20 Eght…® k…® God…®n gavgavim inigh…®va duar kuraba batoght…®, eght…® bizir kam ian akaght…®, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam ia batogha g…®fa.  
\v 21 Eght…® gumazir gavgavitam m…®dorozir biziba bar da inigh egh uan d…®penim bagh gant…® an biziba bar deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 22 Eght…® gumazitam bar gavgavigh a gafiragh a ko uaning m…®sogh, egh a gafiragh, egh an m…®dorozir bizir a gami a gavgavigha ikia m…®soziba inigh, mang…® da tuiragh a da is…® gumazir igharazibar an…®ngam.  
\v 23 Tina nan namakam puvat…®, a nan apanim. Ez…® gumazim nan akuragha gumazamiziba akumakuir puvat…®, gumazir kam men g…®nt…®zima me tintinibar zui.‚Äù 
\s1 Duar kuram uamategha ize 
\r (Matyu 12:43-45) 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúDuar ikuratam gumazitam ategha d…®paba puvat…®zir danganibar arua ikiamin danganiba buri, egha a tam batozir puvat…®gha, egha uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® uamategh faragha ikezir d…®penim…®n mangam.‚Äô  
\v 25 Egha a uamategha ghua garima, me d…®penim aviz…®, a bar zuez…®ma an itir biziba bar deragha iti.  
\v 26 Egh duar kurar kam mang…®, 7 plan duar kurar a gafiragha arazir kurabagh amiba, men aku izam. Egh me mang…®, d…®penir kam…®n ikiam. Gumazir kam faragha paza ike, egh a dat…®r…®gh…®n bar pazav…®ra ikiam, eght…® an dabirabim a faragha ikezir dabirabim bar a gafiragh bar ikuvigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir manaba bar akuegham? 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus bizir kabav g…®av…®ra itima, amizim gumazamizibar torim…®n ikia d…®a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizir kam n…® bategha oteba n…® gan…®di, a bar akongegh.‚Äù  
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúEz…® tina nan Afeziam…®n akam baragha egha an g…®n zui, a bar akongegh.‚Äù 
\s1 Mirakel…®n azangs…®zim 
\r (Matyu 12:38-42 ko Mak 8:12) 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…®ma gumazamiziba otiva izav…®ra itima, Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba bar ikufi. Me mirakel…®n arazir k…® damight…® me ganigh foghamim bagha azangs…®si. Eght…® k…® arazitam me danigan kogham. God Jona gamizir arazim…®n m…®n, me arazir kam…®n ganam.  
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jona nguibar ekiam, Niniven gumazamiziba arazim men aka, ez…® kamagh…®ra Gumazibar Otarim dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba arazim men akagham.  
\v 31 Fom…®ra Seban Amizir Atrivim…®n nguazir kam…®n saghon ikegha Solomon…®n fofozir aghuim…®n akaba baraghasa ize. Ez…® gumazir mam bar Solomon gafiragha ian tong…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Gumazamiziba God…®n Kotiam…®n Tuivamin Dughiam…®n, Seban Amizir Atrivim tugh dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizibar arazir kurabar gun m…®k…®mam.  
\v 32 Eght…® God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, Nineven gumazamiziba d…®kavigh ian arazir kurabar gun m…®k…®mam. Ia fo, Nineven adarazi Jona akunizir akam baregha navibagh ira. Ez…® Gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n ian tong…®n itir mam, a bar Jona gafira!‚Äù 
\s1 N…®n damazimning m…®karzim…®n angazangarim 
\r (Matyu 5:15 ko 6:22-23) 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam lam gaborogha danganir mogometam…®n a modozir puvat…®, o a isava itarir ekiam…®n aven amadaz…® pu. Puvat…®, anes…® an danganimram anefagham. Eght…® tina aven iz…®, an angazangarim…®n ganam.  
\v 34 Damaziba, da lam…®n m…®n namnam…®n angazangarim…®n m…®n iti. Egha damazim deraz…®, n…®n namnam angazangarim bar a giz…®fa. Eght…® n…®n damazim ikuvight…®ma, n…®n namnam, m…®tatem anevaragham.\f + \ft (11:34) Israelba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, n…®n damazimning angazangarim puvat…®ght…®, me suam n…® akurvazir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 35 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ua bagh derav…®ra gan, angazangarir n…®n itim, m…®tarmem an epazagham.  
\v 36 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, angazangarim bar n…®n m…®karzim giz…®vaght…®, eght…® m…®tarmem tong an epazaghan koght…®, n…®n m…®karzim bar angazangarim…®n ikiam, mati lam…®n angazangarim n…® gisiraz…® mogh…®n.‚Äù 
\s1 Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, arazir kurabagh ami 
\r (Matyu 23:1-36 ko Mak 12:38-40 ko Luk 20:45-47) 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…®ma Iesus m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Farisin mam Iesus ko damasava an gighamiz…®ma, ez…® Iesus an d…®penim…®n aven ghugha dagher dakozim gapera.  
\v 38 Ez…® Farisi garima, Iesus ruezir puvat…®gha a koma api. Ez…® a kamagh…®n ganigha aguaghfa. 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Farisiba, ia kapba ko itariba azenan da rua da zue, ez…® ian aven navir averiaba bar kufi. Ok…®mak…®am koma arazir kuraba, ia dagh ami.  
\v 40 Ia bar gumazir onganiba! God azenan ingarizir biziba, a uaghan aven dar ingari?  
\v 41 Eght…® ia bizir itaribar aven itiba is…®va gumazir onganaraziba me dan…®ng, eght…® biziba bar ian zuegham. 
\p  
\v 42 ‚ÄúIa Farisiba, ia ghaze, ia uan azenibar itir zuravariba tong…®ra da tuiragh, egh akuaba is…® God dan…®ng. Egha ia God…®n arazir aghuim ko a gifongezir arazim ataghrasi. Egha ia arazir kabar amuasa gavgavigh, egh uaghan arazir maba ataghraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia bar kuvigham! 
\p  
\v 43 ‚ÄúIa zurara God ko m…®geir d…®penibar dabirabir danganir aghuariba iniasa bar ifonge. Egha uaghan maket…®n danganiba me dughiaba ia dan…®ngasa, ia bar ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar ikuvigham. 
\p  
\v 44 ‚ÄúIa mati matmatiar me gan foghan koghamibar m…®n iti. Eght…® gumaziba me gis…®n daruam. Egh God…®n damazim…®n zueghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar kuvigham!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 45 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir mam a ikara, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® bizir kabav g…®a, uaghan e gas…®ghas…®si.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 46 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúEz…® ia Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, ia gumazamiziba os…®mt…®ziba me gar…®zima me da ateran ibura. Ez…®ma ia uari, uan dafaribar men akuragh bizitam aterir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar kuvigham!  
\v 47 Ian inazir afeziaba God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghez…®ma me ariagh…®re. Ez…® ia me bagha dag…®ar mozir aghuiba okoregha men aghariba mozibagh ar…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia bar ikuvigham!  
\v 48 Ez…® ia arazir kam gumazibar akakagha ghaze, ian inazir afeziaba amir arazir kam dera. Ez…® me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghez…® da ariagh…®re, ez…® ia me bagha mozibagh ami.  
\v 49 Bizir kam bagha, God…®n fofozim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® me bagh nan akam inigha izir gumaziba koma aposelba amangam, eght…® men tarazi, me me m…®soght…®ma, me ar…®gh…®ram. Eght…®ma igharaziba, me arazir kurabar me damuam!‚Äô  
\v 50 Fom…®ra nguazir kam otozir dughiam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, me me m…®soghez…® me ar…®agh…®ra, ez…® arazir kam iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iti darasi, men ivezim iniam.  
\v 51 Ez…® modorozir arazir kam, an Abel…®n dughiam…®n tugha iza Sekaraian dughiam. Gumazir kam, Sekaraia, me ofan danganim ko God…®n D…®penim…®n t…®zim…®n a m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, arazir kurar kabar ivezim gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n itiba bativam. 
\p  
\v 52 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba God…®n fofozim…®n tiar akam…®n kiba inigha ghue. Ia uari aven ghuezir puvat…®. Egha aven mangamin gumazibar tiar akam ap…®ri.‚Äù  
\v 53 Egha Iesus danganir kam ataghrazima, Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba koma Farisiba, me akar kurabar a m…®gei. Egha azangs…®zir av…®ribar a gami.  
\v 54 Egha an gari, a bizitam paz…®va a m…®kemeght…®ma, me an suigham. 
\c 12  
\s1 Farisibar arazir ifavariba bagh gan 
\r (Matyu 10:26-27) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir bar av…®rim uari akuvaghav ikia uari d…®kab…®ri. Ez…® Iesus magh…®ra uan suren gumaziba faragha dav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh gan. Farisiba mati, yis bret…®n aven ghughava a gamiz…®ma a bar buiz mogh…®n ian aven mang…® ia gas…®ghas…®gham. Kamagh…®ra ifavarir araziba uaghan bar ia gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 2 Bizir tizir mongeziba, da azenim giregham. Akar aven itiba, gumaziba dagh fogham.  
\v 3 Ez…® bizir ia am…®nir b…®rim…®n m…®kemeziba, me aruer angazangarim…®n da baragham. Ez…®ma bizir tizir ia sighsirir akabar uan kuaribagh ar…®gha d…®penir averiabar uariv kemeziba, me d…®penibagh is…®n tuiv dar gun m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazim Godram atiating 
\r (Matyu 10:28-31) 
\p  
\v 4 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan namakaba, k…® ia m…®gei, ia gumazir namnar k…®nibav sozibar atiatingan mark…®. Egh me g…®n ua bizitam damighan kogham.  
\v 5 Ez…®, tinarama ia an atiatingam, k…® ian akagham. Ia God…®n atiating, a ian namnam gas…®ghasigh…®va, g…®n ia inigh hel…®n avim m…®k…®namin gavgavim iti. Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia God…®n atiating.  
\v 6 Ez…® ia fo, gumazim kuarazir dozir 5 pla 2 toearama dagh ivese. Ez…® God men tav bak…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 7 Egha God uaghan ian dapanir ar…®ziba dar pone, egha a bar deraghav…®ra ia g…®fo. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia atiatingan mark…®. Ia kuarazir dozir kabar m…®n itir puvat…®. Ia God…®n damazim…®n bar ekefe, egha dagh afira.‚Äù 
\s1 E Iesus…®n ziam…®n aghums…®ghan kogham 
\r (Matyu 10:32-33 ko 12:32 ko 10:19-20) 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, Gumazir manam gumazamizibar damazim…®n ghaze, a nan anam, eght…® Gumazibar Otarim uaghan God…®n enselbar damazibar m…®k…®m suam, gumazir kam a nan anam.  
\v 9 Eght…® gumazitam gumazamizibar damazim…®n m…®k…®m suam, a nan anav puvat…®, eght…® k…® uaghan God…®n enselbar damazibar m…®k…®m suam, gumazir kam nan anav puvat…®.  
\v 10 Eght…® gumazitam akar kuratam Gumazibar Otarim m…®kemeght…®, God an arazir kurar kam g…®n amadagham. Eght…® gumazitam God…®n Duam akar kuratam a m…®kemeght…®ma, God an arazir kurar kam, a g…®n amadaghan kogham.  
\v 11 Me ia inigh God ko m…®geir d…®penibar mangam. Egh gavman…®n gumazir ekiaba ko gumazir ziaba itibar damazibar mang…®t…®ma, ia atiatingan mark…®. Egh suam, k…® manmagh…®n ua bagh ganam, o manmagh…®n m…®k…®mam?  
\v 12 Dughiar kamra God…®n Duam n…® m…®kemeght…®ma n…® me m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir dag…®aba bar av…®rasemezir onganim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazir mam gumazamizibar torim…®n ikia kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, nan aveghbuam m…®kemeght…®ma a gan afeziam ga bagha taghizir bizitaba na bagh taba tuiragh.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúTinara guan os…®mt…®zibar k…®r guan biziba tuiraghasa, na m…®sefe?‚Äù  
\v 15 Egha a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh ganigh. Biziba bar dagh ifongezir arazir kaba bagh, uari bagh ganigh! Gumazim…®n dabirabim a bizir av…®rir a itir kaba saram otozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Eghava an akar is…®n zuir kam…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir dag…®aba bar av…®rasemezir mam iti. Egha uan nguazim…®n dagher aghuir av…®riba isi.  
\v 17 Ez…® a kamagh…®n uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄòK…® manmagh…®n damuam? K…® uan daghebar ar…®ghamin danganiba puvat…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEgha a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® kamagh…®n damuam. K…® uan dagher d…®peniba kuarigh…®va, d…®penir ekiabara ingarigham. Egh d…®penir ekiaba, k…® uan maziaba ko dagheba ko biziba bar dar ar…®gham.  
\v 19 Egh k…® uab…®ra uab…® m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúN…® dughiar av…®riba bagha ua bagha bizir aghuir av…®rim ar…®ki. Egh n…® dam…®va, wain…®n d…®pabar am…®va, egh dughiar aghuarim iniva, egh bar akuegh ikiam.‚Äù ‚Äô 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúEz…® God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® gumazir onganim. D…®magarir kamra n…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim k…® a inight…®, naremegham. Eght…® tina n…® ua bagh ar…®ghizir bizir kabanagh iniam?‚Äô 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúEz…® tina ua bagh biziba puv dar pozim m…®k…®n…®va, egh a God…®n damazimning…®n onganarazibar amut…®, bizir kam a bativam.‚Äù 
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuan mark…® 
\r (Matyu 6:25-34) 
\p  
\v 22 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia m…®gei, ia pamten uan ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh kamagh…®n azangan mark…®, e dagher manatam ramam, o e d…®par manatam ramam? Egh ia pamten uan nivaf…®zibagh n…®ghn…®gh m…®k…®man mark…®, e inir manatam uan nivaf…®zim avam?  
\v 23 Gumazim…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim, a daghebagh afira, ez…® gumazim…®n namnam inibagh afira.  
\v 24 Ia kotkotbar gan. Me dagheba opari puvat…®ghava dagh eghuvir puvat…®, me dagheba ar…®zir d…®peniba puvat…®. Ez…® God dagheba dagh an…®di! Ez…® ian dabirabim bar kuarazibagh afira.  
\v 25 Egh ian tav deraghv…®ra ik…®s…® n…®ghn…®gh kamagh…®n a ti uan ik…®r…®m…®rim damut…® a tong ruaragham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 26 N…® bizir muziarir kam damuan iburagh, n…® tizim bagha biziba bar a dagh n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami? 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúIa ak…®marir aghuaribagh n…®ghn…®gh. Da manmagh…®n otifi? Me ingangarir ekiatam gamir puvat…®. Egha me korotiatam isamizir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, fom…®ra Atrivim Solomon bizir bar av…®riba itima an azuir adiariba bar dera, egha an korotiatam ak…®marir kabar m…®n otozir puvat…®.  
\v 28 E fo, graziba pura biziba, da iti, gurum…®n gumazitam da akoregh…®va da is…®va avitam m…®k…®nigham. Grazir k…®nir kabanagh God adiariba me gazui. Ia bizir kam g…®fogh, God uaghan adiariba ia dan…®ngam. Ia gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir muziarim itiba!  
\v 29 Egh ian n…®ghn…®zim dagheba ko d…®pabara ikian mark…®. Egh ia pamtem dagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.  
\v 30 Nguazir kam…®n gumaziba bizir kaba puv dagh n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® ian Afeziam fo, ia da iniam.  
\v 31 Eght…® ia faragh God at…®ght…®ma, a ian Atrivim…®n ik…®t…®ma, ia an g…®n mang…®. Eght…®, a bizir kaba ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Bizir aghuiba akumakuir arazim 
\r (Matyu 6:19-21) 
\p  
\v 32 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa sipsip…®n b…®zir muziarim, ian Afeziam ia damight…®, ia Atrivim…®n otivasa a bar akonge. Kamagh…®n ia atiatingan mark…®.  
\v 33 Ia uan biziba amang…®va dag…®aba inigh, egh gumazir onganarazibar an…®ng. Egh uari bagh dag…®aba azuir m…®tariba inigh dar aright…®ma da d…®ghorigh…®ran kogham. Ian bizir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n itiba, da g…®vaghan kogham. God…®n nguibam…®n ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba rogh…®ra izan kogham, eght…® barareba dagh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham.  
\v 34 Danganir manam n…®n bizir aghuiba iti, danganir kam n…®n navir averiam…®n aven itir ifongiam, a uaghan ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Dakuan mark…®, ia uari bagh gan 
\r (Matyu 24:42-44) 
\p  
\v 35 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ingaramin korotiabar aghuigh…®va otivamin bizim bagh gan…®va uan lamba ateght…®ma da isi, mamagh…®ra ik…®.  
\v 36 Egh mati gumazim uan otarim amir ik…®zir isam bagha ghugha uamategh izasa, me a m…®zuai. Eght…® a uamategh iz…® tiam gafught…® me zuam…®ram a bagh tiam kuigham.  
\v 37 Ingarir gumazir kabar gumazir aruam uamategh iz…® men gant…®, me a m…®zua gari. Kamagh…®n me bar akuegham. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, a dagheba, me dan…®ngs…®, uab…®n kurukegham. Egh me m…®kemeght…®, me dakozim dapiaght…® a iz…® dagheba me dan…®ngam.  
\v 38 Egh men gumazir aruam d…®magarir ar…®zim, o am…®nim tit…®m a uamategh iz…® men gant…® me a bagh gan m…®zuam ik…®t…®, kamagh…®n me bar akuegham.  
\v 39 Ia arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Gumazir manam, ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba d…®magarim…®n izava an d…®penim akarasava amima, a men dughiam g…®fogha, egha men arafa. Egha me ataghiz…® me an d…®penim akarizir puvat…®.  
\v 40 Kamagh…®ra, ia uaghan aravagh ik…® gan. Guizbang…®ra, dughiar ia Gumazibar Otarim m…®zuaman koghamim, a dughiar kamram otogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ingangarir gumazir aghuim ko kuram…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 24:45-51) 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Pita Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® akar is…®n zuir kam…®n erara m…®gei, o e bar mogh…®ra?‚Äù  
\v 42 Ez…® Ekiam an akam ikara, ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazir manamra n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ikia derav…®ra uan ingangarim gami? An gumazir ekiam a damut…®, a ingangarir gumazir igharazibar ganam. Egh dughiar an gumazir ekiam ifongezim…®n, a dagheba is…® ingangarir gumazibar an…®ngam.  
\v 43 Ingangarir gumazir kam ingara itima, an gumazir ekiam izava a batogha an ingangarir kam…®n garima, gumazir kam…®n navir averiam bar an dera.  
\v 44 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ingangarir gumazir kam…®n ekiam a damight…®ma, an an ingangarir gumazir mabar ekiam…®n ik…®va an biziba bar dar ganam.  
\v 45 Egh ingangarir gumazibar dapanim uab…®ra uab…® m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòNan gumazir ekiam dughiar ruarim…®n ikegh izam.‚Äô Egh a d…®kavigh ingangarir gumaziba ko ingangarir amizibav sogh…®va, dam…®va, wain…®n d…®pabar am…®va dapanim onganigham.  
\v 46 Eght…® an ekiam, dughiar an ingangarir gumazim a bagha garir puvat…®zim…®n, an otogham. A dughiar a fozir puvat…®zim…®n uamategham. Eght…®ma an ekiam bar anerghorarigh…®va a inigh…®va gumazir God g…®fozir puvat…®ziba ko anet…®gham. 
\p  
\v 47 ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazibar dapanim fo, an ekiam bizir tizim damuasava a m…®keme, ez…®ma an a gamizir puvat…®. Eght…® an ekiam dughiar av…®ribar a ifozoregham.  
\v 48 Eght…® ingangarir gumazim an ekiam ifongezir arazibagh fozir puvat…®gh…®va, egh a uab…® m…®soghamin arazibar amut…®, an ekiam dughiar av…®ribar a ifozoreghan kogham. Tina bar bizir av…®riba ini, a ua bizir av…®riba God dan…®ngam. Ez…®ma tina God bizir av…®riba an dafarim gar…®ki, God uam a dam av…®riba inis…®va an azangs…®gham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus gumazamiziba ab…®ghasa ize 
\r (Matyu 10:34-36) 
\p  
\v 49 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® nguazim avim a dar…®ghasa izi. Ez…® avim dat…®r…®gh…®ra isiasa k…® ifonge.  
\v 50 K…® t…®ghar rurir mam a iniam. A mati d…®pam gumazim avaraz…® mogh…®n, os…®mt…®ziba na bativam. Ez…® k…® a inizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n k…® bar oseme, mang…® dughiar kam otogham!  
\v 51 N…® ghaze, k…® navir am…®r…®zim inigha nguazir kam…®n izi? puvat…®, k…® ia m…®gei, k…® gumazamiziba ab…®ghasa ize.  
\v 52 Dat…®r…®gh…®n tugh mang…® 5 plan amuiroghboriba d…®penir tam…®n ik…®v uari tuiragham, 3 pla pumuning…®n apanim…®n ikiam, eght…®, pumuning 3 plan apanim…®n ikiam.  
\v 53 Me uari tuiragham, afeziam uan otarim…®n apanim…®n ikiam, eght…® otarim uan afeziam…®n apanim…®n ikiam. Amebam uan guivim…®n apanim…®n ikiam, eght…® guivim uan amebam…®n apanim…®n ikiam. Otarim…®n amuim uan pam…®n amebam…®n apanim…®n ikiam, eght…®, otarim…®n amebam uan otarim…®n amuim…®n apanim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus dughiar otivamibar gun m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 16:2-3) 
\p  
\v 54 Egha Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribav gei, ‚ÄúIa gant…®, ghuariam aruem mag…®ramin amadagham anangt…®ma, ia zuam…®ra suam, ‚ÄòAmozim izam,‚Äô eght…®ma a izam.  
\v 55 Egh Sainain am…®nim vangt…®, ia suam, aruem gan bar puv…®ra isiam. Eght…® an otogham.  
\v 56 Ifavarir gumaziba! Ia overiam ko nguazim…®n otivamin bizibar gun m…®k…®masa fo. Manmagh…®n amiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n otivamin bizibagh fozir puvat…®?‚Äù 
\s1 N…® gumazir n…® is…® kot daraghasa m…®geim ko akabar k…®righ 
\r (Matyu 5:25-26) 
\p  
\v 57 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEz…® ia uari uarir azangs…®ghan aghua, bizir tizim a dera.  
\v 58 Egh n…®n apanim n…® inigh mejistretbar damazim…®n mang…®t…®ma, n…® a ko os…®mt…®zir kam ak…®rs…® tuavim…®n a m…®k…®m ganigh. Puvat…®ght…®ma, a n…® inigh jas…®n damazim…®n mangam. Eght…® jas n…® inigh polis…®n dafarim dat…®ght…®ma polis n…® is…® kalabuziam dat…®gham.  
\v 59 K…® n…® m…®gei, n…® azenim gir…®ghan kogham, kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® n…® ivezim bar anet…®gh azenim giram.‚Äù 
\c 13  
\s1 Gumaziba navibagh iraghan kogh ar…®m…®ghregham 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n gumazir maba ikiava Galilin gumazibar gun Iesus m…®gei, Pailat…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba me m…®soghez…®ma men ghuziba God bagha tuer asizibar ghuziba sara verevere.  
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGalilin gumazir kaba kamagh…®n ariagh…®re. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia ghaze men arazir kuraba Galilin gumazir igharaziba bar men arazir kurabagh afira?  
\v 3 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, bar puvat…®! Egh ia navibagh iraghan kogh…®va, ia uaghan bar ar…®m…®ghregham.  
\v 4 Egh ia uaghan bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, 18 plan gumazir Siloam…®n dag…®ar d…®penim d…®p…®righa me m…®soghez…®ma me ariagh…®re. Ez…® ia ghaze, men arazir kuraba bar Jerusalem itir gumaziba men arazir kurabagh afira?  
\v 5 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, bar puvat…®. Ez…® ia navibagh iraghan kogh…®va, ia uaghan bar ar…®m…®ghregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam temer figh uan wain…®n azenim…®n anekaragha egha ghuava ov…®ziba bagha an gara tam…®n apizir puvat…®.  
\v 7 Egha a wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® 3 plan azenibar arua izava figh…®n ov…®ziba bagha garava avenge, da bar puvat…®. An okegh! Manmagh sua a puram aghui?‚Äô 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEz…®ma a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam aneteght…®ma, an azenir tam uam an ik…®t…®ma, k…® an povim…®n nguaziba a dar…®ght…®ma a dagher aghuiba iniam.  
\v 9 An azenir munam…®n beght…®, deragham. Puvat…®ght…®ma n…® na m…®kemeght…®ma k…® an okegham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus amizir ak…®rir kuram ak…®riz…®, a ua dera 
\p  
\v 10 Egha Iesus Sabat…®n dughiam…®n God ko m…®geir d…®penir mam…®n sure gami.  
\v 11 Ez…®ma amizir mam 18 plan azenim…®n duar kuram an ak…®ragharim gamiz…®ma an aviraghav…®ra ikiava bar uab…® am…®nava avenge. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus an apighava an diaz…®ma an ada zuima, a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizim, n…®n ar…®mariam n…® ataki.‚Äù  
\v 13 Egha uan dafarimning a gis…®n at…®z…®ma, a zuam…®ra uab…® am…®negha tugha, God…®n ziam fe. 
\p  
\v 14 Iesus Sabat…®n amizim ak…®riz…®ma a dera, ez…® bizir kam bagha God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n garir gumazim atarava, egha a kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIngangarir dughiar 6 pla iti, egh ia dughiar kabar iz…®t…®ma, a ian ar…®mariaba ak…®ram. Egh Sabat…®n dughiam…®n ia izan mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Ekiam an akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa uarira uari gifarir gumaziba! Ian tav Sabat…®n dughiam…®n uan bulmakau o donki f…®righa a inigha ghua d…®patam a gan…®dir puvat…®?  
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, amizir kam an Abraham…®n ovavim, Satan 18 plan azenir kabar a ike. Ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® Sabat…®n dughiam…®n a f…®right…® a deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®ma, an apaniba bar mogh…®ra aghums…®ki. Ez…®ma gumaziba ko amiziba an amizir bizir aghuibar gara bar akonge. 
\s1 Mastet…®n ov…®zir akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 13:31-32 ko Mak 4:30-32) 
\p  
\v 18 Egha Iesus gumazamizibar azara, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam manmagh…®n gari? Ez…® k…® akar is…®n zuir manam…®n a m…®k…®mam?  
\v 19 A mastet…®n ov…®zim m…®ngari. Ez…® gumazim a inigha uan azenim…®n an ekaraz…®ma, an aghua ghuava temem gava. Ez…®ma kuaraziba an aguabar m…®konibagh ami.‚Äù 
\s1 Yis…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 13:33) 
\p  
\v 20 Eghava Iesus ua gumazamizibar azara, ‚ÄúK…® bizir manatam…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar is…®n zuim m…®k…®mam?  
\v 21 A yis…®n m…®n ami. Amizir mam yis…®n muziarir mam inigha, flauan dram…®n ekiam…®n itim inigha, aning verevere. Ez…® flauan kam g…®n bar bui.‚Äù 
\s1 Tiar akar asuv…®r…®zim 
\r (Matyu 7:13-14 ko 7:21-23) 
\p  
\v 22 Egha Iesus Jerusalem…®n ghuava nguibar ekiaba ko dozibar bar gumazamizibar sure gamua zui.  
\v 23 Ez…® mav an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, God gumazamizir vabara ua me iniam, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, av…®riba tiar akar asuv…®r…®zir kam…®n aven mang…®va avegham. Ez…® kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia gavgavigh tiar akar asuv…®r…®zir kam…®n d…®righ…®va aven mang…®.  
\v 25 Eght…® d…®penim…®n ghuavim d…®kavigh tiam asaraght…®ma. Ia azenan ik…®va tiam m…®sogh d…®m…®va avegh suam, ‚ÄòEkiam, e bagh tiam kuigh.‚Äô Eght…®ma a kamagh…®n ian akam ikaragham, ‚ÄòK…® ia g…®fozir puvat…®. Ia managh izava otifi?‚Äô 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúEght…® ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòE n…® ko dagheba ko d…®paba ame. Ez…®ma n…® tuavibar en sure gami.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúEght…® a kamagh…®n ian akam ikaragham, ‚ÄòK…® ia g…®fozir puvat…®. Ia managh izava otifi. Na gitagh, ia arazir kurabagh amiba!‚Äô 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúEgh ia, Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ik…®t…®ma ia men gan ikiam. Egh ia azenan ik…®va bizir kam bagh aziva atariba kuskugham.  
\v 29 Egh gumazamizir av…®riba nguazim…®n m…®kebaba bar dar ikegh iz…®va God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n isam bagh uan danganiba iniam.  
\v 30 Ia oragh, g…®n itir gumaziba me faragham, eght…® gumazir faraziba me g…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Jerusalem…®n apangkufi 
\r (Matyu 23:37-39) 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® dughiar kamra Farisin maba Iesus bagha iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúHerot n…® m…®soghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma n…® nguibar kam ategh igharagh mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúMang…® afiar ifarir mam m…®kemegh, ‚ÄòN…® oragh, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ko gurum…®zaraghan duar kuraba batogh…®va egh gumazibar ar…®mariaba ak…®ram. Egh k…® zuer…®m…®n uan ingangarim a g…®vam.‚Äô  
\v 33 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazitam Jerusalem…®n azenan aremeghan kogham. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ko gurum…®zaraghan ko zuer…®m…®n mangv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúOio, ia Jerusalem…®n adarazi, k…® ian apangkufi! Ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba m…®sozi me ariaghiri, egha God ia bagha amadir gumaziba, ia dag…®aba isa, me ginivi, me ariaghiri. Dughiar av…®ribar k…® ian boriba akuv me mughasa, mati tuarir amebam uan av…®ziming…®n nguziba avaraz…® mogh…®n, k…® ia damuasa ifonge. Ez…® ia na bagh izan aghua.  
\v 35 Ia oragh! Ian nguibam, God anetaki. Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia ua nan ganan kogham kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar ia suam, ‚ÄòGod uan ziam…®n gumazir kam anemada! God deragh a damu!‚Äô‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Iesus m…®karzim buizir gumazim gamiz…® a ua dera 
\p  
\v 1 Sabat…®n mam Iesus ghua Farisibar gumazir ekiam…®n d…®penim…®n api. Ez…®ma dughiar kam gumazamiziba bar derav…®ram an gari.  
\v 2 Ez…®ma an guam…®n gumazir m…®karzim buizir mam iti.  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba men azara, ‚ÄúMoses osirizir araziba, da Sabat…®n gumazamizibar ar…®mariaba ghuamaghasa amamangat…®z…®, o puvat…®?‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® me n…®m…®ra itima a gumazim…®n suiragha a gamiz…®ma a dera. Egha anemadaz…® a ghu.  
\v 5 Ez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúIan tav…®n otaritam o bulmakaun tam Sabat…®n dughiam mozirpam…®n a g…®r…®ght…®ma, eght…® n…® zuam…®ra a gekuigham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® me m…®k…®mamin akabagh asa. 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia uarira uari fan mark…® 
\p  
\v 7 Dughiar kam Iesus gari, gumazir gighamiziba me dabirabir danganir ekiaba dagher dakozim…®n da isi. Ez…® Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 8 ‚ÄúGumazitam amuir ik…®zim…®n isam bagh diaght…®, n…® mang…® dabirabir danganir ekiar faragha itim dapian mark…®. Me, gumazir ziar ekiar n…®n ziam gafirazim, a bagha a ginaba.  
\v 9 Eght…®, isar ghuavir v…®rara guan diazim iz…® kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòN…® uan m…®siam gumazir kam dan…®ngigh.‚Äô Eght…® n…® bar aghums…®gh…®va, danganir bar g…®n itim inigham.  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n dughiar me n…®n diazim, n…® danganir apengan itim inigh, eght…® isar ghuavim iz…® suam, ‚ÄòRoroam, danganir aghuir p…®n itim…®n mang…®.‚Äô Eght…® n…® ziar aghuarim n…® ko itir darazir tong…®n a iniam.  
\v 11 Te uarira uan ziaba fe, God me ab…®raght…®, me apengan ikiam. Eght…® te apengan iti, God me feght…® me ziar ekiaba iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 God…®n ikarvazim o gumazim…®n? 
\p  
\v 12 Egha Iesus ua isar ghuavim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® isam damuva, egh uan roroaba, aveghbuaba, o anababa, o n…®n namakar biziba bar av…®rasemeziba, me diaghan mark…®. N…® men diaght…®, me uamategh n…®n diaght…®ma, kamagh…®n n…® uan ikarvazim uamategh a inigham.  
\v 13 Ez…® n…® isam damuamin dughiam, n…® onganarazibagh amiba, soroghafariba ikuviziba, suer kurar aruir puvat…®ziba, ko damazir kurabar diagh.  
\v 14 Eght…® God arazir aghuim n…® damigham. Gumazir kaba n…®n dagheba ikaraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amizim, n…® uan ikarvazim dughiar gumazir God…®n damazim…®n deraziba ua d…®kavamin dughiam…®n a iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Isar ekiam…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 22:1-10) 
\p  
\v 15 Egha Iesus ko dakozim…®n itir gumaziba men mav Iesus…®n akaba baregha, kamagh…®n Iesus…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n isar ekiam ramamim, a bar akongegham.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúDughiar mam gumazir mam isar ekiam bagh bizibar ak…®rava gumazir av…®rim…®n dia.  
\v 17 Isam azuir dughiam…®n isar ghuavim a gighamiziba bagha uan ingangarir gumazim me m…®k…®masa anemaga ghaze, ‚ÄòE biziba bar dar ak…®righa g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia iz…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEz…®ma me bar mogh…®ra mangan aghuaghava uan d…®mdiam ava m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavaribagh ami. Egha farazim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra nguazim givese, egh mang…®va an ganasa. Noka, k…® izan kogham.‚Äô  
\v 19 Ez…® igharazim ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® 10 plan bulmakaubagh ivese, egha k…® da ingangarim gat…®gha dar ganasa zui. Noka, k…® izan kogham. Ga uaning, n…® nan gun isar ghuavim m…®kemegh.‚Äô  
\v 20 Ez…® kamagh…®ra gumazir m…®kezim a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® amuim ini, kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® izan kogham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúEz…® ingangarir gumazim uamategha izava akar kabar gun uan ekiam m…®keme. Ez…® isar ghuavim atara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® zuam…®ra azenan mang…®va nguibar ekiam…®n itir tuavir ekiaba ko afeghtiabar mang…®va onganarazibagh amiba, ko soroghafariba ikuviziba, ko damazir kuraba, ko suer kurar aruir puvat…®ziba, me inigh iz…®.‚Äô  
\v 22 Ez…® ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, n…® m…®kemezir mogh…®n k…® amigha g…®fa, ez…® danganir maba ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äô  
\v 23 Ez…® isar ghuavim uan ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® mang…® bar tuavir ekiaba ko tuavir dozibar itiba bar me m…®k…®mt…®, me iz…®, eght…® nan d…®penim iz…®vaka.  
\v 24 Ez…®, k…® n…® m…®gei, gumazir k…® faragha diaziba men tav isar kam…®n dagher tam rameghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\s1 Faragh derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh…®va Iesus…®n g…®n mang…® 
\r (Matyu 10:37-38) 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® gumazir b…®zir dafam Iesus koma arui. Ez…® a ragha men gara kamagh…®n m…®gei,  
\v 26 ‚ÄúTina na bagh iz…®va, egha uan afeziam ko amebam, o amuim ko boriba, o aveghbuaba, o amezamebaba ko buaramiziba bar men aghuagh…®va, egha uaghan uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ateghan kogh…®va, egh nan suren gumazim…®n otoghan kogham.  
\v 27 Egh…®va tina uan ter ighuvim a gupugh, egh nan g…®n izan kogh…®va, nan suren gumazim…®n otoghan kogham.\f + \ft (14:27) N…® akar Matyu 10:38…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúIan tina d…®penir ekiam…®n ingarasa, a ti faragh daperagh n…®ghnigh…®va, egh suam, k…® dag…®aba manmagh…®ra d…®penir kam a g…®vagham?  
\v 29-30 Egh ian tina d…®penir ekiam…®n ingars…®, faragh daperagh n…®ghn…®gh suam, ‚ÄòK…® dag…®aba manmagh…®ra d…®penir kam a g…®vagham?‚Äô Puvat…®ght…®ma, a ghuriamra damigh…®va, egh aneg…®vaghan koght…®ma, me bar an gan…®va d…®bovir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar a damu, suam, ‚ÄòGumazir kam d…®penim…®n ingara bar aneg…®vazir puvat…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúO, k…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, atrivir mam atrivir igharazim ko m…®dorozir ekiam damuasa. A ti faragh daperagh uab…®ra uab…®n azangs…®gh suam, ‚ÄòK…® ti 10 tausen gumaziba ko mang…®, na bagha izir atrivim…®n 20 tausen gumaziba gafiragham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äô  
\v 32 A m…®soghan buragh…®va, egh atrivim saghuiam…®ra ik…®t…®ma, an abuir gumaziba mang…® suam, m…®dorozim mark…®.  
\v 33 Ez…® kamagh…®ra, ian tina bizir a itiba bar mogh…®ra a da ateghan kogh…®va, egh nan suren gumazim…®n otoghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Amangs…®zir kuram…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 5:13 ko Mak 9:50) 
\p  
\v 34 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmangs…®zim a dera, egh a uan s…®ngt…®zim ategh egh manmagh…®n ua uan s…®ngt…®zim inigham?  
\v 35 An obarir nguazim ko bulmakaubar buariba uaghan dar akuraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me a makuni. Tina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù 
\c 15  
\s1 Sipsip…®n ovengezim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 18:12-14) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba ko dag…®aba isir gumaziba, me Iesus baraghasa anekuvagha iti.  
\v 2 Ez…® Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fofozir gumaziba an atara a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba ko m…®g…®a me koma api.‚Äù  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 4 ‚ÄúIan tav 100 pla sipsipba ik…®t…® tam oveght…®ma, a 99 pla ateght…® da puram azenan ik…® dam…®t…®, eght…® a mang…® ovengezim buri mang…®, an apigh…®v…®ra g…®vagham?  
\v 5-6 Egh anan apigh…®va bar akuegh a isi uan d…®p…®zim dat…®gh a gisaghpugh ngun mangam. Egh a uan namakaba ko an borogh…®n itir darazir diagh me akuvagh, egh kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® uan sipsip…®n ovengezim uam an api! Ia iz…®. E a givarvaram.‚Äô  
\v 7 K…® ia m…®gei, kamagh…®ra enselba gumazir kuram bagha agoir agorogem bar 99 plan derazir gumazir kabagh afiragham. Gumazir kuram a navim giraz…® ez…® 99 pla gumaziba me ghaze me dera egha navibagh irazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Dag…®ar ovengezim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEgh amizitam 10 pla wan Kina ik…®t…®, tam oveght…®ma, a manmagh…®n damuam? A lam daborogh, egh d…®penim aviva a buri mang…®, an apigh…®v…®ra g…®vagham.  
\v 9 Egh an apigh, egh uan namakaba ko an borogh…®n itir darazir diagh me akuvagh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® uan ovengezir wan Kina batogha g…®fa. Ia na ko e a givarvaram.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 10 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, gumazir arazir kurabagh amitam navim giraght…®, ia nguazim…®n a givarvara akongez…® mogh…®n God…®n enselba God…®n Nguibam…®n a givarvaram.‚Äù 
\s1 Afeziar otarir pumuning itim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 11 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam otarir pumuning iti.  
\v 12 Ez…® dozim kamagh…®n uan afeziam m…®gei, ‚ÄòAfeziam, n…® ga bagha tuirazir biziba nananaba na dan…®ngigh.‚Äô Ez…® aning…®n afeziam uan biziba aning bagha da tuira. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúEz…® a mong g…®n uan biziba akuvagha da inigha saghon itir nguibar mam…®n ghu. Egha nguibar kam…®n ikiava pura tintinim…®n arazir kurabagh amima, an dag…®aba bar g…®fa.  
\v 14 Ez…® an dag…®aba bar g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® nguibar a itir kam dagheba puvat…®zir dughiam oto. Ez…® a ua bizitam itir puvat…®.  
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ghua nguibar kam…®n itir gumazir mam…®n ingarasa a bato. Ez…® a anemadaz…® a ghua an dabar gara dar akuagh api.  
\v 16 Ez…® gumazitam daghetam a gan…®ngiz…® puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a dabar gari da nguezibar m…®seviba api. Ez…® a uaghan tabar amasa bar ifonge. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuarim an izima, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòNan afeziam…®n ingangarir gumaziba dagher av…®riba iti. Ez…® k…® kagh m…®tiriam bang…®n aremegham.  
\v 18 K…® ti uamategh uan afeziam bagh mang…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúAfeziam, k…® arazir kuram…®n God ko n…® gami.  
\v 19 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir aghuim puvat…®. Eght…® n…® borim na dar…®ghan mark…®. N…® na ateght…® k…® pura n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù ‚Äô  
\v 20 Egha a d…®kavigha uan afeziam bagha zui. 
\p ‚ÄúEz…® a saghon izav…®ra itima, an afeziam an apigha bar an apangkufi. Egha an a bagha ivegha ghua uan agharimning…®n a muigha an tori. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúEz…® an otarim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® arazir kuram God ko n…® gami. K…® ua gumazir aghuim puvat…®, n…® borim na dar…®ghan mark…®.‚Äô  
\v 22 Ez…® an afeziam kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄòIa zuam…®ra! Korotiar bar aghuir ruarim inigh iz…®va a darugh. Egh ring an dafarim darugh, egh dagarir asuaba a daghuigh!  
\v 23-24 Nan borim ovegha ua iti. Egha ovengez…® e uam an api. Kamagh…®n ami, ia mang…® bulmakaun nguzir m…®karzim sara itim a inigh iz…®va a m…®suegh e anem…®va a givarvaram.‚Äô Egha me a givarvara isam gami. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúEz…® dughiar kam…®n otarir ekiam azenibar ikegha izi. A d…®penim…®n borogh…®n iza orazi, me ighiabagh amua izi ighiam gami.  
\v 26 Ez…® a uan afeziam…®n ingangarir gumazir mam…®n diagha an azara, ‚ÄòMarazi tizim gami?‚Äô  
\v 27 Ez…® a an akam ikara, ‚ÄòN…®n dozim uamategha ize. An aremez…® puvat…®gha derav…®ra ikiava uamatenge. Kamagh…®n, n…®n afeziam a bagha bulmakaun nguzir m…®karzim sara itim m…®soke.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúEz…® an otarir ekiam atarava d…®penim…®n aven mangan aghua. Ez…® an afeziam azenan ghua aven mangasa a gakaghorav…®ra iti.  
\v 29 Ez…® a uan afeziam…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄòN…® gan! K…® azenir kabar k…® pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n ikia pura n…®n ingara, egha n…®n akaba batozir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® bar dughiatam…®n k…® uan namakaba ko ik…® bar akueghasa n…® memen nguzitam na gan…®ngiz…® puvat…®.  
\v 30 Ez…® n…®n otarir kam arazir kurabagh amua amiziba ko ikia uan dag…®aba a g…®vagha izez…®, n…® bulmakaun nguzir m…®karzim sara itim a bagha a m…®soke!‚Äô  
\v 31 Ez…® afeziam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòNan otarim, n…® zurara na ko iti. Ez…® nan biziba da n…®n biziba.  
\v 32 N…®n dozim ovegha ua d…®kafi. Egha an ovengez…® e uam an api. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e a bagh isam gamuava ivarvari.‚Äô‚Äù 
\c 16  
\s1 Gumazir fofozir aghuim ikiava n…®ghn…®zir aghuaribagh amim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúDughiar mam…®n dag…®aba bar av…®rasemezir gumazir mam, an ingangarir gumazibar dapanim iti. An ingangarir gumaziba a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…®n gumazir dapanim n…®n dag…®aba pura da makuri.‚Äô  
\v 2 Ez…®ma an an diaz…®ma an aven ghuz…®ma an an azangs…®si, ‚ÄòN…® bizir tizim gamiz…®ma k…® n…® baraki? N…® uan ingangarim…®n aven n…® amizir bizibar gun m…®geir ak…®nafarim na dan…®ngigh. Ez…® bizir kam bagh n…® ua gumazir dapanim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄúEz…®ma gumazibar dapanim uab…®ra uab…® m…®gei, ‚ÄòNan gumazir ekiam, nan ingangarim…®n na g…®vaz…®ma, k…® manmagh…®n damuam? Egha k…® nguazim g…®kuamin gavgaviba puvat…®gha, biziba bagh azangs…®ghan aghums…®ki.  
\v 4 Ez…® k…® fo, k…® manmagh…®n damuam, nan gumazir ekiam ingangarim…®n na g…®vaght…®ma, gumaziba na m…®k…®mt…®ma k…® men d…®penibar mangam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúA fo, gumazir maba pura gumazir ekiam…®n biziba da ini, me t…®ghar an biziba ua da ikarvagham. Eghava a gumazir kaba vaghvagha men deima me aven zui. Eghava a faragha zuim…®n azara, ‚ÄòN…® manmagh…®n nan gumazir ekiam da biziba ini?‚Äô  
\v 6 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® 800 pla dram wel ini.‚Äô Ez…®ma gumazir dapanim kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® uan ak…®nafarim inigh zuam…®ra daperagh 400…®n an osirigh.‚Äô  
\v 7 Ez…®ma a ua mav…®n azara, ‚ÄòEz…® n…® manmagh…®n nan gumazir ekiam da biziba ini?‚Äô Ez…®ma a ghaze, ‚Äò100 bek plaua.‚Äô Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan ak…®nafarim inigh…®va 80 osirigh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumaziba me amir ingangariba me bar dagh fo. Egha angazangarim…®n itir gumaziba bar me gafira. Ez…® kamagh…®n gumazir ekiam gumazir dapanim amizir arazim g…®fogha, egha gumazir dapanir kurar kam…®n ziam fe. A gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itim…®n arazim gami. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, ia nguazir kam…®n dag…®ar kuram gumazibar akuravagh me namakabar amu. Eght…® dughiar da g…®vamim otoght…®ma, God n…® inight…®ma n…® mang…® ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiamin nguibam…®n mangam. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúEgh tina bizir doziba deraghav…®ra dar gari, a uaghan bizir ekiaba deraghv…®ra dar ganam. Egha tina deraghav…®ra bizir dozibar garir puvat…®, a uaghan bizir ekiaba deraghav…®ra dar ganan kogham.  
\v 11 Egh ia nguazir kam…®n dag…®ar kuram deragh an ganan koght…®ma, tina guizbang…®n biziba ia dan…®ngt…®ma ia dar ganam?  
\v 12 Egh ia gumazir igharazim…®n biziba deraghv…®ra dar ganan koght…®ma, tina ian biziba ia dan…®ngam? 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazitam ingangarir gumazir ekiar pumuning bagh ingaran kogham. A tav…®n aghuagh egh tav gifuegham, o a tav bagh…®v…®ra ik…® egh tav ak…®rim a gasaragham. Ia uaghara God ko dag…®aba bagh ingaran kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Farisin dag…®aba bagha bar ifongeziba 
\r (Matyu 5:31-32 ko 19:9 ko Mak 10:11-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Farisin dag…®aba bagha bar ikuviz…®ba bizir kaba baregha Iesus…®n garav m…®nbaba sighsirav…®ra iti.  
\v 15 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizibar damazibar bizibagh amua ghaze ia dera. Ez…® God ian n…®ghn…®zibagh fo. Ez…® bizir gumazamiziba gari men damazibar bar deraziba, da God…®n damazim…®n bar ikufi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMoses Osirizir Araziba koma God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akam akura mamagh…®ra ikia ghua Jon…®n dughiam…®n tu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Jon God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar aghuim kuri. Ez…® gumaziba ko amiziba bar mogh…®ra dughiar kam…®n aven mangasa uari ghasaghasagha uari munakuri.  
\v 17 Nguazim koma overiam g…®vagham. Eght…® God osizirir arazibar akar otevitam, m…®sevegh…®r…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEz…® n…® gumazir manam uan amuim ategha amizir igharazim…®n ik…®va mati, n…® amizir munam…®n m…®karzim okeme. Ez…® n…® gumazir manam n…® amizir me ikegha taghizim…®n iti, n…® uaghan amizim…®n m…®karzim okeme.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir dag…®aba av…®rasemezim ko Lasarus 
\p  
\v 19 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar mam, gumazir dag…®aba av…®rasemezir mam iti. Egha a korotiar bar aghuir aghevim arugha dagher aghuiba ikia zurara isabagh amua da apa mamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 20 Ez…®ma an tiar akam…®n, gumazir puv biziba bagha azangs…®zir mam, duaba bar a giz…®vaz…®ma a ir…®ghav iti, an ziam Lasarus.  
\v 21 Egh gumazir dag…®aba av…®rasemezir kam…®n dagher oteviba dakozim…®n apengan suaghiriba, a dar amasa gara iti. Ez…®ma afiaba uaghan izava an duaba oz…®si. 
\p  
\v 22 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir puv biziba bagha azangs…®zim aremeghamin dughiam otoz…®ma, an areme. Ez…®ma enselba a inigha ghua Abraham…®n m…®n anet…®. Ez…®ma gumazir dag…®aba av…®rasemezim uaghan aremez…®ma me anefa.  
\v 23 Ez…® a hel…®n ikia m…®zazir kuram isi. Egha a kogha p…®n garava Abraham…®n garima, a bar saghon itima Lasarus an m…®n iti.  
\v 24 Egha an Abraham…®n dei, ‚ÄòAfeziam Abraham, nan apangkufigh. K…® m…®zazim isava avim…®n iti. Ez…® bizir kam bagh Lasarus amadaght…®ma, a uan dafarir puzim d…®pam darugh nan m…®zem orangigh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúEz…®ma Abraham an d…®mdiam ikara, ‚ÄòOtarim, n…® bizir kam gin…®r…®, n…® angamra itir dughiam…®n, n…® bizir aghuiba iti. Ez…® Lasarus bizir kuraba iti. Ez…®ma a dat…®r…®gh…®n kagh deraghav…®ra itima n…® m…®zazir kuram isi.  
\v 26 Ez…® ua bizir mam, ga ko no en t…®zim…®n ruzir konim e ab…®ki. Ez…® te kagh ikegh n…® bagh mang…®s…® iburagham, o tina magh ikegh kagh iz…®s…® iburagham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 27-28 ‚ÄúEz…® dag…®aba av…®rasemezir gumazim Abraham…®n akam pamtem…®n a ikara, ‚ÄòK…® aveghbuar 5 pla iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Afeziam, k…® pamtem…®n n…®n azangs…®si, Lasarus amadaght…®ma a nan afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n mang…®. Egh me m…®kemeght…®, me k…® itir nguibar m…®zaziba isir kam…®n izan mark…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúEz…®ma Abraham an akam ikara, ‚ÄòMe Moses koma God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar osiziriba men iti. Ez…® me men akaba baragh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúEz…®ma an Abraham m…®gei, ‚ÄòPuvat…®, Afeziam. Gumazir ovengezitam ua d…®kavigh me bagh mang…®t…®ma, me navibagh iragham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúEz…®ma Abraham kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòMe Moses koma God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba baraghan koght…®ma, tav aremegh ua d…®kavigh iz…®, me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n an akabar ikian kogham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\c 17  
\s1 Arazir kuraba, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gas…®ghas…®si 
\r (Matyu 18:6-7 ko 18:21-22 ko Mak 9:42) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúBizir gumazamizibagh amima me arazir kurabagh amiba. da guizbang…®ra izam. Ez…® gumazir dagh ami da otivim, a bar kuvigham.  
\v 2 A ik…®va borir katam arazir kuratam an akagham, kamagh…®n ia a inigh…®va dag…®am an f…®rim ikegh…®va a is…® ongarim m…®k…®night…®, an aremeght…®, kamagh…®n deragham.  
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia derav…®ra uari bagh gan. 
\p ‚ÄúEgh…®va n…®n aveghbuam arazir kuratam damight…®ma, n…® pamtem a m…®k…®m suam, n…® da atakigh. Eght…® a navim g…®raght…®ma, n…® an arazir kuraba g…®n amada.  
\v 4 Egh…®va a 7 plan dughiabar arazir kurabar n…® damigh…®va, egh 7 plan dughiabar uamategh n…® bagh iz…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® navim g…®ra,‚Äô n…® an arazir kuraba da g…®n amadagh.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim m…®gei 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® aposelba kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim damight…®ma an ekefegh!‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEgh ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim suvigh zuravarim mastet…®n ov…®zitam…®n m…®n ik…®t…®ma, ia temer kam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® uab…® asigh…®va egh biba sara mang…®va ongarim…®n uab…® ekaragh,‚Äô eght…® a ian akam baragham.‚Äù \f + \ft (17:6) Mastet…®n ov…®zim, a bar sufi.\f* 
\s1 Iesus ingangarir gumazim…®n arazim m…®gei 
\p  
\v 7 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan tav ingangarir gumazitam an azenim…®n ingari o sipsipbar gari. Ingangarir gumazim azenibar ikegh iz…®t…®ma, eght…® a suam, n…® iz…® daperagh dam…®? Puvat…®. Ia kamagh…®n m…®geir puvat…®.  
\v 8 Gumazir dapanim kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, n…® na bagh dagheba isamigh uan inim kegh da tuigh faragh na danight…® k…® dar amam, eght…® n…® g…®n dam…®.  
\v 9 A ingangarir gumazim amizir bizir kaba bagha a m…®nabagham, o puvat…®gham? Puvat…®.  
\v 10 Ez…® ia uaghan, God damuasa ia m…®kemezir biziba bar dagh ami, egh suam, E pura ingangarir gumazir kuraba, ingangarir Ekiam e gan…®ngiziba e pura dagh ami.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus 10 plan gumazir lepa itibar k…®riz…®ma me ua dera 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus Jerusalem…®n ghuava, Samaria koma Galilin Distrigh…®n t…®zim…®n zui.  
\v 12 Ez…® a nguibar mam…®n aven zuima, 10 pla lepa itir gumaziba a bato. Me mong saghon tuivighav ikiava,\f + \ft (17:12) Lepan ar…®mariar fom…®ra Baibel…®n dughiam…®n ikezim ighara. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir lepan ar…®mariam a igharaghav ami. Fom…®ra ikezim, pura m…®karzir ghurghurim gumazir namnabar otifi. Egha uaghan bizir igharaziba sara posi.\f* 
\v 13 tiarir arozim…®n an dei, ‚ÄúIesus, Gumazir Ekiam, en apangkufigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…®ma a men apighava, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®va, uari is…®va God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar akagh.‚Äù Ez…®ma me me bagha ghua tuavir ar…®zim…®n men m…®karziba zuegha dera 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® men mav, uab…®n garima an ar…®mariam g…®vaz…®ma a uamategha izava pamtem…®n God…®n diava egha an ziam fe.  
\v 16 Egha Iesus…®n suemning…®n apengan ir…®ghava uan guam nguazim m…®tuaghava, Iesus a gamizir bizim bagha a m…®naba. A Samarian gumazimra. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® k…® 10 plan gumazir kaba ak…®ris ti, o puvat…®? Ez…® 9 pla managh iti?  
\v 18 Ez…® Judan gumazitam ua iza, a God…®n ziam fe, o puvat…®? Gumazir saghuiam…®n izezim uab…®ra izava God…®n ziam fe.‚Äù  
\v 19 Eghava a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh mang…®. N…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…® gamiz…®ma, n…® dera.‚Äù 
\s1 God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam izam 
\r (Matyu 24:23-28 ko 24:37-41) 
\p  
\v 20 Dughiar mam…®n Farisin gumaziba Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mana dazogh…®n izam?‚Äù Ez…®ma Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa orasi, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n arazaraziba ia uan damazibar an ganighan kogham.  
\v 21 Eght…® gumazitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham suam, ‚ÄòA kara,‚Äô o ‚ÄòA muna.‚Äô Ez…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a ian navir averiam…®n aven iti.‚Äù\f + \ft (17:21) Gumazir maba kamagh…®n akar otevir kam giragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, ian aven iti.‚Äù\f* 
\v 22 Egha Iesus uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúDughiam iz…®t…®ma n…® Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam a bagh gans…® damuva avegham.  
\v 23-24 Gumaziba ia m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòAra muna!‚Äô o ‚ÄòAra kara!‚Äô Ez…® ia fo, Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam an on…®marim…®n m…®n taghtagham. Eght…®ma an angazangariba bar overiam…®n ruaghatevimning uagharam aning…®n tagham. Eght…® ia ivemar…®v men akaba g…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 25 Egh a faragh bizir av…®riba bagh m…®zazim inigham. Eght…®ma dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n itir gumaziba an aghuagham. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúEz…® bizir Noan dughiam…®n otiviziba, da uaghan kamagh…®n Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam…®n otivam.  
\v 27 Gumazamiziba dagheba ko d…®paba apava, uarir ikiava mamagh…®ra ikia ghua, Noa uan kurim…®n ghuavanabozir dughiam. Ez…®ma aperiam izava bar me kuavareme. 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúEz…® Lot…®n dughiam…®n kamagh…®ra, gumazamiziba dagheba ko d…®paba apava, dag…®aba bagha biziba amagava, dagh ivezava, dagheba oparava d…®penibar ingari.  
\v 29 Ez…® Lot Sodom ataghizir dughiam…®n, avim koma dag…®ar isiba amozim…®n m…®n overiam…®n ikegha suaghira izagh…®ra bar mogh…®ra me kuavareme. 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúGumazibar Otarim azenimra izighramin dughiam biziba uaghan kamagh…®ram otivam.  
\v 31 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n n…® tina uan d…®penim…®n avughs…®zir danganim ik…®va, egha uan biziba ataghiz…® da aven iti, n…® da bagh mag…®r…® da inian mark…®. Kamagh…®ra, tina azenibar iti, a bizir tam bagh nguibam…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 32 N…® Lot…®n amuim g…®n…®ghn…®gh!  
\v 33 Ez…®ma tina uan m…®karzim geghufi, an aremegham. Ez…® tina na bagha uan m…®karzim anataki, a g…®n deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 34 K…® ia m…®gei, d…®magarir kam…®n taning uaning inigh m…®siar vam…®ra dakut…®ma, God tav inigh…®va tav ategham.  
\v 35-36 Eght…® amizir pumuning uaning inigh maziaba r…®ghr…®ght…®ma, God tav inigh…®va tav ategham.‚Äù\f + \ft (17:35-36) Baibel…®n fofozir gumazir maba ghaze akar otevir mam uaghan kagh iti. Akar otevir kam kamak…®n, ‚ÄúGumazir pumuning azenim…®n ik…®t…®, God aning…®n tav inigh egha tav ategham.‚Äù N…® deragh foghs…®, Mt 24:40…®n gan.\f* 
\v 37 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam managh…®ra?‚Äù Ez…®ma a men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir kuaba managh iti nagh…®n, taragiaba uari akuvagham.‚Äù 
\c 18  
\s1 Zurara God ko m…®geir arazim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus akar is…®n zuir mam…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, egh men akaght…®, me zurara God ko m…®k…®m mamaghra ikiam. Egh am…®raghan mark…®.  
\v 2 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguibar ekiar mam…®n aven jas…®n mam iti, a God…®n atiatir puvat…®. Egha gumazibagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Ez…® amuir odiarir mam uaghan nguibar ekiar kam…®n iti. Ez…® gumazir mam pazava a gamua os…®mt…®ziba a gar…®si. Ez…® a jas bagha zurara izava a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® kotiam…®n nan akuragh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄúEz…®ma dughiar av…®rir maba a bizitam gamizir puvat…®. Eghava abuan a uab…®ra uab…® m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® God…®n atiatir puvat…®. Egha k…® gumazibagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 5 Ez…® amuir odiarir kam dughiar av…®ribar na bagha izi. K…® bar am…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ua bagh zuam…®ra an os…®mt…®zim ak…®righam, eght…® a ua iz…® na damut…®ma k…® bar am…®raghan kogham!‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa jas…®n kuram…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baragh.  
\v 7 Ez…® God…®n inabaziba, me d…®magariba ko aruebar a bagha araima, a men os…®mt…®ziba bagha iza a da ak…®ram, o puvat…®gham? A me ataghraght…® me pura mangam? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 8 K…® ia m…®gei, a men os…®mt…®zibar gan…®va, zuam…®ra men akuragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Gumazibar Otarim uamateghamin dughiam…®n, a gant…®, nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir pumuning God ko m…®geir akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 9 Gumazir mabara uarira uan ziaba fava egha igharaz daraziv g…®a ghaze, me derazir puvat…®. Ez…® Iesus kamagh amir gumaziba bagh akar is…®n zuir kam gami,  
\v 10 ‚ÄúGumazir pumuning God ko m…®k…®masa God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu, aning…®n mav Farisi, ez…® mav dag…®aba isir gumazim.  
\v 11 Ez…® Farisin gumazim d…®kavigha tugha uab…®ra ua bagha God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® n…® m…®naba, k…® gumazir mabar m…®n amir puvat…®. Me biziba ok…®ava, arazir kurabagh amuava egha martiar amiziba ok…®a me koma akui. Egha k…® uaghan dag…®aba isi gumazir kam…®n m…®n amir puvat…®.  
\v 12 K…® wigh…®n vam…®ran dughiar pumuning…®n n…® ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrasi. Egha bizir k…® isiba, k…® tong…®ra da tuiragha uaghan n…® gan…®di.‚Äô  
\v 13 Ez…® dag…®aba isir gumazim mong munamagh…®n tu. Egha a kogha overiam…®n gari puvat…®gha uan evarim m…®sogha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® gumazir kuram, God n…® nan apangkufigh!‚Äô  
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazir dag…®aba isir kam, a God…®n damazim…®n deragha egha d…®penim…®n ghu. Ez…® igharazim puvat…®. Te uarira uan ziaba fe, God me ab…®raght…®, me apengan ikiam. Eght…® te apengan iti, God me feght…® me ziar ekiaba iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, borir doziba na bagh iz…® 
\r (Matyu 19:13-15 ko Mak 10:13-16) 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® gumazamiziba borir doziba Iesus dafarimning me dar…®ghasa, me inigha izi. Ez…®ma an suren gumaziba kamagh…®n ganigha egha men atari.  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus borir dozibar diaz…® me a bagha zuima a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tina God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ik…®s…®, borir dozir kabar m…®n ik…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma borir doziba ateght…®ma me na bagh iz…®, egh men anogoroghan mark…®.  
\v 17 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazitam borir dozir kabar m…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam inighan kogh…®va, egh an aven mangan bar iburagham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir dapanir biziba av…®rasemezim, Iesus ko m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 19:16-30 ko Mak 10:17-31) 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Judabar gumazir dapanir mam Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúTisan Aghuim, k…® manmagh…®n damigh zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh sua gumazir aghuim na gar…®si? Gumazir aghuitam itir puvat…®. God uab…®ra gumazir aghuimra.  
\v 20 N…® God Moses gan…®ngizir arazim g…®fo, ‚ÄòN…® gumazim m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®, n…® poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuam mark…®, n…® gumazir igharazim…®n biziba ok…®man mark…®, n…® bizibagh ifaran mark…®, n…® ua bagh biziba inis…® gumazibagh ifaran mark…®, n…® uan afeziam ko amebam…®n apengan ik…® aning…®n akaba baragh.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® a kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ram agh…®rimra ikiava arazir kabagh amua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kati.‚Äù  
\v 22 Ez…®ma Iesus kamagh…®n oregha, egha a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bizir vam…®ra n…® t…®ghar a damuam. Bizir n…® itiba bar da amangigh…®va dag…®aba inigh, egh gumazir biziba puvat…®zibar an…®ngigh. Egh n…® God…®n Nguibam…®n bizir aghuariba iniam. Egh, nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù  
\v 23 A biziba bar av…®raseme, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, a Iesus…®n akam baregha bar oseme.  
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus an gara egha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir biziba av…®rasemeziba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n mang…®s…® bar iburagham!  
\v 25 Kamel…®n tam iniba isair d…®konir torim…®n aven mang…®s…® ingangarir dafam damigh aven mangam. Eght…® gumazir biziba av…®rasemeziba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n mang…®s…® guizbang…®ra bar iburagham!‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n oregha an azara, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n damight…®ma, tinara zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir kam iniam?‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus me ikara, ‚ÄúBizir kaba gumazim…®n bar osemegham. Bizir kaba God…®n osemezir puvat…®. A biziba bar dagh ami.‚Äù  
\v 28 Ez…® Pita a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ge, e bizir e itiba bar da ategha, n…®n g…®n ize.‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazitam God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam bagha uan d…®penim, o uan amuim, o aveghbuaba, o ameboghfeziaba, o boriba ataki,  
\v 30 egh dat…®r…®gh…®n itir dughiar kam…®n God bizir av…®riba me faragha inizir bizibagh afiragh me dan…®ngam. Egh dughiar g…®n otivamim me zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Dughiar m…®kezim Iesus ua m…®g…®a ghaze, an aremegh ua d…®kavigham 
\r (Matyu 20:17-19 ko Mak 10:32-34) 
\p  
\v 31 Egha Iesus 12 plan suren gumaziba inighava me uarira ikiava a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh! E nguibar ekiam Jerusalem…®n ghuavanadi. Eght…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, Gumazibar Otarim…®n gun m…®kemezir osizirir biziba bar, guizbang…®ra otogham.  
\v 32 Eght…® me a is…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazibar dafaribar ar…®gham. Eght…® me a d…®pova a m…®k…®mam. Egh aghums…®zir arazibar a damuam. Egh a gipar…®va, egh…®va a ifozoregh egh a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.  
\v 33 Eght…® dughiar m…®kezim a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù  
\v 34 Ez…®ma an suren gumaziba bizir katam g…®fozir puvat…®, a bizir tizim m…®gei. Dar m…®ngarim men monge, ez…® me bar fozir puvat…®. 
\s1 Iesus gumazir damazir kuram gamiz…®ma, a gari 
\r (Matyu 20:29-34 ko Mak 10:46-52) 
\p  
\v 35 Egha Iesus Jerikon borogh…®ra izima, gumazir damazir kurar mam tuavir m…®riam…®n aperaghav ikia biziba bagha azangs…®si.  
\v 36 Egha an orazima gumazamizir av…®rim iza zuima, a men azara, kar tizim.  
\v 37 Ez…® me a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNasaret…®n gumazim Iesus iza zui.‚Äù  
\v 38 Ez…® a dia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIesus, Devit…®n Otarim, n…® nan apangkufigh!‚Äù  
\v 39 Ez…® faragha zuiba me an atarava egha a m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® n…®m…®ra ik…®. Ez…® a bar pamtem dia m…®gei, ‚ÄúDevit…®n ovavim, n…® nan apangkufigh!‚Äù  
\v 40 Ez…® Iesus tugha akar gavgavim gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir munam inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® a rogh…®ra izima, Iesus an azara,  
\v 41 ‚ÄúK…® tizim n…® bagha a damuasa, n…® ifonge?‚Äù Ez…® an a ikara, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® ganasa ifonge.‚Äù  
\v 42 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gan. N…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n akuraz…®, n…® dera.‚Äù  
\v 43 Ez…® a zuam…®ra gari. Egha Iesus…®n g…®n ghua God…®n ziam fe. Ez…®ma gumazamiziba an ganigha, me uaghan God…®n ziam fe. 
\c 19  
\s1 Iesus Sakius…®n d…®penim…®n ghu 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus Jerikon nguibam…®n ghuava, aneteghasa tuavim…®n zui.  
\v 2 Gumazir mam nguibar kam…®n iti, an ziam Sakius. A dag…®aba isir gumazibar gumazir dapanim, a dag…®aba bar av…®raseme.  
\v 3 A Iesus…®n ganasa, a manmagh…®ra garir gumazim. Sakius bar gumazir otevim, egha gumazamizir av…®rim…®n tong…®n iti. Egha kamagh…®n a Iesus…®n garir puvat…®.  
\v 4 A fo, Iesus tuavir kamra izam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ivegha faragha ghua, Iesus…®n ganasa temer figh…®n ghuavanabo. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam…®n oto. Egha kogha temer kam gis…®n gara, kamagh…®n Sakius…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúSakius n…® zuam…®ra izighir…®. Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…®n d…®penim…®n ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® a zuam…®ra izaghr…®ghava, bar akonge. Egha Iesus inigha uan d…®penim…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® gumaziba bar an ganigha, egha me kamagh…®n m…®g…®ava ngavamadi, ‚ÄúA ghua gumazir kuram…®n d…®penim…®n iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Me d…®penim…®n ikiava, Sakius tughava, kamagh…®n Ekiam m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, N…® oragh! Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® uan biziba bar da tuiragham. Egh taba k…® gumazir biziba puvat…®zibar an…®ngam. Egh k…® gumazir tam gifaragh…®va, an bizitam okemegh…®va, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uamategh bizir pumuning ko pumuning a dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam a uaghan Abraham…®n ovavim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n God d…®penir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar men akura.  
\v 10 Gumazibar Otarim, gumazir ovengeziba bagha ruiava men akurvaghasa ize.‚Äù 
\s1 Dag…®aba inizir ingangarir gumazir 10 plan akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 25:14-30) 
\p  
\v 11 Gumazamiziba ikia Iesus barazima, a m…®gei. A Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itima, me ghaze, dat…®r…®gh…®ra God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam otogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, an akar is…®n zuir mam me m…®gei.  
\v 12 A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir aruar mam nguibar saghuiam…®n mangasa, eght…® me a damight…®ma an atrivim…®n ikiam. A g…®n uamategh uan nguibam…®n izegh…®va, men ganam.  
\v 13 A mangasa, a uan ingangarir gumazir 10 plan diagha, 20 kina, 20 kina bar mogh…®ra me rome. Egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa dag…®ar kaba inigh…®va uari bagh dag…®ar ingangaribar amu ik…®t…®, k…® uamategham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúAn apengan itir gumaziba me bar navir kuram an iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me akam inigha zuir gumaziba amadaz…®ma me nguibar gumazir aruam ghuz…®m…®n ghu. Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòE gumazir kam en atrivim…®n otivan, e aghua.‚Äô  
\v 15 Ez…® gumazir igharaziba gumazir aruar kam a gamiz…®ma an atrivim…®n otogha, egha g…®n uamatenge. A uamategha izegha, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazir k…® fom…®ra dag…®aba an…®ngiziba, men diagh. K…® foghasa me manmagh…®n nan dag…®abagh is…®n dag…®aba ini.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúEz…®ma gumazir faragha zuim iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, k…® n…®n 20 kinan kam…®n dag…®ar ingangarim gamighava a gis…®n 200 kina ini.‚Äô  
\v 17 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® nan ingangarir gumazir aghuim, egha n…® ingangarir bar aghuim gami. N…® bar deraghv…®ra bizir muziarim gami, kamagh…®n k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir ekiam n…® danight…®ma, n…® nguibar ekiar 10 plan ganam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEz…®ma ingangarir gumazir igharazim iza m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, k…® n…®n 20 kinan kam…®n dag…®ar ingangarim gamigha dat…®r…®gh…®n a gis…®n 100 kina ini.‚Äô  
\v 19 Ez…® atrivim a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® n…® at…®ght…® n…® nguibar ekiar 5 plan ganam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúEz…® ingangarir gumazir m…®kezim iza m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam n…®n 20 kina ikia kati. K…® a isa inir av…®zim…®n a nomkez…®ma, a kati.  
\v 21 K…® n…® g…®fo, n…® gumazir atarim. Gumazir igharaziba amir biziba, n…® pura da isi. Egha dagher me opariziba, n…® uaghan pura da isi. Kamagh…®n k…® n…®n atiati.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 22 ‚ÄúEz…®ma atrivim kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir kuram! N…®n akamra k…® n…® tuis…®gham. N…® kamagh…®n na g…®n…®ghn…®si, k…® ti gumazir atarim. Egha k…® gumazir igharaziba amir biziba, k…® ti pura da isi. Egha dagher me opariba, k…® ti uaghan pura da isi?  
\v 23 Manmagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® nan dag…®aba benk gat…®z…® puvat…®, eght…® k…® uamategh iz…®va ua da iniva dag…®ataba a gis…®n ua da iniam?‚Äô  
\v 24 Ez…® a kamagh…®n an borogh…®n tuivighav itir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄòIa ada 20 kina inigh…®va gumazir 200 kina itim dan…®ngigh.‚Äô  
\v 25 Me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, a 200 kina inigha g…®fa.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúEz…®ma a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® ia m…®gei! Gumazitam bizir taba ik…®t…®, k…® av…®ritaba uam a danigham. Eght…® gumazitam biziba puvat…®gh…®va, eght…® bizir muziarim a itim, k…® ada da inigham.  
\v 27 Nan apaniba, k…® men atrivim…®n ikian me nan aghua, ia me inigh kagh iz…®va nan damazim…®n me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghregh.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Iesus akar is…®n zuim gamigha g…®vagha, uan darorim gamua tuavir Jerusalem…®n ghuzim ghuavanadi. 
\ms1 Iesus Jerusalem…®n otoghava God…®n D…®penim…®n gumaziba ko amizibar sure gami 
\mr (Sapta 19:29-21:38) 
\s1 Iesus atrivim…®n m…®n Jerusalem…®n aven zui. 
\r (Matyu 21:1-11 ko Mak 11:1-11 ko Jon 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 29 Iesus Betfage ko Betanin borogh…®n oto, m…®ghs…®am Oliv gis…®n. Egha uan suren gumazir pumuning amaga,  
\v 30 kamagh…®n aning…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar munagh itim…®n mang…®. Gua nguibar kam…®n mang…® gant…®ma donkin igiar mam me a ikez…®ma, a iti. Gumazitam dughiatam…®n a gaperaghava aruizir puvat…®. Gua an benim f…®righ…®va donki inigh kagh iz…®.  
\v 31 Tav kamagh…®n guan azaragham, ‚ÄòGua tizim bagha donkin kam f…®ri?‚Äô, eght…® gua suam, ‚ÄòEkiam ingangarim an iti.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Egha Iesus aning amadaz…®ma aning ghua garima, biziba bar mogh…®ra Iesus m…®kemez…® mogh…®n iti.  
\v 33 Ez…® aning donkin benim f…®rima, an ghuaviba aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizim bagha donkin benim f…®ri?‚Äù  
\v 34 Ez…®ma aning kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam ingangarim an iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Egha aning donki inigha Iesus bagha izi. Egha aning uan azenan azuir korotiar ruariba donki gis…®n da ghuani. Egha aning Iesus…®n akuraz…®ma a donki gis…®n apera.  
\v 36 A donki gaperagha zuima, gumazamiziba uan korotiar ruariba suava tuavim m…®ghuari.  
\v 37 A iza danganir tuavir Oliv…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuaghirim…®n borogh…®n izima, an g…®n aruir darazi me God amizir mirakelbar ganighava da bagha bar akongegha pamtem God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 38 Me kamagh…®n araghasi, ‚ÄúGod uan ziam…®n atrivim amada! God derav…®ra a damu! Navir am…®rizim God…®n Nguibam…®n iti. Ia God…®n ziam f…®!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Farisin marazi gumazamizir kabar tong…®n ikia, kamagh…®n Iesus…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® uan suren gumazibav k…®mt…®ma, me n…®m…®ra ik…®! Me kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®!‚Äù  
\v 40 Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, me n…®m…®ra ik…®t…®ma dag…®aba uari araghasam!‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Jerusalem bagha azi 
\p  
\v 41 Iesus Jerusalem…®n borogh…®ra iza, egha an gara a bagha azi.  
\v 42 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúJerusalem, k…® kamagh sua, n…® amua dat…®r…®gh…®n navir am…®riz…®m…®n bizibagh foghai. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n modo.  
\v 43 Dughiam iz…®t…®, eght…® n…®n apaniba nguazir d…®vazim ingaright…®, a n…® arught…®ma, n…® ar…®mang…®ghan kogham.  
\v 44 Egh…®va n…® Jerusalem me n…®n borir n…®n aven itiba sarama as…®ghasigham. N…® God…®n dughiar n…®n akuraghasa izezim, n…® a g…®fozir puvat…®. Bizir kam bagh d…®penim…®n ingarizir dag…®atam, me aneteght…®, a tam gis…®n keghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ivezir gumaziba ko biziba amadir gumaziba God…®n D…®penim me batosi 
\p  
\v 45 Egha a God…®n D…®penir av…®zim…®n aven ghuava, biziba amadiba me batosi.  
\v 46 A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod fom…®ra Aisaian ak…®nafarim…®n aven kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄòNan d…®penim God ko m…®geir d…®penimra, ez…® ia a gamiz…®ma, an ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba modir danganim…®n m…®n oto.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 47 A zurara God…®n D…®penim…®n aven men sure gami. Ez…®ma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko gumazir dapaniba, me a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa.  
\v 48 Ez…® gumazamiziba a baraghasa bar ifongegha, bar an borogh…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an apaniba a m…®soghan ibura. 
\c 20  
\s1 Me Iesus…®n gavgavim bagha an azara 
\r (Matyu 21:23-27 ko Mak 11:27-33) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam…®n Iesus God…®n D…®penir av…®zim…®n aven ikiava, gumazamizibar sure gamuava akar aghuim akuri. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, ko Judan gumazir aruaba, me izava anekufa.  
\v 2 Egha me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE m…®kemegh, n…® gavgavir manam…®n bizir kabagh ami? Tina gavgavir kam n…® gan…®ngi?‚Äù  
\v 3-4 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® uaghan azangs…®zitam ia damuasa. Ia na m…®k…®m, Jon…®n rurim, a God…®n ize o gumazibar ize?‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® me uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúE suam, ‚ÄòAn rurim God…®n ize,‚Äô eght…®, a kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa manmagh…®n amigha ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Jon damuan aghua?‚Äô  
\v 6 E suam, ‚ÄòAn rurim gumazibar ize,‚Äô eght…® gumaziba dag…®abar e ginivight…®ma, e ar…®ghregham. Me kamagh…®n fo Jon a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim.‚Äù  
\v 7 Egha me Iesus ikara, ‚ÄúE fozir puvat…®, Jon…®n rurim manmagh…®n ize.‚Äù  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, k…® uan gavgavim inizir tuavim…®n, gun ia m…®kemeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Wain…®n azenir gumazibar akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 21:33-46 ko Mak 12:1-12) 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Iesus m…®g…®av…®ra ikia akar is…®n zuir kam gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam wain…®n azenim oparigha, egha azenim…®n garir gumazir mabar dafarim gar…®gha ghaze, me g…®n a givezam. Egha a ghua dughiar ruarim…®n saghon iti.  
\v 10 Egha wain…®n ov…®ziba kuarir dughiam…®n a ingangarir gumazir mam amadagha ghaze, me wain…®n ov…®zir and…®zir taba a dan…®ngam. Ez…® azenim…®n garir gumaziba a m…®sueghava anemadaz…®ma, a dafaribara uamatenge.  
\v 11 Ez…® a ingangarir gumazir igharazim amada, ez…® me uaghan a m…®suegha aghums…®zir arazibar a gamigha, anemadaz…® a dafaribara uamatenge.  
\v 12 Ez…® a ua m…®kezim amadaz…®, me bar puv a m…®suegha a isa azenim m…®k…®ni. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúEz…® wain…®n azenir ghuavim uab…®ra uab…® m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® manmagh…®n damuam? K…® uan otarir ifongezim amangam. Eght…® me ti a m…®sueghan kogham.‚Äô  
\v 14 Ez…® wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumaziba otarir kam…®n ganigha, kamagh…®n uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòKar otarir g…®n azenir kam iniamim. E a m…®sueght…® an aremeka. Eght…® wain…®n azenir kam enanam.‚Äô  
\v 15 Egha me a isa azenim m…®k…®nigha a m…®soghez…®ma an areme.‚Äù 
\p Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúWain…®n azenir ghuavim manmagh…®ra azenim…®n garir gumazir kabar amuam?  
\v 16 A iz…®va azenim…®n garir gumazir kabav soght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® a wain…®n azenim is…®va igharazibar anigam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® gumazamiziba bizir kam baregha m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®gham!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus merara gara ghuava azara, ‚ÄúEz…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam, an m…®ngarim manmak…®n? 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòKar d…®penir ak…®nir ingangarir gumaziba aghuazim, 
\q2 a dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®penim aterir guarim gava?‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 18 N…® tina temer guarir kam gis…®n ir…®gh…®va d…®p…®righ ir…®gham, eght…® a tina gis…®n ir…®ght…®ma gumazir kam bar m…®sarighregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, ko ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba Iesus bar kagh…®ram an suighasa tuaviba buri. Me fo, an akar is…®n zuir kam me gasara, ez…® me an suighan gumazamizibar atiati. 
\s1 Dag…®aba Sisar gan…®di 
\r (Matyu 22:15-22 ko Mak 12:13-17) 
\p  
\v 20 Egha me bar derav…®ra a bagha garava, egha moga garir gumaziba amadaz…®, me ifara mati me guiz…®n m…®gei. Me kamagh sua, me Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevitam…®n an suiragh…®va, egh a is…® Rom…®n gavman…®n gumazir ekiam danigam.  
\v 21 Ez…® moga garir gumazir kaba an azangs…®si, ‚ÄúTisa, e fo n…® bizir aghuibav g…®ava sure gamuava, ziabagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. N…® gumazamiziba God…®n arazibar m…®rara guizbang…®ra men sure gami.  
\v 22 N…® e m…®k…®m. E gavman…®n dag…®aba Sisar dan…®ngam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23-24 Ez…® a men n…®ghn…®zir ifavaribagh fogha, egha a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDag…®atam nan akagh. Tinan nedazim ko ziam an iti?‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…® me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúSisar…®n ziam koma nedazim an iti.‚Äù Ez…® a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra ia Sisar…®n biziba Sisar dan…®ng…®va, God…®n biziba is…®, God dan…®ng.‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® me gumazamizibar tong…®n, a m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bagha an suighan ibura. Egha me purama an m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh n…®ghn…®ghava n…®m…®ra iti. 
\s1 Aremezir gumaziba ua d…®kavigham 
\r (Matyu 22:23-33 ko Mak 12:18-27) 
\p  
\v 27 Sadyusin maba azangs…®zir mam sara Iesus bagha ize. (Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, aremeziba ua d…®kavan kogham.)  
\v 28 Egha me Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, Moses e bagha ak…®nafarim osira ghaze, gumazitam…®n aveghbuam amuim…®n ik…®va boriba puvat…®gh…®va aremeght…®, anar…®ra irir aveghbuam an amuir odiarim…®n ik…®va a bagh boriba iniam.  
\v 29 Ez…® 7-plan aveghbuaba iti. Egha men mav faragha amuim…®n ikia boriba puvat…®gha areme.  
\v 30-31 Ez…® anar…®ra irim an ikia kamagh…®ra, ez…® m…®kezim kamagh…®ra ghu. Kamagh…®ra, 7 plan aveghbuaba bar ariaghregha, me boriba puvat…®.  
\v 32 Abuan amizir kam uaghan areme.  
\v 33 Fom…®ra me bar amizir kam…®n ike. Kamagh…®n a ua d…®kavamin dughiam…®n, a tinan amuim gavagham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikara, ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n gumaziba ko amiziba me poroghamibagh ami.  
\v 35 Eght…® gumazamizir God inabaziba, me uaghan dughiar izamim ko ua d…®kavamin dughiam, me poroghamibar amuan kogham.  
\v 36 God me damight…®ma, me ua d…®kavigham. Me ua d…®kavight…® e fogh suam me God…®n boribara, egh me enselbar m…®n ikiam. Kamagh…®n me uam ar…®m…®gh…®ran kogh…®va, egh kamagh…®n me poroghamibar amuan kogham.  
\v 37 Ez…® Moses uab…® temer avim…®n eghaghanim…®n aven en aka, aremeziba ua d…®kavam. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, N…® Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God.‚Äô  
\v 38 Kamagh…®n e fo, God aremezibar God puvat…®, a gumazir angamra itibar God. Ez…®ma an damazim…®n an boriba bar angamra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuim, Tisa.‚Äù  
\v 40 Egha me uam an azangs…®ghan atiati. 
\s1 Iesus a tina? 
\r (Matyu 22:41-46 ko Mak 12:35-37) 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Iesus gumazamiziba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® gumazamiziba ghaze, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim Krais, a Devit…®n ovavim?  
\v 42 Devit uab…® Ighiabar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven m…®keme, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòEkiam, nan Ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄúNan agharir guvim…®n amadaghan daperagh.\f + \ft (20:42) Ekiam Iesus, God ko biziba bar dar ganam.\f* 
\q1  
\v 43 Egh mang…® dughiar k…® n…®n apaniba, 
\q2 me damut…®ma me n…®n apengan ikiamim.‚Äù ‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 44 Egha Devit ‚ÄòEkiam‚Äô a gat…®. Manmagh…®n amiz…®, a Devit…®n ovavim?‚Äù 
\s1 Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba arazir kurabagh ami 
\r (Matyu 23:1-36 ko Mak 12:38-40 ko Luk 11:37-54) 
\p  
\v 45 Ez…® gumazamiziba orazima a uan suren gumaziba kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 46 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba bagh gan. Me uari fava korotiar ruarir kaba aghuraruasa ifonge. Ez…® gumazamiziba maket…®n danganim…®n men ziaba fasa me bar akonge. Egha God ko m…®geir d…®penir averiam…®n dabirabir aghuariba iniva, egha isar ekiabar dughiabar me danganir ziaba itiba iniasa bar ifonge.  
\v 47 Me amuir odiaribagh ifara, men d…®peniba ok…®a, ghaze e dera. Egha gumaziba men ziaba fasa, egha me God ko m…®g…®a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruaribagh ami. Kamagh…®n amir gumaziba, men ivezir kuram gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar ivezim bar a gafiragham.‚Äù 
\c 21  
\s1 Amuir odiarim dag…®amning God gan…®ngi 
\r (Mak 12:41-44) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus damazimning fegha garima dag…®aba itir gumaziba uan dag…®aba isa God…®n D…®penim…®n dag…®aba ar…®zir danganim gar…®si.  
\v 2 Ez…® a garima dag…®aba puvat…®zir amizir pam aremezir mam uaghan uan dag…®ar muziarimning, at…®.  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, biziba puvat…®zir amuir odiarir kam dag…®ar muziarir pumuning dag…®aba ar…®zir danganim gat…®, ez…® an dag…®ar pumuning gumazir igharaziba ar…®gh…®zir dag…®abagh afira.  
\v 4 Me uan dag…®ar av…®ribar amodogh…®n dag…®ar muziariba an…®ngi. Ez…®ma a uan dabirabir onganarazim…®n m…®rara dag…®ar muziarir abuananamning at…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, God…®n D…®penim ikuvigham 
\r (Matyu 24:1-2 ko Mak 13:1-2) 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…®ma an suren gumazir maba God…®n D…®penim…®n garava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe dag…®ar bar aghuibar an ingarighava, Afeziar Ekiam dan…®ngamin bizir aghuir maba an kuruke.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n garir bizir kabanagh, dughiam iz…®t…®ma dag…®ar kaba, gumaziba bar da pueght…® da bar mogh…®ra daghregham. Eght…® tam tam gis…®n ikeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, os…®mt…®ziba g…®n otivam 
\r (Matyu 24:3-14 ko Mak 13:3-13) 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúTisa, bizir kaba manad…®zogh…®n otivam? Eght…® arazir manam faragh otoght…®ma, e fogh suam, dughiar kam rogh…®ra ize?‚Äù  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan, ia men ifavariba baraghan mark…®. Gumazir av…®riba nan ziam…®n iz…®va suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara!‚Äô ez…®, ‚ÄòDughiam rogh…®ra ize!‚Äô Men g…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 9 Egh ia inogoviba ko adoghadozir m…®dorozir akaba baragh…®va, atiatingan mark…®. Bizir kabanagh faragh otivigham, eght…®ma nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®ra otoghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguibaba uarira uariv soght…®ma, dakoziba uarira uariv sogham.  
\v 11 Eght…® m…®k…®mk…®zir gavgaviba, koma dagheba otevir dughiaba koma ar…®mariar gavgaviba nguibar tabar otivt…®ma, atiatingamin biziba koma overiam…®n p…®n arazarazir ekiaba otivam. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúEght…® bizir kaba g…®n otivam, me faragh ian suiragh…®va arazir kurabar ia damuam. Me ia kotiam dar…®ghs…® ia inigh…®va God ko m…®geir d…®peniba koma kalabuziabar aven mangam. Eght…®ma ia nan g…®n zuir gumaziba me bizir kam bang…®n ia inigh…®va atriviba koma gavman…®n gumazir ekiabar damazim…®n mangam.  
\v 13 Eght…® kar dughiar aghuir ia nan akam me m…®k…®namim.  
\v 14 Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh. Ia faragh me m…®k…®ms…® akabagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.  
\v 15 Eght…® k…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba koma m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuiba ia dan…®ngt…®ma, ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibara damut…®ma, ian apanitam ian akaba batogh…®va ia adoghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® ian ameboghfeziaba, ko aveghbuaba, ko anababa, ko namakaba merara, ia inigh…®va gumazir kurabar dafaribar at…®ght…®, me ian taraziv soght…® ia ar…®m…®ghregham.  
\v 17 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian aghuagham.  
\v 18 Egh me bar tong arazitam ia damuan kogham. Kamagh…®n ian dapanar…®zitam asigh…®ran kogham.  
\v 19 Ia tugh gavgavighv…®ra ik…®va, dabirabir bar aghuim iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze Jerusalem kuvigham 
\r (Matyu 24:15-21 ko Mak 13:14-19) 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n gant…®ma m…®dorozir gumaziba iz…®va a kont…®ma, n…® fogham a gas…®ghas…®gham…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize.  
\v 21 Egh gumazir Judian itiba ar…® m…®ghs…®abar mang…®t…®ma, Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itiba azenan mang…®t…®ma, Jerusalem…®n azenan itir gumaziba uam an aven mangan markiam.  
\v 22 Kar os…®mt…®zibar dughiam, God da is…®va Israelbar an…®ng…®va, men arazir kuraba ikarvagham. A fom…®ra osirizir mogh…®n otogham.  
\v 23 Aiee! Amizir naviba adaiba koma oteba boribagh an…®diba dughiar izamiba bar men osemegham! Eght…®ma God gumazir kabar atart…®ma, os…®mt…®zir ekiam nguazir kam bativam.  
\v 24 Eght…® m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®sozir sababar tarazigh inivt…®ma me arigh…®r…®t…®, me tarazi suigh…®va, me amangt…®ma me nguibar Israel…®n azenan itibar mangam. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba Jerusalem bar paz…®va an itir bizibar amu mang…® dughiar me Jerusalem…®n ganamin dughiam g…®vagham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazibar Borim g…®n izam 
