\p  
\v 25 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEght…® arazaraziba aruem ko iakinim ko m…®koveziba bativam. Eght…® ongarim d…®p…®r t…®ngagh…®v…®ra ik…®t…®ma nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bar atiatigh okam n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 26 Eght…® overiam…®n biziba bar n…®gham, kamagh…®n gumaziba atiating…®va damaziba men isirt…®ma me daighir…®va, egh me otivamin biziba bagh m…®zuam…®va n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 27 Egh me dughiar kam…®n Gumazibar Borim…®n gant…®, a ghuariam…®n tong…®n gavgavim ko angazangarir ekiam sara izam.  
\v 28 Eght…® bizir kabanagh otivighr…®t…®ma ia d…®kavigh, uan dapaniba fegh gan! God ua ia iniamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize!‚Äù 
\s1 Temer figh…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 24:32-35 ko Mak 13:28-31) 
\p  
\v 29 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa temer figh…®n gan…®va temer maba sara gan.  
\v 30 Temeba dafariba asit…®ma ia fogham, aruem ganamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize.  
\v 31 Kamagh…®ra ia bizir kabar gan fogh suam, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize. 
\p  
\v 32 ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamizir kaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® bizir kaba bar otivam.  
\v 33 Overiam ko nguazim g…®vagham, eght…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n suren gumaziba uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan 
\p  
\v 34 Egha Iesus ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh ganigh! Isaba ko, d…®par onganiba ko nguazir kam…®n biziba, ia puv dagh n…®ghn…®ght…®, da ia d…®kab…®nt…®, dughiar otivamin kam puram otogh…®va, mati as…®zibar azuazim…®n m…®n ian suigham.  
\v 35 Eght…® dughiar kam nguibaba koma nguazir kam…®n gumaziba bar me bativam.  
\v 36 Ia zurara uari bagh gan Afeziam ko m…®k…®mv…®ra ik…®t…®ma, a gavgavim ia dan…®ngt…®ma ia bizir otivamin kabagh itavragham. Egh ia Gumazibar Otarim…®n damazim…®n tuivam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Egha dughiabar zurara Iesus, God…®n D…®penim…®n aven men sure gamuava, guarat…®zibar Oliv…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuava d…®magaribar an iti.  
\v 38 Ez…® gumaziba bar Iesus baraghasa, m…®zarazibar God…®n D…®penim…®n arui. 
\c 22  
\ms1 Iesus m…®zazim inigha aremegha ua d…®kafi 
\mr (Sapta 22-24) 
\s1 Judas Iesus isa gumazir kurabar dafaribagh at…® 
\r (Matyu 26:1-5 ko 26:14-16 ko Mak 14:1-2 ko 14:10-11 ko Jon 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Dat…®r…®gh…®n Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam rogh…®ra izi. An ziam, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam.  
\v 2 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me gumazibar atiatighava, kamagh…®n me Iesus…®n m…®soghasa tuaviba buri.  
\v 3-4 Iesus…®n 12-plan gumazir mam Judas, an ziar mam Iskariot. Satan an navir averiam…®n ghu. Ez…® a Iesus isava God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazir ekiaba, ko ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dafaribar ar…®ghasa ghua me koma m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh ami.  
\v 5 Ez…® me an m…®g…®r…®g…®am gifuegha ivezim a dan…®ngasa, akabar k…®ri.  
\v 6 Ez…® Judas ivezim inian ifuegha Iesus is…®va men dafaribar ar…®ghasa tuaviba buri. A ghaze, Iesus uab…®ra ik…®t…®, an an suiragh men dafarim dar…®gham. 
\s1 Suren gumazimning daghebar k…®ri 
\r (Matyu 26:17-25 ko Mak 14:12-21 ko Jon 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 7 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n oto. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n me God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam bagha sipsip…®n nguzim m…®suegh anem…® ik…®va, a g…®n…®ghn…®ghasa.\f + \ft (22:7) N…®, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam koma Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam…®n m…®ngariba g…®foghs…®, n…® ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus Jon koma Pita amadagha kamagh…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua mang…®va e God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam ramamin daghebar k…®r.‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® aning an azara, ‚ÄúGa managh a bagh danganim ak…®ram?‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® a kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar ekiam…®n aven mang…®t…®, gumazitam magh…®ra m…®ner d…®pam ater iz…® gua batoght…®ma, gua an g…®n a zuir d…®penim…®n mang…®.  
\v 11 Egh d…®penim…®n ghuavim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòTisa kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan danganir k…® uan suren gumaziba ko God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam ramamim mana?‚Äù ‚Äô  
\v 12 Eght…® a ghuriam…®n aven danganir bar ekiatam guan akagham, dakoziba koma dapiagh damamin dabirabiba ko biziba bar ik…®t…®, gua magh bizibar k…®r.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® aning ghua garima, biziba bar Iesus m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama otifi. Ez…®ma aning God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam bagha dagheba ko bizibar k…®ri. 
\s1 Iesus bret ko wain uan aposelbagh an…®di 
\r (Matyu 26:26-30 ko Mak 14:22-26 ko 1 Korin 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® damamin dughiam otoz…®, Iesus uan aposelba ko me dagher dakozim…®n m…®n apiaghav iti.  
\v 15-16 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® ua God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam…®n dagher katam rameghan kogham. Kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n otogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® ia ko isar kam ramasa bar ifonge. Egh k…® g…®n m…®zazim iniam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17-18 Egha Iesus wain apir itarim inighava Ekiam m…®nabagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, k…® uam wain…®n ov…®zim…®n d…®par katam raman kogham, kamagh…®ra ik…®t…®ma God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam otogham. Kamagh…®n, ia kagh a inigh ia uari dan…®ng.‚Äù  
\v 19 Egha a bret inigha, Ekiam m…®nabagha anebighava me gan…®ga kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar nan nivaf…®zim, \f * \ft (22:19-20) Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Akar m…®kovezir pumuning…®n (*) tong…®n itiba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazim g…®n a da osiri.\f* k…® ia bagha anen…®ngi. Ia anem…®, na g…®n…®ghn…®gh.‚Äù  
\v 20 Me amegha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® kamagh…®ra a wain…®n apir itarim inighava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúItarim…®n aven itir wain…®n kam, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam, k…® uan ghuzim…®n a gamiz…®ma, a ia bagha iri.  
\v 21 Eght…® ia gan, dafarir na inigh…®va gumazir kurabar dafarim dar…®gham, a kara na ko dakozim gaperaghavt…®.  
\v 22 Eght…® Gumazibar Borim tuavir Afeziam faragha a bagh at…®zim…®n g…®n mangam. Ez…® gumazir a inigha gumazir kurabar dafarim gat…®zim, gumaka, a bar ikuvigham.‚Äù  
\v 23 Ez…® me akar kam baregha uarira uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúTina bizir kam damuam?‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n aposelba uari adogha m…®gei, tina faragham? 
\p  
\v 24 Egha aposelba uari adogha ghaze, tinara en faragham?  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKantrin Igharazir Gumazibar atriviba, me uan gavgaviba ko ziaba fava, arazir kuraba gumazibagh amuava, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei ‚ÄòE gumazibar akurvasi.‚Äô  
\v 26 Ia kamagh…®n damuan mark…®. Gumazir ian torim…®n ikia ian faragha zuim, a uab…® apengan ik…®va, borim…®n m…®n uab…® ar…®gh. Ez…® gumazir ian faragha zuim, ian ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®.  
\v 27 Tinara ekefe, gumazir pura dagher dakozim…®n aperaghav itim o gumazir dagheba an…®dim? Gumazir pura dagher dakozim…®n aperaghav itim. Ez…®ma k…® ian torim…®n ikia mati ian ingangarir gumazim. 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúK…® os…®mt…®ziba aterima ia na ko iti.  
\v 29 Kamagh…®ra nan afeziam Atrivim…®n m…®n na at…®z…®ma, k…® uaghan atrivibar m…®n ia ar…®ghasa.  
\v 30 Eght…® nan atrivir dughiam…®n aven ia na ko atrivim…®n dabirabir aghuaribar apiagh…®va Israelbar anabar 12 plan ganam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Pita ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham 
