\v 42 ‚ÄúAfeziam, n…® ifueghava na da os…®mt…®zir kam inigh. Egh nan ifongiam…®n g…®n mangan mark…®. N…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 43 \f * \ft (22:43-44) Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Akar m…®kovezir pumuning…®n (*) tong…®n itiba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazim g…®n a da osiri.\f* Ez…® ensel mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izava gavgavim a gan…®di.  
\v 44 Ez…® Iesus n…®ghn…®ghava bar oseme, egha a pamtem Afeziam ko m…®gei. Ez…® an doriba otivaghira mati ghuzim nguazim giri.  
\v 45 An Afeziam ko m…®kemegha, d…®kavighava uamategha uan suren gumaziba bagha zui. Egha a men garima, me bar osemeghava akuav…®ra iti.  
\v 46 Ez…® a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha akui? Ia d…®kavigh…®va Afeziam ko m…®k…®m. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir ekiam ia damut…®ma, ia ireghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Judas Iesus isava, gumazir kurabar dafarim gat…® 
