\v 47 Egha Iesus m…®g…®av…®ra itima maburan gumazir b…®zim oto. An 12 plan gumazir mam Judas men faragha iza tuavim men aka. A Iesus…®n borogh…®ra izeghava an torasava ami.  
\v 48 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúJudas kar n…® Gumazibar Otarim…®n toregh…®va a inigh…®va, gumazir kurabar dafarim dar…®ghasa?‚Äù 
