\v 49 Ez…® suren gumaziba Iesus ko ikia garima arazim otivasava amima, me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, e uan m…®dorozir sababar me m…®sogham, o?‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® men mav m…®dorozir sabam inighava, ofa gamir gumazibar ekiam…®n ingangarir gumazir mam m…®soghava, an kuarim bar anetuz…® a ir…®.  
\v 51 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúArazir kam atakigh!‚Äù Egha an an kuarim…®n suiraz…®, a dera. 
