\v 59 Dughiam mong ghugha g…®vaz…®ma, gumazir igharazim izava pamtem ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra kav, a Galilin gumazimra. Kamagh…®n e guizbang…®ra fo, a uaghan a ko ike.‚Äù  
\v 60 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAiee! N…® tizim m…®gei? K…® bar fozir puvat…®!‚Äù Eghava a m…®g…®av…®ra itima tuarim ake.  
\v 61 Ez…® Ekiam raghr…®ghava m…®gh…®gha Pitan garima, a m…®kemezir akabagh in…®r…®, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® na g…®fozir puvat…®,‚Äô eght…® tuarim magh…®rama akegham.‚Äù  
\v 62 Egha Pita in…®r…®ghava azenim…®n ghua bar puv…®rama azi. 
\s1 Me Iesus…®n m…®soghava a d…®pofi 
