\p  
\v 63 Ez…® gumazir Iesus…®n suighiziba d…®bovir akabar a m…®g…®ava a m…®sosi.  
\v 64 Egha me inir av…®zim…®n an damazimning ikegha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, n…® e m…®k…®m! Tina n…® m…®soke?‚Äù  
\v 65 Egha me akar kurar av…®rir maba saram a m…®keme. 
\s1 Iesus gumazir apanibar damazim…®n tughav iti 
\r (Matyu 26:59-66 ko Mak 14:55-64 ko Jon 18:19-24) 
\p  
\v 66 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma, Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazir aruaba (ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba) me bar iza uari akuvaghav itima, me Iesus inighava men damazim…®n zui.  
\v 67 Ez…® me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®k…®m, kar n…® Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, o ti puvat…®?‚Äù Ez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®kemeght…®ma, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikian kogham.  
\v 68 Eght…® k…® ian azaraght…®ma, ia na m…®kemeghan kogham.  
\v 69 Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ko g…®n izamin dughiaba, Gumazibar Otarim gavgaviba bar itir God…®n agharir guvim…®n daperagh…®v ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 70 Ez…® me bar an azara, ‚ÄúKar n…® God…®n Otarim?‚Äù Ez…®ma a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® an Otarimra.‚Äù  
\v 71 Egha me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE tizim bagh uamategh gumaziba inight…® me gumazir kam…®n arazibar gun e m…®k…®mam? A uab…® bizir kam m…®kemez…®ma e an akatorim baregha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 23  
\s1 Me Iesus inighava Pailat…®n damazim…®n zuima a m…®t…®ghav iti 
\r (Matyu 27:1-2 ko 27:11-14 ko Mak 15:1-5 ko Jon 18:28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha gumazir b…®zim bar d…®kavigha Iesus inigha Pailat bagha zui.  
\v 2 Egha me d…®kavigha a gifara, kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE gumazir kam…®n garima an en gavman…®n ikura. Egha an e dag…®aba Sisar dan…®ngan bar en anogoregha, kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, a uab…® atrivim ko God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, Krais.‚Äù  
\v 3 Ez…® Pailat Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® Judabar atrivim, o?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar n…® m…®geim, a guizbang…®ra.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba koma gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® gumazir kam…®n arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® me bar gavgavigha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA Galilin Provins…®n ikegha nguibabagh aruava men sure gamua men navibagh inivava da fe. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n a Judian Provins…®n izegha kagh otogha kamagh…®n amuav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\s1 Me Iesus inighava Herot…®n damazim…®n zui 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Pailat m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha, kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúKar Galilin gumazim?‚Äù  
\v 7 Iesus Herot garir Provins…®n ikez…®ma, Pailat kamagh…®n foghava, anemadaz…® a Herot bagha ghu. Dughiar kam…®n Herot uaghan Jerusalem…®n iti.  
\v 8 Herot fom…®ra Iesus…®n ganasa ifuegha, an ganizir puvat…®gha, dughiar kam…®n an an ganigha, bar akonge. Egha Iesus…®n akaba baregha an mirakel…®n tam…®n ganasa. 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Herot azangs…®zir av…®rav…®ribar Iesus gamima, a bar an azangs…®zitam ikarazir puvat…®.  
\v 10 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me rogh…®ra tuivighava, an atarava, akaba pamtem a gasi.  
\v 11 Egha Herot uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko an atarava d…®bovir akar kurabar a m…®gei. Egha me atrivim…®n inir aghuir mam inigha a gikegha, uam anemadaz…®, a Pailat bagha zui.  
\v 12 Fom…®ra Herot Pailat…®n an…®ngaghe, egha dughiar kam aning ua uaning ini. 
\s1 Me Iesus is…® temem gafughasa, Pailat…®n m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 27:15-26 ko Mak 15:6-15 ko Jon 18:38-19:16) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Pailat, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko gumazir dapanir ekiaba, ko gumazamiziba, men deima me bar uari akuvagha iti.  
\v 14 Ez…®ma a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir kam inighava na bagha ize. Egha ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòA gumazamizibav geima me gavman…®n ikura.‚Äô Ez…® k…® ian damazim…®n arazir kabanagh bagha an azangs…®ki. Ia oragh! K…® gumazir kam…®n arazitam batozir puvat…®. Ia purama a gifari.  
\v 15 Ez…® Herot uaghan n…®ghn…®zir kam ikiava, gumazir kam e bagha uam anemada. Ia oraki! An arazir kuratam damigh…®va, an ovengam. Gumazir kam arazir kuratam gamizir pu, an ovengan kogham.  
\v 16-17 Kamagh…®n, k…® purama a fozoregh, an ateght…®ma a mangam.‚Äù\f + \ft (23:16-17) Fofozir gumazir maba m…®g…®a ghaze, akar igharazir mam uaghan vez…®n kam iti. A kamak…®n, ‚ÄúMe arazir kam iti, me azeniba bar, Isar Ekiam…®n Dughiar kam…®n itima, Pailat kalabus…®n gumazir mam ataghiz…® a me bagha zui.‚Äù N…® Mak 15:6…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® amiziba ko gumaziba bar mogh…®ra tuai, ‚ÄúGumazir mam…®n m…®sokegh! Egh Barabas ateght…® a e bagh iz…®!‚Äù  
\v 19 (Barabas a fom…®ra Rom…®n gavman…®n ikuragha Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n aven m…®dorozim fore. Ez…® gumazir maba ariagh…®re. Ez…® me a isa kalabus gat…®.)  
\v 20 Ez…® Pailat Iesus ateght…® a mangasa ua me m…®gei.  
\v 21 Ez…® me kamagh…®n tuai, ‚ÄúA m…®sokegh! A m…®sokegh! A is…® ter ighuvim gafugh!‚Äù  
\v 22 Ez…® dughiar m…®kezim a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh su? An arazir kurar manam gami? K…® an arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®. An arazir kuratam damigh…®va an ovengam. Gumazir kam arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. K…® purama a fozoregh…®va aneteght…®, a mangam.‚Äù  
\v 23 Ez…®ma me bar mogh…®ra gavgavigha dei, ‚ÄúIesus is…®va ter ighuvim gafugh!‚Äù Ez…® men d…®mdiaba bar Pailat…®n akam gafira.  
\v 24 Ez…®ma Pailat men akam…®n g…®n ghugha, Iesus…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, an ovengam.  
\v 25 Gumazamiziba me Pailat…®n deima a Barabas ataki. Gumazir kam a gavman ikuragha m…®dorozim forez…®ma, gumazir maba ariagh…®re. Ez…® me a isa kalabus gat…®. Ez…®ma Pailat gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghuava, Iesus isava m…®dorozir gumazibar dafarim gat…®. 
\s1 Me Iesus isa ter ighuvim gafu 
\r (Matyu 27:32-44 ko Mak 15:21-32 ko Jon 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus inigha zuima, gumazir mam an ziam Saimon, a Sairin…®n gumazir mam. A Jerusalem…®n mangasa iza me gitav…®raz…®ma, me an suira. Egha me ter ighuvim an d…®p…®zim gat…®gha a m…®geima a Iesus…®n g…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…®ma gumazir av…®rim an g…®n ghua, amiziba a bagha aziava azir akar ighiar am…®r…®zibagh ami.  
\v 28 Ez…®ma Iesus raghr…®gha kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Jerusalem…®n amiziba, ia na bagh arangan mark…®. Ia uari ko uan boriba bagh arang!  
\v 29 G…®n dughiatam otoght…®ma, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòAmizir furabaghatiba ko amizir t…®ghar boriba batamiba ko, amizir oteba boribagh an…®ngizir puvat…®ziba, me bar akuegham.‚Äô 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 ‚ÄòEgh me dughiar kam…®n kamagh…®n m…®ghs…®abav k…®mam, 
\q2 ‚ÄúIa e gis…®n ir…®gh…®va, e mongegh!‚Äù ‚Äô 
\m  
\v 31 ‚ÄúMe dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kam…®n temer angamt…®zim damigh…®va arazir mana tam…®n temer m…®diar…®m damuam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba gumazir kurar pumuning Iesus ko aning…®n m…®sueght…®ma me aremeghasa aning inigha izi.  
\v 33 Egha me ghua danganir mam…®n oto, an ziam Dapanir Agharim. Egha me danganir kam Iesus isava temem…®n anegura. Me uaghan gumazir kuramning aguraz…®ma, mam an guvim…®n itima, mam an k…®riam…®n iti.  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, me amir biziba me dagh fozir puvat…®. N…® men arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh.‚Äù Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus…®n korotiaba iniasa satu gikararai. 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® gumazamiziba an gara tuivighav itima, gumazir dapanir ekiaba uaghan an gara m…®nbaba sighsirava kamagh…®n a m…®gei. ‚ÄúA gumazir mabar akurvakis. Egh a guizbang…®ra God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, gumazir God inabazim, a uab…® uab…®n akuragh.‚Äù  
\v 36-37 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba izava uaghan a d…®povava, egha wain…®n d…®par m…®sozim a ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® guizbang…®ra Judabar atrivir gumazim, n…® uab…® uab…®n akuragh!‚Äù  
\v 38 Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba osizirir mam Iesus…®n dapanim gis…®n anegura. An osiziriba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam Judabar Atrivir Gumazim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® gumazir kurar mam ter ighuvim…®n guraghav ikia, atara kamagh…®n Iesus…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® guizbang…®ra God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, n…® uab…®n akurvagh…®va ga sarama akuragh!‚Äù  
\v 40 Ez…® gumazir kurar igharazim atarava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ovengasava amuava, God…®n atiati, o puvat…®?  
\v 41 Me deragha ga gami, ga uan arazir kurabagh ipuri. Ez…®ma gumazir kam arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 42 Egha gumazir kam kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúIesus, n…® g…®n atrivim…®n ikiamin dughiam n…® na gin…®r…®gh.‚Äù  
\v 43 Ez…®ma Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na ko God…®n Nguibar Aghuarim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus areme 
\r (Matyu 27:45-56 ko Mak 15:33-41 ko Jon 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 44-45 Ez…® aruem dughiar kam…®n garir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®tatem 12 klogh…®n nguazim bar anevaragha ghua 3 klogh…®n tu. Ez…®ma God…®n D…®penim…®n itir inir ekiam tong…®ra b…®ki. 
\p  
\v 46 Ez…® Iesus pamtem kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, k…® uan duam n…®n dafarim gar…®si.‚Äù A kamagh…®n m…®kemeghava uan duam sue. 
\p  
\v 47 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir ekiam kamagh…®n ganighava God…®n ziam fe. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, kar gumazir aghuim, a bizitam pazava a gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 48 Ez…® gumazamizir iza itiba bizir kabanagh…®n gari da otivima, me azia, uan afar…®zibav m…®sogha, egha uan d…®penibar zui. 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…®ma Iesus g…®fozir gumaziba, ko amizir an g…®n Galilin izeziba, me mong saghon tuivigha ikia, bizir kabar gari da otifi. 
\s1 Me Iesus…®n kuam dag…®ar torim gar…®si 
\r (Matyu 27:57-61 ko Mak 15:42-47 ko Jon 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 50-51 Ez…® gumazir mam, an ziam Josep, a Judian Provins…®n nguibam Arimatean ikegha ize. A gumazir aghuim, a God…®n damazim…®n derazir mam, a Kaunsel memban mam. Egha a men n…®ghn…®ziba ko arazibar g…®n mangan aghua. A God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam a baghav…®ra muza iti.  
\v 52 Egha Josep Iesus…®n kuam iniasa ghua Pailat…®n azaraz…®ma, Pailat an amamangat…®.  
\v 53 Ez…® a Iesus…®n kuam temem…®n anedegha, inir ghurghurim…®n a righa, a inigha ghuava dag…®ar torir me fom…®ra gumazir kuatam at…®zir puvat…®zim gat…®.  
\v 54 Kar dughiar bizibar k…®rim, ez…® Sabat…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize. 
\p  
\v 55 Ez…® amizir Iesus…®n g…®n Galilin izeziba, me Josep…®n g…®n ghua dag…®ar torim…®n gari. Egha me uaghan garima, Josep manmagh…®n Iesus…®n kuam at…®.  
\v 56 Egha me ganigha g…®vaghava, uamategha uan d…®penibar ghuava bizir mughuriaba itiba ko boreba isa da ar…®si. Egha God…®n osizirim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me Sabat…®n dughiam…®n avughsi. 
\c 24  
\s1 Iesus ua d…®kafi 
\r (Matyu 28:1-10 ko Mak 16:1-8 ko Jon 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Sanden bar m…®zaraghara, amiziba borer mughuriar aghuir me ar…®gh…®ziba, inighava dag…®ar torim…®n zui.\f + \ft (24:1) Wikbar faraghav…®ra zuir aruem, a Sandera.\f* 
\v 2 Egha me gari, me torim avarazir dag…®am, me a puegha ghu.  
\v 3 Egha me aven ghua Iesus…®n kuam bagha garava avenge.  
\v 4 Egha me kamagh…®n ganigha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua tuivighav itima, gumazir pumuning zuam…®ra aning…®n korotiaba on…®marim…®n m…®n taghtagha men m…®n tughav iti.  
\v 5 Ez…® amiziba bar atiatigha avigha nguazim…®n gari, ez…® gumazimning kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha gumazir angamra itim gumazir ovengezibar danganim…®n a buri?  
\v 6 A kagh itir puvat…®; a ua d…®kafi! A ia ko Galilin ikia ia m…®kemezir bizim, ia a g…®n…®ghn…®gh,  
\v 7 ‚ÄòGumazibar Otarim, me a is…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar dafarim dat…®ght…®, me a is…® ter ighuvim…®n a guragham. Eght…® a dughiar m…®kezim…®n ua d…®kavigham.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 8 Ez…® a m…®kemezir akaba me a dagh in…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 9 Egha me mozim ategha uamategha ghua bizir kabar gun Iesus…®n suren gumazir 11 plan m…®g…®ava igharaz darazi sara m…®keme.  
\v 10 Amizir bizir kabar gun Iesus…®n 11 plan aposelba ko igharaz daraziv kemeziba. Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, ko Joana, ko Maria a Jems…®n amebam, koma amizir igharazir maba uaghan me ko ikia bizir kabar gun aposelbav m…®gei.  
\v 11 Ez…® me amizibav g…®a ghaze, me ti onganighama, egha kamagh…®n me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim men akabar itir puvat…®.  
\v 12 \f * \ft (24:12) Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, akar otevir m…®kovezir pumuning…®n (*) tong…®n itiba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri.\f* Egha Pita kamagh…®n oregha d…®kavigha ivegha mozim…®n ghu. Egha an aviragha, mozim…®n gara bizitam…®n apizir puvat…®gha inir ghurghuribara gari da ireghav iti. Egha a uamategha ghua n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua ghaze, kar manmagh…®n amizir bizim. 
\s1 Gumazir pumuning Emeus…®n tuavim…®n Iesus bato 
\r (Mak 16:12-13) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® dughiar kamra gumazir pumuning Emeus…®n nguibam…®n zui, Emeus…®n nguibam…®n ikegha Jerusalem…®n zuir tuavim…®n ruarim, a 11 kilomita.  
\v 14 Ez…® aning bizir otivizir kabar gun uaningra uaning…®n m…®gei.  
\v 15 Egha aning bizir kabav g…®a uaning…®n azangs…®zima, Iesus uab…® otogha aning ko me zui.  
\v 16 Ez…® aning an garava egha deragha a g…®fozir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® an aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizibar uaning…®n m…®g…®a tuavim…®n zui?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® aning tughava an garava bar osemegha aziasava ami.  
\v 18 Ez…® aning…®n mav, an ziam Kliopas, an azara, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n izezir gumaziba bar bizir kam g…®fo. Ez…® n…® ti uab…®ra dughiar g…®vazibar Jerusalem…®n bizir kabagh fozir puvat…®?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúBizir tiziba?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® aning a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa Nasaret…®n Iesus bativizir bizibav gei. A God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, ez…® an akaba ko ingangariba God ko gumaziba bar men damazim…®n bar gavgafi.  
\v 20 Ez…® en ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko en gumazir aruaba a isa gavman…®n dafarim gat…®z…®, me a m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® me ter ighuvim…®n a gura.  
\v 21 Ez…® e faragha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n an iti, a God Ua Israelba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim. 
\p ‚ÄúEz…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam ua iti, bizir kaba otivigha g…®vaz…®, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an aremezir dughiar m…®kezim oto.  
\v 22-23 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en amizir maba m…®zaraghara mozim…®n ghuegha an kuam…®n apizir puvat…®. Egha iza e m…®kemez…®, e bar aguaghfa. Egha me ghaze, e irebam…®n m…®n enselbar garima, me kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, a ua d…®kafi.  
\v 24 Ez…® en marazi mozim…®n ghuegha amiziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar gari da iti, ez…® me an apizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua gumazir onganimning! Gua God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim koma navim zuam…®rama adar itir puvat…®.  
\v 26 Ez…® gua ti fozir puvat…®? God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, faragh m…®zaziba inigh egh g…®n God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iniam.‚Äù  
\v 27 Egha Iesus aning geghari. A faragha Moses osirizir akabav g…®a, ghua God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba bar aning m…®gei. A God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar an gun m…®kemeziba, dar m…®ngariba bar aning…®n sure gami. 
\p  
\v 28 Egha me nguibar me ikiamim…®n borogh…®ra ghuava, Iesus aning bada ghuav…®ra itima,  
\v 29 aning a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAruem bar g…®vaz…®ma am…®nim p…®ri. N…® ga ko dakuam.‚Äù Ez…®ma a ghuava aning koma akui.  
\v 30 Egha Iesus damasa aning koma aperaghav ikia, bret inighava Afeziar Ekiam m…®nabagha, bret abigha aning gan…®di.  
\v 31 Ez…® aning dat…®r…®gh…®n an garava a g…®fofozima, a pura puvat…®.  
\v 32 Ez…®ma aning magh…®ra uaning…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA tuavim…®n ga batogha God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n akabar ga m…®geima, gan navimning d…®kafi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Egha aning d…®kavigha zuam…®ra ghua Jerusalem…®n uamategha ghua garima, 11 pla Iesus…®n suren gumaziba, me marazi ko me uari akuvagha itima,  
\v 34 aning kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra! Iesus aremegha d…®kavigha ghua Saimon bato!‚Äù  
\v 35 Ez…® aning magh…®ra tuavim…®n otivizir bizibar gun me m…®g…®ava ghaze, a bret ab…®ghiz…®ma aning an ganighava a g…®fo. 
\s1 Iesus uan suren gumaziba bato 
\r (Matyu 28:16-20 ko Mak 16:14-18 ko Jon 20:19-23) 
\p  
\v 36 Iesus…®n suren gumazir 11 pla ko marazi, bizir kabar gun uariv geima, Iesus pura men tong…®n tughav ikia, \f * \ft (24:36) Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar otevir m…®kovezir pumuning…®n (*) tong…®n itiba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri.\f* a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNavir am…®rizim ia ko iti.‚Äù  
\v 37 Ez…® me bar atiatigha ghaze, me duam…®n gari.  
\v 38 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha atiatiava n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami?  
\v 39 Ia kagh nan dafariba ko dagaribar gan. Egh ia fogh suam, kar k…® Iesus uab…®. Egh ia nan suigh ia fogh. Duam aghariba ko nivaf…®ziba puvat…®. Ez…® ia nan gari, k…® da iti.‚Äù  
\v 40 \f + \ft (24:40) Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar otevir m…®kovezir pumuning…®n tong…®n itiba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri.\f* A kamagh…®n m…®kemegha uan dafariba ko dagariba men akakasi.  
\v 41 Egha me bar akuegha tintinibar n…®ghn…®gha, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®. Ez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúIa damamin daghetam iti?‚Äù  
\v 42 Ez…® me osirir tuazim…®n akuam a gan…®ngiz…®ma,  
\v 43 a men damazibar a inighava anepi. 
\p  
\v 44 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúFom…®ra Moses Osirizir Araziba, ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar osiziriba, ko Devit…®n ighiaba, da nan gun m…®kemezir biziba, da bar mogh…®ra guiz…®n otivam. Kar bizir k…® ia ko ikia ia m…®kemeziba.‚Äù  
\v 45 Egha a n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba me gan…®ngiz…®ma me Afeziar Ekiam…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n akabar m…®ngaribagh fo.  
\v 46 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziar Ekiam…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme, God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, Krais, an aremegh dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ikegh uamategh mozim…®n d…®kavigham.  
\v 47 Egh ia nan ziam…®n ia nan akam inigh mangam. Ia Jerusalem ikegh…®va nan akam inigh…®va nguazim…®n m…®kebaba bar dar mang…®. Ia gumazamizibav k…®mt…®, me navibagh iraght…® k…® men arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.  
\v 48 Ia uari uan damazibar bizir kabar ganiz…® mogh…®n dar gun m…®k…®m.  
\v 49 Ia oragh. Afeziam faragha akam ak…®ragha ghaze, a uan Duam is…® ia dan…®ngam. Ez…® k…® a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ia bagh anemangam. Kamagh…®n ia nguibar ekiam…®n ik…®. Egh mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar God ko itir gavgavim izighr…®t…®ma ia a iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 God Iesus inigha uamategha uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo 
\r (Mak 16:19-20 ko Aposel 1:9-12) 
\p  
\v 50 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba inigha ghuava Betanin borogh…®n itir danganim…®n tu. Egha a uan agharim ghufegha arazir aghuim me damuasava God…®n azai.  
\v 51 An arazir aghuim me damuasa God…®n azav…®ra itima, God a inigha uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanadi.  
\v 52 Ez…®ma me an ziam fa bar akuegha uamategha Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 53 Egha me God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ikiava an ziam fa mamagh…®ra iti. 
\p